\id MAT 
\h MATTHEW 
\toc3 Mat 
\toc2 Matthew 
\toc1 Matthew Gelh Lungdamna Thu 
\mt1 MATTHEW 
\mt2 Gelh Lungdamna Thu 
\ili Laigelh: Matthew 
\ili Laisim mite: Judah mite 
\ili A hun: A.D. 50 
\imt1 Thu Mapi 
\ip Lai Siangtho Lui sungah Messiah hong pai nading thu tamveipi kigen hi. Pasian in Lai Siangtho Lui sunga thugenna nunung pen a neih khit kum 400 ciangin, a Tapa leitung ah hong paisak hi. Lungdamna thu bu liteng in Zeisu nuntakna, sihna le thawhkikna thute limgen uh hi. A.D. 50 kum ciangin Lai Siangtho Lui sunga a kigenkhol thute Zeisu in tangtungsak taktak ahihna thu lahkhiat nadingin Matthew in lungdamna thubu a gelh ahi hi. Judah mite in Zeisu pen Messiah hi cih a tel theih nading uh hong gen phadiak hi. 
\ip Matthew in Levi kici min dang khat zong nei hi. Zeisu nung a zuih ma in siahdongpa khat ahi hi (\xt Mak 2:14\xt*). Tua hun laitakin Rome kumpite in Judah mite uk ahih manin Judah mite aa dingin a galte uh ahi hi. Siahdongte in a galte uh ahi Rome kumpi aa dingin siahdonsak a, amau aa ding zong tampi mah donbeh uh hi. Hih a uthuai het lo siahdonna panin Topa in Matthew samkhia a, a nuntakna kikhelsak in a nungzui suaksak a, hih lungdamna thubu gelh dingin zang hi. 
\ip Matthew lungdamna thubu sunga a gen noppi pen in Zeisu in Messiah ahihna thu ahi hi. Tua thu pen a tang masa panin hong kilang pah hi. A lian khatna sunga khangsimna sungah Zeisu pen Abraham Tapa ci in hong kipulak a, David Tapa ahihna zong hih laibu sung mun tampi ah kigelh hi. Matthew in David le kumpigam thu mun tampi ah na ciamteh hi. Zeisu in Lai Siangtho Lui sunga genkholhnate a tangtungsak Kumpipa ahihna thu zong Matthew in gen hi. Amah pen Israelte aa ding bek hi loin, leitung mi khempeuh aa ding Messiah zong ahi hi. Hih lungdamna thubu a tawpna pen ah, leitung minam khempeuh Zeisu nungzui suahsak nading sawlna lianpi tawh thu kikhum hi. 
\ip Zeisu in minam khempeuh Kumpi le Messiah ahihna laisimte in a tel baih nadingun limtakin a thu gualin Matthew in gelh hi. Matthew in Zeisu nuntakna le a nasepnate khenpi thumin khen hi. Tua khenpite sungah Zeisu tangthu le Zeisu thuhilhnate gen khawm hi. Zeisu thugen laka a minthang pen khat in Mual tung Thuhilhna ahi hi (a lian \xt 5-7). 
\ip Zeisu pen minamte khempeuh Kumpipa le Messiah ahih manin amah umin a nung zuih ding ahi hi. 
\iot Tomlakna: 
\io1 I. Kumpipa kiginkholhna (\ior 1:1-4:16\ior*) 
\io1 II. Kumpipa in mipi lakah a nasepna (\ior 4:17-16:20\ior*) 
\io1 III. Kumpipa sihna, kivuina le thawhkikna (\ior 16:21-28:20\ior*) 
\c 1 
\s1 Zeisu Khazih Khang Ciaptehna 
\r Luk 3:23-38 
\p 
\v 1 \x + \xo 1:1 \xt Isa 9:6-7; Jer 23:5-6; Luk 1:32, 69; Gal 3:16; Kil 22:16\x*Hih in Zeisu Khazih khang ciamtehna ahi hi. Amah in David tapa hi a, David in Abraham tapa ahi hi. 
\li1 
\v 2 \x + \xo 1:2 \xt Pian 21:3, 12; 25:26; 29:35\x*Abraham tapa Isaac, 
\li1 Isaac tapa Jacob, 
\li1 Jacob tapa Judah le a sanggam pasal teng ahi hi. 
\li1 
\v 3 \x + \xo 1:3 \xt Pian 38:27-30\x*Judah in Tamar tawh a neih a tapa Perez le Zerah, 
\li1 Perez tapa Hezron, 
\li1 Hezron tapa Ram, 
\li1 
\v 4 Ram tapa Amminadab, 
\li1 Amminadab tapa Nahshon, 
\li1 Nahshon tapa Salmon, 
\li1 
\v 5 \x + \xo 1:5 \xt Heb 11:31\x*Salmon in a zi Rahab tawh a neih a tapa Boaz, 
\li1 Boaz in a zi Ruth tawh a neih a tapa Obed, 
\li1 Obed tapa Jesse, 
\li1 
\v 6 \x + \xo 1:6 \xt 1Sa 16:1; 2Sa 12:24\x*Jesse tapa kumpipa David ahi hi. 
\p David in Uriah zi tawh a neih a tapa Solomon, 
\li1 
\v 7 Solomon tapa Rehoboam, 
\li1 Rehoboam tapa Abijah, 
\li1 Abijah tapa Asa, 
\li1 
\v 8 Asa tapa Jehoshaphat, 
\li1 Jehoshaphat tapa Joram, 
\li1 Joram tapa Uzziah, 
\li1 
\v 9 Uzziah tapa Jotham, 
\li1 Jotham tapa Ahaz, 
\li1 Ahaz tapa Hezekiah, 
\li1 
\v 10 \x + \xo 1:10 \xt 2Ku 20:21\x*Hezekiah tapa Manasseh, 
\li1 Manasseh tapa Amon, 
\li1 Amon tapa Josiah ahi hi. 
\li1 
\v 11 \x + \xo 1:11 \xt 2Ku 24:14-16; Jer 27:20; Dan 1:1\x*Jeconiah le a sanggam pasal tengin Babylon gam ah sala a kipaipih madeuh in a suak Josiah tate ahi uh hi. 
\p 
\v 12 \x + \xo 1:12 \xt Ezr 3:2\x*Babylon gama saltan khit ciangin Jeconiah in a neih a tapa Shealtiel, 
\li1 Shealtiel tapa Zerubbabel, 
\li1 
\v 13 Zerubbabel tapa Abiud, 
\li1 Abiud tapa Eliakim, 
\li1 Eliakim tapa Azor, 
\li1 
\v 14 Azor tapa Zadok, 
\li1 Zadok tapa Achim, 
\li1 Achim tapa Eliud, 
\li1 
\v 15 Eliud tapa Eleazar, 
\li1 Eleazar tapa Matthan, 
\li1 Matthan tapa Jacob, 
\li1 
\v 16 \x + \xo 1:16 \xt Mat 27:17; Luk 1:27\x*Jacob tapa Joseph hi a, 
\li1 Joseph in Khazih a kici Zeisu a hong suahna Mary pasal ahi hi. 
\p 
\v 17 Tua hi a, Abraham khang panin David khang ciang a vekin khang sawm le khang li, David khang panin Babylon gama saltang dinga a kimat hun ciang khang sawm le khang li, Babylon gama saltan hun pan Khazih khang ciang khang sawm le khang li mah ahi hi. 
\s1 Zeisu Khazih Suahna 
\r Luk 1:26-38; 2:1-7; Joh 1:14 
\p 
\v 18 \x + \xo 1:18 \xt Luk 1:35\x*Zeisu Khazih a suah zia hih bang ahi hi. A nu Mary pen Joseph zi dingin zuthawl kipiasa hi a, a kiteen ma un Kha Siangtho hangin a gai hi. 
\v 19 \x + \xo 1:19 \xt Thu 24:1\x*A lawmpa Joseph in mi dik hi a, a lawmnu Mary min daisak nuam lo ahih manin maksim dingin a ngaihsun hi. 
\p 
\v 20 \x + \xo 1:20 \xt Mat 27:19; Saw 5:19\x*Tua banga a ngaihsut laitakin Topa \w vantungmi\w* khat a mang sungah kilang a, “David tapa Joseph aw, na lawmnu Mary na teenpih ding lauthawng kei in; banghang hiam cihleh a sunga a paai nau pen Kha Siangtho hangin nau a paai ahi hi. 
\v 21 \x + \xo 1:21 \xt Lat 130:8; Luk 1:31; 2:11; Joh 3:17; Saw 5:31; Rom 11:14; Tit 2:14\x*Amah in tapa khat nei ding a, tua tapa in ama mite a mawhna panun honkhia ding ahih manin a min ZEISU na phuak ding hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 22 \x + \xo 1:22 \xt Mat 2:15; Luk 4:21; Joh 13:18\x*Topa in kamsangpa tunga a gensa thu a tangtun nadingin hih thu khempeuh a piang ahi hi. 
\v 23 \x + \xo 1:23 \xt Isa 8:10\x*Kamsangpa in, \qt “Ngai un, nungak siangtho khat gai in Tapa khat nei ding a, ama min Immanuel kici ding hi,”\qt*\f + \fr 1:23\ft \+xt Isa 7:14\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* a ci hi. 
\p Immanuel a khiatna in, “Eite tawh Pasian hong omkhawm hi,” a cihna ahi hi. 
\p 
\v 24 \x + \xo 1:24 \xt Saw 5:19\x*Joseph a ihmutna panin khanglo a, Topa vantungmi thupiakna bangin a lawmnu a teenpih hi. 
\v 25 \x + \xo 1:25 \xt Luk 1:31\x*Ahi zongin tua a tacil a suah khit matengin a lawmnu luppih lo a, a suah ciangin a min dingin ZEISU a phuak hi. 
\c 2 
\s1 Mi Pilte Hawhna 
\p 
\v 1 \x + \xo 2:1 \xt Luk 1:5; 2:4-7\x*Kumpipa Herod a man laitakin Judea gam Bethlehem khua ah Zeisu a suak hi. A suah khit ciangin en in, nisuahna lam pana hong pai mi pilte Jerusalem khuapi hong tung uh hi. 
\v 2 \x + \xo 2:2 \xt Jer 23:5; Mak 15:2; Luk 23:38; Joh 1:49\x*Amaute in, “Judah mite Kumpi dinga hong suakpa koi ah om ahi hiam? Nisuahna lam panin ama aksi ka muh uh ciangin amah bia dingin kong pai uh hi,” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 3 Kumpipa Herod in tua thu a zak ciangin Jerusalem khua mi khempeuh tawh a patau mahmah uh hi. 
\v 4 Herod in siampi liante le \w thukhamhilh siate\w* khempeuh kaikhawm in Khazih suah nading mun a dong hi. 
\v 5 \x + \xo 2:5 \xt Joh 7:42\x*Amaute in, “Judea gam Bethlehem khua ah a suak ding hi; banghang hiam cihleh kamsangpa in, 
\b 
\q1 
\v 6 \x + \xo 2:6 \xt 2Sa 5:2\x*‘\qt Judah gam Bethlehem khua aw,\qt* 
\q1 \qt Judah gam ukpite lakah khuaneu khua gina lo pen na hi kei hi.\qt* 
\q1 \qt Banghang hiam cihleh keima mi Israelte a cing ding Ukpa khat nangma sung panin a piang ding hi,’\qt*\f + \fr 2:6 \ft \+xt Mic 5:2\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* 
\m ci in a gelh khinzo hi,” a ci uh hi. 
\b 
\p 
\v 7 Tua khit ciangin Herod in mi pilte samsim a, aksi kilat hun teltakin a dong hi. 
\v 8 Amah in Bethlehem khua ah amaute sawl a, “Pai unla, tua naupangno va mukhia hamtang un. Kei zong pai in ka va biak theih nadingin na muh khit uh ciangin kei kiangah hong zasakkik un,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 9 Amaute in kumpipa vaikhakna a zak khit uh ciangin a paikhia uh hi. Tua ciangin nisuahna lama a muhsa uh aksi in naupangno omna tung a tun masiah amaute mai ah a pai hi. 
\v 10 Aksi a muh uh ciangin a lungdam mahmah uh hi. 
\v 11 \x + \xo 2:11 \xt Lat 72:10; Isa 60:3\x*Inn sungah a lut uh ciangin naupangno le a nu Mary mu uh a, bokin amah a bia uh hi. A van manphate uh suahkhia in kham, \w paknamtui\w*\f + \fr 2:11 \fk paknamtui\ft : Greek ah “libanos” kici a, \w zatui\w* le biakpiakna a kizang khawm paknamtui nam khat ahi hi.\f* le \w paknamtui kha\w* letsong in a pia uh hi. 
\v 12 \x + \xo 2:12 \xt Heb 11:7\x*Herod kiangah a paikik nawh loh nadingun Pasian in amaute mang sungah hilh ahih manin lampi dang tawnin amaute gam ah a ciahkik uh hi. 
\s1 Egypt Ah Taina 
\p 
\v 13 \x + \xo 2:13 \xt Saw 5:19; Kil 12:4\x*Mi pilte a ciah khit uh ciangin Topa \w vantungmi\w* khat Joseph mang sungah va kilang a, “Tho inla, naupangno le a nu Egypt gam ah taipih in. Herod in naupangno that nuamin zong ding ahih manin nang kiangah thu kong zaksakkik mateng tualai ah va om phot un,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 14 Joseph zong tho in naupangno le a nu zankimpi mahin Egypt gam ah a paikhiatpih hi. 
\v 15 \x + \xo 2:15 \xt Pai 4:22-23\x*Herod a sih mateng tualai ah a va om uh hi. Hih in, 
\b 
\q1 \qt “Egypt panin ka Tapa ka samkhia hi,”\qt*\f + \fr 2:15 \ft \+xt Hos 11:1\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* 
\m ci a, kamsangpa tungtawnin Topa gensa thu a tangtun nading ahi hi. 
\s1 Herod In Bethlehem Ah Naupangnote That 
\p 
\v 16 Herod in mi pilte khemna a theih ciangin heh mahmah hi. Tua ahih manin mi pilte a dotna panin a hun ding seh a, Bethlehem khua le a kim gam sunga om pasalno kum nih le a nuaisiah khempeuh a thatsak hi. 
\v 17 \x + \xo 2:17 \xt Mat 1:22\x*Kamsangpa Jeremiah in a gensa thu hihlai ah a tangtung hi. Amah in, 
\b 
\q1 
\v 18 \x + \xo 2:18 \xt Pian 35:19\x*\qt “Ramah ah tamlawhna, kahna le nakpi in thumna aw kiza hi.\qt* 
\q1 \qt Rachel in a tate kahkah a,\qt* 
\q1 \qt Amaute om nawn lo ahih manin,\qt* 
\q1 \qt A kihehnep ding a ut kei hi,”\qt*\f + \fr 2:18 \ft \+xt Jer 31:15\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* 
\m a ci hi. 
\s1 Nazareth Ah Ciahkikna 
\r Luk 2:39, 40 
\p 
\v 19 \x + \xo 2:19 \xt Saw 5:19\x*Herod a sih khit ciangin, en in, Egypt gama om Joseph mang sungah Topa vantungmi khat a va kilang hi. 
\v 20 \x + \xo 2:20 \xt Pai 4:19\x*Amah in, “Naupangno a that nuamte si khinzo ahih manin tho inla naupangno le a nu Israel gam ah ciahpih in,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 21 Amah zong tho a, naupangno le a nu tawh Israel gam hong zuan uh hi. 
\v 22 \x + \xo 2:22 \xt Luk 2:39\x*Archelaus in a pa Herod za luahin Judea gam uk hi cih thu a zak ciangin tua gam ah pai ngam lo a, Pasian in a mang sunga a hilhkholh mah bangin Galilee gam ah a pai hi. 
\v 23 \x + \xo 2:23 \xt Isa 11:1; 13:10; Mak 1:24; Luk 1:26; Joh 1:45\x*“Amah Nazareth mi kici ding hi,” ci a, kamsangte gensa thu a tangtun nadingin Nazareth kici khua ah hong pai in tualai ah a teeng hi. 
\c 3
\s1 Tuiphumpa John Thuhilhna
\r Mak 1:1-8; Luk 3:1-20; Joh 1:6-8, 15-36
\p
\v 1 \x + \xo 3:1 \xt Luk 1:13, 57-66; Saw 19:3-4\x*Tua hunin Judea gam gamlak ah Tuiphumpa John thuhilh in hong pai a,
\v 2 \x + \xo 3:2 \xt Dan 7:14; Luk 11:20; Joh 3:3, 5; Saw 1:3, 6\x*“Vantung kumpigam hong nai zo ahih manin na mawhna uh kisikkik un!” ci in a tangko hi.
\p
\v 3 \x + \xo 3:3 \xt Mal 3:1; Luk 1:76; Joh 1:23\x*Kamsangpa Isaiah in,
\b
\q1 \qt “Gamlak a kikopa awging in,\qt*
\q1 \qt ‘Topa pai nading lam na sial unla,\qt*
\q1 \qt Ama lampite na tangsak un,’ ci hi,”\qt*\f + \fr 3:3 \ft \+xt Isa 40:3\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f*
\m ci a a genpa in hih John ahi hi.
\b
\p
\v 4 \x + \xo 3:4 \xt Siam 11:22; 2Ku 1:8; Mat 3:1\x*John in kalaoh mul tawh a kigan puan silhin savun kawnggak tawh a kawng gak a, \w kauphe\w* le gamlak khuaizu tawh a kivak hi.
\v 5 Tua hun sungin Jerusalem a kipan Judea gam sung khempeuh le Jordan Gun kuam mun khempeuh panin John kiangah mite a va pai uh hi.
\v 6 \x + \xo 3:6 \xt Mak 1:4\x*Amaute in a mawhnate uh pulakin John in Jordan Gun ah a tuiphum hi.
\p
\v 7 \x + \xo 3:7 \xt Rom 1:18\x*\w Pharisee\w* pawlte le \w Sadducee\w* pawlte tampi tui kiphum dinga hong pai John in a muh ciangin amaute kiangah, “Gul gupha suante aw! Hong tung ding hehna panin a kihemkhia dingin kua in note hong hilhkhol ahi hiam?
\v 8 \x + \xo 3:8 \xt Saw 26:20\x*Tua ahih manin kisikkikna tawh a kituak gah na gah un.
\v 9 \x + \xo 3:9 \xt Luk 3:8\x*Note lungsim sungah, ‘Ka pa uh Abraham hi,’ ci in kimuang kha kei un; banghang hiam cihleh ken kong cih in ah Pasian in hih suangte nangawn Abraham tate a suaksak thei hi.
\v 10 \x + \xo 3:10 \xt Luk 3:9; Joh 15:2, 6\x*Tu mahmahin zong singphung tengah hei kinga zo hi. Tua ahih manin gah hoih a gah lo singkung khempeuh kiphuk in meikuang sungah kikhul ding hi.
\p
\v 11 \x + \xo 3:11 \xt Isa 4:4; Mak 1:4, 8\x*“Kisikkikna tungtawnin note kong tuiphum hi. Ahi zongin kei khit cianga hong pai ding pa in kei sangin vanglian zaw a, ama khedap tawi dingin zong ka kilawm kei hi. Amah in Kha Siangtho le mei tawh note hong phum ding hi.
\v 12 Amah in a buhcilna tual hahsiang dingin a khut ah \w ansi zapna\w* a tawi hi. Ama antak teng ansal sungah sung ding a, ansite ahih leh a mit ngei lo meikuang sungah a khul ding hi,” a ci hi.
\s1 Zeisu A Kituiphumna
\r Mak 1:9-11; Luk 3:21, 22; Joh 1:31-34
\p
\v 13 \x + \xo 3:13 \xt Mak 1:4\x*Tua ciangin John tui kiphumsak dingin Galilee gam panin Jordan Gun ah Zeisu hong pai hi.
\v 14 Ahih hangin John in, “Nangmah in kei nong tuiphum ding hi zaw napi in banghang in kei kiangah hong pai zawsop na hi hiam?” ci in a mang nuam kei hi.
\p
\v 15 Tua ciangin Zeisu in, “Thuman khempeuh i tangtungsak ding kilawm ahih manin tu in hong mang in,” a cih ciangin John in zong a mang hi.
\p
\v 16 \x + \xo 3:16 \xt Isa 11:2; Eze 1:1; Joh 1:51; Saw 7:56; Kil 4:1\x*Zeisu tui a kiphum khit ciangin tui sung panin a dingto pah hi. Tua laitakin en in, vantung kihong a, Pasian Kha in vakhu bangin hong kumsuk in Zeisu tungah a khawl, John in a mu hi.
\v 17 \x + \xo 3:17 \xt Thu 4:12; Lat 2:7; Isa 42:1; Mat 17:5; Mak 1:11; Luk 3:22; Saw 13:33; Heb 1:1-5; 2Pe 1:17\x*Vantung pan thakhatin aw khat hong gingkhia a, “Hihpa in a hong lungdamsak mahmah ka it ka Tapa ahi hi,” a ci hi.
\c 4 
\s1 Zeisu Kize-etna 
\r Mak 1:12-13; Luk 4:1-13 
\p 
\v 1 \x + \xo 4:1 \xt Pian 3:1-7; Heb 4:15\x*Tua khit ciangin \w Dawimangpa\w* ze-etna thuak dingin Kha in gamlak ah Zeisu a paipih hi. 
\v 2 \x + \xo 4:2 \xt Pai 34:28; 1Ku 19:8\x*Zeisu in sun 40 le zan 40 an a tan khit ciangin a gil a kial hi. 
\v 3 \x + \xo 4:3 \xt Mak 3:11; Luk 1:35; Joh 1:34, 49; Saw 9:20; Rom 1:4; 1Th 3:5; 1Jn 5:10-13, 20; Kil 2:18\x*Tua ciangin a ze-et ding pa ama kiangah va pai a, “Pasian Tapa na hih leh hih suangte anlum a suah nadingin thupia in,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 4 \x + \xo 4:4 \xt Joh 4:34\x*Ahih hangin Zeisu in, “\w Lai Siangtho\w* sungah, \qt ‘Mihing in an bek tawh a nungta hi loin Pasian kam panin a pusuak thu khempeuh tawh a nuntak ding ahi hi,’\qt*\f + \fr 4:4 \ft \+xt Thu 8:3\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* ci in kigelh hi,” ci in a dawng hi. 
\p 
\v 5 \x + \xo 4:5 \xt Neh 11:1; Dan 9:24\x*Tua khit ciangin Dawimangpa in khuapi siangtho sungah Zeisu lutpihin \w biakinnpi\w* khumdawn ah a koih hi. 
\v 6 Tua ciangin ama kiangah, “Pasian Tapa na hih leh lengkhiasuk in; banghang hiam cihleh, 
\b 
\q1 \qt ‘Amah in nang hong kem dingin,\qt* 
\q1 \qt Ama vantungmite thupia ding a,\qt* 
\q1 \qt Na khe le suang a kitah khak loh nadingin,\qt* 
\q1 \qt A khut uh tawh nang hong dom ding uh hi,’\qt*\f + \fr 4:6 \ft \+xt Lat 91:11-12\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* 
\m ci in \w Lai Siangtho\w* sungah kigelh hi,” a ci hi. 
\b 
\p 
\v 7 \x + \xo 4:7 \xt Rom 16:20; 2Co 2:11; 2Th 2:9; Kil 12:9\x*Zeisu in ama kiangah, “Lai Siangtho sungah, ‘\qt Topa na Pasian na ze-et kei ding hi,’\qt*\f + \fr 4:7 \ft \+xt Thu 6:16\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* ci in kigelh hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 8 Dawimangpa in mual sang mahmah khat dawn ah Zeisu paitohpih a, leitung kumpigam khempeuh le tuate thupina teng a vekpi in a lak hi. 
\v 9 Tua ciangin ama kiangah, “Bokin hong bia leteh hih na khempeuh kong pia ding hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 10 \x + \xo 4:10 \xt 1Kh 21:1; Job 1:6-9; Mak 4:15; Luk 10:18\x*Zeisu in ama kiangah, “\w Satan\w* aw, ka nungah kihemkhia in! \qt ‘Topa na Pasian na bia ding a, ama na bek na sem ding hi,’\qt*\f + \fr 4:10 \ft \+xt Thu 6:13\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* ci in Lai Siangtho sungah kigelh hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 11 \x + \xo 4:11 \xt Luk 22:43; Heb 1:14; Jam 4:7\x*Tua ciangin Dawimangpa in amah nusia a, en in, vantungmite hong pai in amah a kem uh hi. 
\s1 Zeisu Thuhilh Kipan 
\r Mak 1:14, 15; Luk 4:14, 15 
\p 
\v 12 Thong sungah John a kikhiatna thu Zeisu in a zak ciangin Galilee gam ah a pai hi. 
\v 13 \x + \xo 4:13 \xt Mak 1:21; Luk 4:23, 31; Joh 2:12\x*Nazareth khua nusia in \w Zebulun\w* le Naphtali gamnawl, tuilipi gei a om Capernaum khua ah a teeng hi. 
\v 14 Tua in kamsangpa Isaiah gensa thu a tangtun nading ahi hi. Amah in, 
\b 
\q1 
\v 15 \qt “Zebulun gam le Naphtali gamkete in,\qt* 
\q1 \qt Jordan Gun gal tuili zuatna lampidung ah om a,\qt* 
\q1 \qt Gentilete teenna,\qt* 
\q1 \qt Galilee gamhuam ahi hi.\qt* 
\q1 
\v 16 \x + \xo 4:16 \xt Luk 2:32; Joh 5:35\x*\qt Khuamial sunga tu tua mite in,\qt* 
\q1 \qt A tang mahmah khuavak mu uh a,\qt* 
\q1 \qt Sihna gam sung le sihna liim nuai a om,\qt* 
\q1 \qt Tua mite tungah,\qt* 
\q1 \qt Khuavak a tang ta hi,”\qt*\f + \fr 4:16 \ft \+xt Isa 9:1-2\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* 
\m a ci hi. 
\b 
\p 
\v 17 Tua hun a kipan Zeisu thuhilh kipan a, “Vantung kumpigam hong tung dekta ahih manin na mawhna uh kisikkik un,” a ci hi. 
\s1 Nungzui Masate Sapna 
\r Mak 1:16-20; Luk 5:1-11; Joh 1:35-51 
\p 
\v 18 \x + \xo 4:18 \xt Mak 7:31; Joh 6:1\x*Galilee tuili gei ah Zeisu a pai laitakin unau nih mu a, Peter a kici Simon le a sanggampa Andrew ahi hi. Amaute ngabeng mi ahih manun tuili ah ngen khuhin a om uh hi. 
\v 19 \x + \xo 4:19 \xt Mak 10:21, 28, 52; Luk 5:28; Joh 1:43\x*Tua ciangin amah in, “Ka nung hong zui un, note mi mante kong suaksak ding hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 20 Amaute in thakhatin a ngen uh nusia in Zeisu nung a zui uh hi. 
\p 
\v 21 \x + \xo 4:21 \xt Mak 3:17; Luk 8:51; Joh 21:2\x*Tua mun pan a paikhiat ciangin a dang unau nihte a mu hi. Amaute in Zebedee tapa James le a sanggampa John hi a, a pa uh Zebedee tawh gunkuang sungah ngen khui in a om uh hi. Amah in amaute a sap ciangin, 
\v 22 thakhatin a gunkuang le a pa uh nusia in amah a zui uh hi. 
\s1 Cinate Damsakna 
\r Mak 1:29-32; Luk 4:38-44 
\p 
\v 23 \x + \xo 4:23 \xt Mak 1:39; 3:10; Luk 4:15, 44; Joh 6:59; Saw 10:38; 20:25\x*Galilee gam sung tengah Zeisu vak kawikawi a, kikhopna innte ah thuhilh in kumpigam lungdamna thu a tangko hi. Amaute laka cinate le natna tuamtuam a nei khempeuh zong a damsak hi. 
\v 24 \x + \xo 4:24 \xt Mak 1:32; 2:3\x*Syria gam sung khempeuh ah a minthanna kizel in natna le zawngkhalna a tuamtuam a nei cina khempeuh le dawilutte, a sibup theite, pumzawte hong paipih uh a, amah in a damsak hi. 
\v 25 \x + \xo 4:25 \xt Mak 3:7; Luk 6:17\x*Galilee gam, \w Decapolis gam\w*, Jerusalem a kipan Judea gam le Jordan Gun gal panin hong pai mi honpi in amah a zui uh hi. 
\c 5 
\s1 Mual tung Thuhilhna 
\s2 Mi Hampha 
\r Luk 6:20-26 
\p 
\v 1 Zeisu in mi honpite a muh ciangin mual tung ah kahto in tu a, ama kiangah a nungzuite in hong naih uh hi. 
\v 2 Tua ciangin amah in thu a hilh in ah, 
\b 
\q1 
\v 3 “A lunggim mite in mi hampha ahi uh hi. 
\q1 Banghang hiam cihleh vantung kumpigam in amaute aa ahi hi. 
\q1 
\v 4 \x + \xo 5:4 \xt Isa 61:2-3; Kil 7:17\x*A dah a kapte in mi hampha ahi uh hi. 
\q1 Banghang hiam cihleh amaute in hehnepna a ngah ding uh hi. 
\q1 
\v 5 \x + \xo 5:5 \xt Lat 37:11; Rom 4:13\x*A lungnemte in mi hampha ahi uh hi. 
\q1 Banghang hiam cihleh amaute in leitung a luah ding uh hi. 
\q1 
\v 6 \x + \xo 5:6 \xt Isa 55:1-2\x*Gilkial dangtak banga dikna thu a lunggulhte in mi hampha ahi uh hi. 
\q1 Banghang hiam cihleh amaute a gilvah ding uh hi. 
\q1 
\v 7 \x + \xo 5:7 \xt Jam 2:13\x*Mi dang a hehpih theite in mi hampha ahi uh hi. 
\q1 Banghang hiam cihleh amaute in hehpihna a ngah ding uh hi. 
\q1 
\v 8 \x + \xo 5:8 \xt Heb 12:14; Kil 22:4\x*Lungsim siangthote in mi hampha ahi uh hi. 
\q1 Banghang hiam cihleh amaute in Pasian a mu ding uh hi. 
\q1 
\v 9 \x + \xo 5:9 \xt Rom 8:14; 14:19\x*Kilemna a bawlte in mi hampha ahi uh hi. 
\q1 Banghang hiam cihleh amaute in Pasian tate cihna a ngah ding uh hi. 
\q1 
\v 10 \x + \xo 5:10 \xt 1Pe 3:14\x*Dikna thu hanga bawlsiatna a thuakte in mi hampha ahi uh hi. 
\q1 Banghang hiam cihleh vantung kumpigam in amaute aa ahi hi. 
\b 
\p 
\v 11 \x + \xo 5:11 \xt Isa 51:7; Joh 15:21\x*“Keima hanga zahkona, bawlsiatna, a man lopi a mawhsakna namkim note in na thuak uh ciangin mi hampha na hi uh hi. 
\v 12 \x + \xo 5:12 \xt Saw 7:52; 2Co 6:10; Col 1:24; Jam 1:2; 1Pe 1:6\x*Vantung ah thaman lianpi sang ding na hih manun kipak unla lungdam mahmah un. Note ma a kamsangte zong tua bangin a bawlsia zo uh hi. 
\s2 Ci Le Khuavak 
\r Mak 4:21-23; 9:50; Luk 8:16-18; 11:33-36; 14:34-35 
\p 
\v 13 \x + \xo 5:13 \xt Mak 9:50; Luk 14:34\x*“Note in leitung mite aa dingin ci na hi uh hi. Ahih hangin ci pen al nawn keileh bangci bangin ki-alkiksak thei ding ahi hiam? Paikhia a mite tuatcil gawp ding longal a kimanna om lo hi. 
\p 
\v 14 \x + \xo 5:14 \xt Joh 8:12\x*“Note in leitung mite aa dingin khuavak na hi uh hi. Mual dawna om khua kiliah thei lo hi. 
\v 15 \x + \xo 5:15 \xt Mak 4:21; Luk 8:16\x*Kuamah in mei a vak khit ciangin seeng a khuh ngei kei hi. Inn sunga om mi khempeuh in khuavak a ngah theih nadingin meivak tunna tungah meivak a koih zaw uh hi. 
\v 16 \x + \xo 5:16 \xt 1Co 10:31; Phi 1:11; Tit 2:14\x*Tua mah bangin mite in note gamtat phate mu a, vana om na Pa uh a phat theih nadingun mite mai ah na khuavak uh na taangsak un. 
\s2 Thukham A Tangtunna 
\p 
\v 17 \x + \xo 5:17 \xt Joh 10:34; Rom 3:31\x*“Thukham ahi a, Kamsangte laibute ahi zongin a beisak dinga hong pai hong sa kei un. A beisak dinga hong pai hi loin a kicingsak dinga hong pai ka hi zaw hi. 
\p 
\v 18 \x + \xo 5:18 \xt Isa 40:8; Mak 13:31; Luk 16:17\x*“Note kiang a man takpi kong cihin ah, van le lei a mangthang zongin thukham khempeuh a tangtun khit mateng \w laimal neupen\w*\f + \fr 5:18 \fk laimal neu\ft : Greek iota; Greek laimal bul sunga a neu pen ahi hi.\f* khat ahi a, laimal them\f + \fr 5:18 \fk laimal them\ft : Sut vom, laimal tunga a kikui ciuciau khat genna hi.\f* khat nangawn ahi zongin a mangthang kei ding hi. 
\v 19 \x + \xo 5:19 \xt Jam 2:10\x*Tua ahih manin thupiakte lak panin a neupen khat nangawn palsat a, midangte zong a palsat dinga a hilh mi peuhmah vantung kumpigam sungah a neupen kici ding hi. Ahi zongin hih thupiaknate zui in midangte zong a zui dingin a hilh mi peuhmah vantung kumpigam sungah milian a kici ding hi. 
\v 20 \x + \xo 5:20 \xt Isa 26:2; Joh 3:5\x*Tua hi a, ken kong cih in ah note dikna in \w thukhamhilh siate\w* le \w Pharisee\w* pawlte dikna a khup zawh keileh vantung kumpigam sungah na lut thei kei ding uh hi. 
\s2 Mi Thahna 
\r Luk 12:58-59 
\p 
\v 21 “~\qt ‘Mi na that kei ding hi. Mi thatte in thukhenna thuak ding uh hi,’\qt*\f + \fr 5:21 \ft \+xt Pai 20:13; Thu 5:17\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* ci a, tanglai mite tunga a kigen thu na za zo uh hi. 
\v 22 \x + \xo 5:22 \xt Ths 7:9; Mak 9:43; Luk 16:24; 1Co 13:5; Eph 4:26; Jam 1:19-20\x*Ahih hangin note kiang ken kong cih in ah a sanggampa tungah a thu om lopi a a heh mi peuhmah in thukhenna a thuak ding lauhuai hi. A sanggampa kiangah, ‘Nang, \w mi gina lo\w*\f + \fr 5:22 \fk mi gina lo\ft : Greek raka; Aramaic pau hi in mi hai, bangmah thei lopa cihna hi in zahpihna kammal khauh ahi hi.\f*!’ a ci mi in zong thukhenna a thuak ding lauhuai hi. A sanggampa kiangah, ‘Nang, mi hai!’ a cite \w hell\w* meikuang sungah a kikhul ding lauhuai hi. 
\p 
\v 23 “\w Biaknatau\w* ah Pasian biak nading nate tawi a na om laitakin na sanggampa nang tungah lungkim lo hi ci a, na phawk leh, 
\v 24 Pasian na biak nading nate pen \w biaknatau\w* mai ah koihphot in ciahkik inla, na sanggampa tawh va kilem masa in. Tua khit ciangin paikik inla Pasian na biakna nate piapan in. 
\p 
\v 25 “Na langpa tawh thukhen zum zuana na pai laitakin kilem mengmeng in. Tua hi keileh amah in thukhenpa tungah hong khia in thukhenpa in palikte tungah hong ap ding a, palikte in thong sungah hong khum ding uh hi. 
\p 
\v 26 “A man takpi kong cihin ah, na liausum dangka na piak khit\f + \fr 5:26 \fk na liausum dangka na piak khit\ft : Greek kam in “a nunung pen kodrantes”; a nunga Vantehnate nuai ah “quadran” a kici en in.\f* matengin thong pan na suakta kei ding hi. 
\s2 Mi Zi Tawh Mawhna 
\r Mat 19:1-12; Mak 10:1-12; Luk 16:18 
\p 
\v 27 “~\qt ‘Ang na kawm kei ding hi,’\qt*\f + \fr 5:27 \ft \+xt Pai 20:14; Thu 5:18\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* ci a, tanglai mite tunga a kigen thu na za zo uh hi. 
\v 28 \x + \xo 5:28 \xt Pau 6:25; 2Pe 2:14\x*Ahih hangin note kiang ken kong cih in ah mawh nopna lungsim tawh numei khat a en mi peuhmah, tua numei tungah a lungsim mawh zo hi. 
\p 
\v 29 \x + \xo 5:29 \xt Mak 9:42-47; Luk 17:2; Rom 14:21; 1Co 8:13; 2Co 6:3\x*“Tua ahih manin na taklam mit in hong khialhsak leh khelkhia inla pai in; banghang hiam cihleh hell sungah na pumpi bupin hong kikhiat sangin na pumpi nate khat kisia leh a hoihzaw hi. 
\v 30 Na taklam khut in hong khialhsak leh sattan inla pai in. Na pumpi bupin hell sungah hong kikhiat sangin na pumpi nate khat kisia leh a hoihzaw hi. 
\s2 Kimakna 
\r Mat 19:3-10; Mak 10:2-12; Luk 16:18 
\p 
\v 31 \x + \xo 5:31 \xt Thu 24:1-4\x*“Tua banah, \qt ‘A zi a ma nuam mi peuhmah in, a zi tungah kimakna lai pia tahen,’\qt*\f + \fr 5:31 \ft \+xt Thu 24:1\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* a cihna thu na thei zo uh hi. 
\v 32 \x + \xo 5:32 \xt Luk 16:18\x*Ahih hangin note kiang ken kong cih in ah mi khatpeuh in pasal dang tawh a mawhna longal thu dang khatpeuh hangin a zi a mak leh, a zi mi dang tawh a mawh dingin a bawl ahi hi. A kimasa numei a teenpih mi peuhmah zong mi zi tawh a mawh ahi hi. 
\s2 Kiciamna 
\p 
\v 33 “Tua banah, \qt ‘A man lopi in na kiciam kei ding a, ahi zongin Topa tunga na kamciamte tangtungsak in,’\qt*\f + \fr 5:33 \ft \+xt Siam 19:12; Gam 30:2; Thu 23:21, 23\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* ci in tanglai mite tunga a kigen thu na thei zo uh hi. 
\v 34 \x + \xo 5:34 \xt Isa 66:1; Jam 5:12\x*Ahih hangin note kiang ken kong cih in ah na kiciam peuhmah kei un. Vantung in Pasian tokhom ahih manin vantung tawh kiciam kei un. 
\v 35 \x + \xo 5:35 \xt Lat 48:2\x*Leitung in ama khengakna ahih manin leitung tawh kiciam kei un. A lian Kumpipa khuapi ahi Jerusalem min tawh kiciam kei un. 
\v 36 Na lutang uh tawh zong kiciam kei in; banghang hiam cihleh na samzang khat na kangsak, na vomsak thei kei hi. 
\v 37 \x + \xo 5:37 \xt Joh 17:15; Eph 6:16; 2Th 3:3; Jam 5:12; 1Jn 2:13-14\x*Ahi thute, ‘Hi mah hi,’ ci unla, a hi lo thute, ‘Hi lo hi,’ ci un. Hih zah val in a tam zawk leh gilopa kiang panin a hong piang ahi hi. 
\s2 Thukkik Kei Un 
\r Luk 6:29-30 
\p 
\v 38 “~\qt ‘Mit tang khat tangin mit tang khat, ha tang khat tangin ha tang khat,’\qt*\f + \fr 5:38 \ft \+xt Pai 21:24; Siam 24:20; Thu 19:21\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* a cihna thu na za zo uh hi. 
\v 39 \x + \xo 5:39 \xt Luk 6:28; Rom 12:17, 19; 1Pe 3:9\x*Ahih hangin ken kong cih in ah mi gilopa na dokik kei un. Mi khatpeuh in na pang taklam hong bet leh a langkhat zong na dawh in. 
\v 40 Mi khatpeuh in na puanak hong suh nop manin zum ah hong khiat sawm leh na puan tungsilh zong na piak beh in. 
\v 41 Zawhthawhthu tawh \w tai\w* khat hong paipih nuamte, tai nih dong na zui in. 
\v 42 \x + \xo 5:42 \xt Thu 15:8; Luk 6:30\x*Hong ngente na pia in. Hong leitawi nuamte na nungngat kei in. 
\s2 Galte Itna 
\r Luk 6:27-36 
\p 
\v 43 \x + \xo 5:43 \xt Lat 139:21-22; Mak 12:31; Luk 10:27; Rom 13:9; Gal 5:14; Jam 2:8\x*“~\qt ‘Na vengte it inla, na galte mudah in,’\qt*\f + \fr 5:43 \ft \+xt Siam 19:18\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* cih thu na za zo uh hi. 
\v 44 \x + \xo 5:44 \xt Luk 6:27-28; Joh 15:20; Saw 7:60; Rom 8:35; 1Co 4:12; 1Pe 2:23\x*Ahi zongin ken kong cih in ah na galte na it un. Hong samsiate thupha na pia un. Hong mudahte tungah thupha na bawl un. A hong simmawh mite le hong bawlsia mite aa dingin thu na ngetsak un. 
\v 45 \x + \xo 5:45 \xt Job 25:3; Luk 6:35; Rom 8:14\x*Tua hi leh vana om na Pa uh tate na hi taktak ding uh hi; banghang hiam cihleh amah in mi hoih lote le mi hoihte tungah a kibangin ama ni suaksak a, mi dikte le mi dik lote tungah guah zong a zusak tuak hi. 
\v 46 \x + \xo 5:46 \xt Luk 6:32\x*Hong itte bek it le uh teh, bang lemlawh tuam ding na hi uh hiam? \w Siahdongte\w* nangawn in zong amau a itte it uh hi lo ahi hiam? 
\v 47 Na lawmte bek maitai le uh teh, midangte sangin na hoih zawkna uh bang om tuan ding ahi hiam? Siahdongte nangawn in zong tua bangmah in hih uh hi lo ahi hiam? 
\v 48 \x + \xo 5:48 \xt Siam 19:2; 1Pe 1:16\x*Tua ahih ciangin vana om na Pa uh a hoihkim bangin note zong na hoihkim un,” a ci hi. 
\c 6 
\s2 A Kitangsam Mite Piakna 
\p 
\v 1 “Na hoih na sep uh ciangin mite muh theih theih dingin na hih khak loh nadingun kidawm un. Tua hi keileh vantung a om na Pa un thaman a hong pia kei ding hi. 
\p 
\v 2 “Tua ahih manin a kitangsam mite huhna na piak uh ciangin a kineihkhem mite piak bangin pia kei un. Amaute in midangte pahtak ding lametna tawh kongzing lak le kikhopna innte ah pengkul tumkawmsa in a pia uh hi. A man takpi kong cihin ah, amaute in thaman a ngah zo uh hi. 
\v 3 Ahi zongin note in a kitangsam mite huhna na piak uh ciangin na taklam khut tawh na piakte uh na veilam khut theisak kei un. 
\v 4 \x + \xo 6:4 \xt Col 3:23-24\x*Tua hi leh a kitangsam mite na huhnate uh kilangkhia lo dinga a kilang lote a mu na Pa un a kilangtang in thaman hong pia ding hi. 
\s2 Thunget Zia Ding Hilhna 
\r Luk 11:1-4 
\p 
\v 5 \x + \xo 6:5 \xt Mak 11:25; Luk 18:10-14\x*“Thu na nget uh ciangin zong a kineihkhem mite hih bangin hih kei un. Amaute in mite muh theih theih dingin kikhopna innte le lamkabom khawng ah ding a, thunget ding a ut uh hi. A man takpi kong cihin ah, amaute in thaman a ngah zo uh hi. 
\v 6 \x + \xo 6:6 \xt 2Ku 4:33\x*Note in thu na nget uh ciangin inndei sungah lut unla kong na khak khit uh ciangin a kilang lo a om na Pa uh kiangah ngen un. Tua hi leh a kilang lote a mu na Pa un a kilangtang in thaman hong pia ding hi. 
\v 7 \x + \xo 6:7 \xt 1Ku 18:26-29; Ths 5:2\x*Thu na nget uh ciangin lawkite bangin na gen sasa uh gen phapha kei un. Amaute in gen pha kikkik le uh a ngahdeuh ding kisa uh hi. 
\v 8 Tua ahih manin amaute bang hi kei un; banghang hiam cihleh na Pa un na kisapnate uh na nget ma un a thei khinzo hi. 
\p 
\v 9 \x + \xo 6:9 \xt Jer 3:19; Mal 2:10; 1Pe 1:17\x*“Tua ahih manin hih bangin thu na ngen un, 
\b 
\q1 Vantung a om kote Pa aw, 
\q1 Na min siangtho kizahtak hen. 
\q1 
\v 10 Na kumpigam hong piang tahen. 
\q1 Vantung ah na deihna a kisep mah bangin, 
\q1 Leitung ah zong kisem tahen. 
\q1 
\v 11 \x + \xo 6:11 \xt Pau 30:8\x*Tuni a ka nek ding uh an hong pia in. 
\q1 
\v 12 Ko tunga hong khialte ka maisak uh bangin, 
\q1 Kote khialhna zong hong maisak ta in. 
\q1 
\v 13 \x + \xo 6:13 \xt Jam 1:13\x*Ze-etna sungah hong lutsak kei inla, 
\q1 Gilopa kiang panin hong honkhia in. 
\q1 Banghang hiam cihleh ukzawhna, 
\q1 Vangliatna le minthanna, 
\q1 Nang aa ahi tawntung hi. \w Amen\w*. 
\b 
\p 
\v 14 \x + \xo 6:14 \xt Mak 11:25-26; Eph 4:32; Col 3:13\x*“Mite khialhnate na maisak uh leh vantunga om na Pa un zong note khialhnate hong maisak ding hi. 
\v 15 Mite khialhnate na maisak kei uh leh na Pa un zong note khialhna hong maisak lo ding hi. 
\s2 Antanna 
\p 
\v 16 \x + \xo 6:16 \xt Siam 16:29, 31; Gam 24:7; Isa 58:5; Zec 7:5\x*“Tua banah an na tan uh ciangin, a kineihkhem mite bangin na mai uh vulsak kei un; banghang hiam cihleh amaute in antang ahihna uh mite mai ah a kilat theih nadingin a maipuak uh a khel uh hi. A man takpi kong cihin ah, amaute in thaman a ngah zo uh hi. 
\v 17 Ahi zongin note in an na tan uh ciangin na lu uh sathau nilh unla na mai uh phiat un. 
\v 18 Tua hi leh na antan lam uh mite mai ah kilang lo ding a, a kilang lo a om na Pa uh mai bekah a kilang ding hi. Tua ciangin a kilang lote a mu na Pa un a kilangtang in thaman a hong pia ding hi. 
\s2 Vantung Ah Sumkhol Un 
\r Luk 12:33-36 
\p 
\v 19 \x + \xo 6:19 \xt Pau 23:4; Luk 12:16-21; Heb 13:5; Jam 5:2-3\x*“Na sum na paite uh nget in a nek theihna, a kekseu theihna le gutate in luh in a guk theihna hih leitung ah khol kei un. 
\v 20 \x + \xo 6:20 \xt Luk 12:33; 1Ti 6:19\x*Nget in a nek theih lohna, a kekseu theih lohna, gutate in luhin a guk theih lohna vantung ah khol zaw un. 
\v 21 \x + \xo 6:21 \xt Luk 12:34\x*Banghang hiam cihleh na sum omna munah na lungsim uh zong a om ding hi. 
\p 
\v 22 “Mittang in pumpi aa dingin meivak ahi hi. Tua ahih manin na mit a ciim leh na pumpi bup a vak ding hi. 
\v 23 Ahih hangin na mit a mial leh na pumpi bup a mial ding hi. Tua ahih manin na sunga om khuavak pen khuamial hi leh a nak mial mahmah ding hi. 
\p 
\v 24 \x + \xo 6:24 \xt Luk 16:13\x*“Kuamah in to nih na semkhawm thei lo hi; banghang hiam cihleh khat mudah in khat a it ding hi. Ahih keileh khat thupi simin khat a simmawh ding hi. Pasian na le leitung na na semkhawm thei kei ding uh hi. 
\s2 Lunghimawh Kei Un 
\r Luk 12:22-31 
\p 
\v 25 \x + \xo 6:25 \xt Luk 10:41\x*“Tua ahih manin note kianga kong cihin ah, bang ne in bang dawn ding ka hi hiam ci in na nuntakna aa dingun lunghimawh kei un. Bang silh in bang teeng ding ka hi hiam ci in na pumpi aa dingun lunghimawh kei un. Nek le tak sangin nuntakna thupi zaw a, silh le teen sangin pumpi thupi zaw hi lo ahi hiam? 
\v 26 \x + \xo 6:26 \xt Job 38:41; Lat 104:21\x*Vana leng vasate en dih un. Amaute in khaici tuh loin, an la lo uh a, bem le salah zong an a khol kei uh hi. Ahi zongin, vantunga om na Pa un amaute an a vak hi. Vasate sangin manpha zaw hi lo na hi uh hiam? 
\v 27 \x + \xo 6:27 \xt Lat 39:5\x*Na lunghimawh manun na tun uh tong khat nangawn a behlap thei kua om na hi uh hiam? 
\p 
\v 28 “Tua ahih leh banghang in puansilh ding lunghimawh na hi uh hiam? Gamlak a unokpakte khankhiat zia ngaihsun dih un. Amaute in na sem loin khau zong khek lo uh hi. 
\v 29 \x + \xo 6:29 \xt 1Ku 10:4-7\x*Ahih hangin ken kong cih in ah Solomon in a minthanna khempeuh tawh kizem a a om laitak nangawn in hih pakte khat zahin hoih zo nai lo uh hi. 
\v 30 \x + \xo 6:30 \xt Luk 12:28\x*Upna neu mite aw, tuni in om a zingciang in meikhuk ah a kikhul ding gamlak a pakte nangawn Pasian in tua bangin puansilh guan ahih leh note hong limguat zawkan ding hi lo ahi hiam? 
\v 31 Tua ahih manin, ‘Bang ka ne ding a, bang ka dawn ding hiam, bang silh dinga bang teeng ding ka hi hiam?’ ci in lunghimawh kei un. 
\v 32 Gentilete in hih nate khempeuh a zonpi pen uh ahi hi. Vantunga om na Pa un hih na khempeuh na kisap lam uh hong thei hi. 
\v 33 \x + \xo 6:33 \xt Lat 37:4\x*Tua ahih manin Pasian kumpigam le ama dikna zong masa un. Tua hi leh hih nate khempeuh hong kipiakthuah ding hi. 
\v 34 Tua ahih manin zingciang aa dingin lunghimawh khol kei un; banghang hiam cihleh zingciang vai ding zingciang mahin hong lunghimawh ding hi. Tuni a lungkhamna pen tuni aa dingin kicing khin hi. 
\c 7 
\s2 Midangte Tungah Thukhenna 
\r Luk 6:37-42 
\p 
\v 1 \x + \xo 7:1 \xt Luk 6:37; Rom 14:4; 1Co 4:5; Jam 4:11-12\x*“Thukhenna na thuak loh nadingun midangte tungah thu na khen kei un. 
\v 2 \x + \xo 7:2 \xt Eze 35:11; Mak 4:24; Luk 6:38; Rom 2:1\x*Banghang hiam cihleh midangte tunga thu na khen bangun no tungah zong thu hong kikhen ding hi. Note zat tehna tektek mah tawh note aa dingin a hong kitehsakkik ding hi. 
\p 
\v 3 “Nangma mita singluang phawk kha loin banghang in na sanggampa mita ninthem muhsak na hi hiam? 
\v 4 Ngaihsun dih in na mit ah singluang khat om napi banghang in na sanggampa kiangah, ‘Na mita ninthem hong lakkhiatsak ning,’ ci thei na hi hiam? 
\v 5 A kineihkhem mipa aw! Nangma mita singluang lakhia masa in. Tua hi leh na sanggampa mita ninthem telmuh in na lakkhiatsak thei pan ding hi. 
\p 
\v 6 “A siangtho nate uite pia kei un. Kepsuangmanphate zong vokpi mai ah lot kha kei un. Na lot khak leh a khe tawh tuangawp in kihei in nang a hong petgawp ding hi. 
\s1 Ngetna, Zonna, Kiuhna 
\r Luk 11:9-13 
\p 
\v 7 \x + \xo 7:7 \xt 1Ku 3:5; Joh 14:13-14; Jam 1:5-8; 1Jn 3:22\x*“Ngen un, hong kipia ding hi. Zong un, na mu ding uh hi. Kiu un, hong kihon ding hi. 
\v 8 \x + \xo 7:8 \xt Pau 8:17; Jer 29:12-13\x*Banghang hiam cihleh a ngente in ngah a, a zongte in mu in, a kiute kong kihon ding hi. 
\p 
\v 9 “Note lakah a ta in anlum ngen leh suang a pia ding, 
\v 10 ngasa ngen leh gul a pia ding kua om na hi uh hiam? 
\v 11 \x + \xo 7:11 \xt Jam 1:17\x*No mi hoih lote nangawn in na tate uh na hoih piak ding thei na hih uh leh vana om na Pa un ama kianga a ngente na hoih hong pia zaw tham lo ding ahi hiam! 
\v 12 \x + \xo 7:12 \xt Luk 6:31; Rom 13:8-10; Gal 5:14\x*Tua ahih manin note tunga hong kibawl dinga na deih khempeuh uh midangte tungah zong na bawl un. Thukham le Kamsangte laibute zong hih thu mah ahi hi. 
\s2 Kong Kawcik 
\r Luk 13:24 
\p 
\v 13 \x + \xo 7:13 \xt Luk 13:24; Joh 10:7, 9\x*“Kong kawcik ah lut un; banghang hiam cihleh siatna mun tun nading kongpi zai a, lampi zong tanzau ahih manin mi tampi in tua lampi a tawn uh hi. 
\v 14 Nuntakna mun tun nading kong kawcik a, lampi zong neu ahih manin mi tawmcik bekin a zui uh hi. 
\s2 Singkung Le A Gah 
\r Mat 12:33-37; Luk 6:43-45 
\p 
\v 15 \x + \xo 7:15 \xt Jer 23:16; Luk 6:26; Saw 20:29; 2Pe 2:1; 1Jn 4:1; Kil 16:13\x*“A lungsim tawng uh ngia bangin gilo napi tuuvun silh a, note kianga a hong pai kamsang zuaute na kidawm un. 
\v 16 \x + \xo 7:16 \xt Luk 6:44; Jam 3:12\x*Amaute bangci mi hiam cih a gah panun na thei ding uh hi. Lingkung panin lenggah kilo thei ahi hiam? Thangling kung panin theigah kilo thei ahi hiam? 
\v 17 Tua ahih manin singkung hoih peuhmah in a gah hoih a, singkung hoih keileh a gah zong a hoih kei hi. 
\v 18 \x + \xo 7:18 \xt Luk 6:43\x*Singkung hoihin gah hoih lo gah thei lo a, singkung hoih loin gah hoih a gah thei kei hi. 
\v 19 Gah hoih a gah lo singkung khempeuh kiphuk in meikuang sungah kikhul ding hi. 
\v 20 Tua ahih manin amaute bangci mi hiam cih a gah panun na thei ding uh hi. 
\p 
\v 21 \x + \xo 7:21 \xt Hos 8:2; Joh 13:13; Rom 2:13; Jam 1:22; 1Jn 3:18\x*“~‘Topa aw, Topa aw,’ hong ci peuhmah vantung kumpigam sungah a lutkim kei ding uh hi. Vana ka Pa deih banga a gamtate bek a lut ding uh hi. 
\v 22 \x + \xo 7:22 \xt Luk 10:20; 1Co 13:1-3\x*Tua ni ciangin mi tampi in, ‘Topa aw, Topa aw, nangma min tawh kamsang in thugen hi lo ka hi uh hiam? Nangma min tawh dawite hawlkhia in, nangma min tawh nalamdang bawl hi lo ka hi uh hiam?’ hong ci ding uh hi. 
\v 23 \x + \xo 7:23 \xt Lat 6:8; Luk 13:25-27\x*Tua ciangin, ‘Note kong thei kei hi. Siatna a bawl mite aw, ka kiang panin paikhia un!’ ka ci ding hi. 
\s2 Innlam Mi Nihte 
\r Luk 6:47-49 
\p 
\v 24 \x + \xo 7:24 \xt Jam 1:22-25\x*“Tua ahih manin hih ka thugente za a a zui mi khatpeuh in suangpi tunga innlam mi pilpa tawh kibang hi ci in ka gen ding hi. 
\v 25 Guahzu in tui hong khang a, huihpi nungin tua inn a nawk hangin suangpi tungah kilam ahih manin a puk kei hi. 
\v 26 Hih ka thugente za napi in a zui lo mi in, sehnel tunga innlam mi haipa tawh kibang hi ci in ka gen ding hi. 
\v 27 Guahzu in tui hong khang a, huihpi nungin tua inn a nawk ciangin a puk hi. Tua pukna in a lian mahmah pukna ahi hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 28 \x + \xo 7:28 \xt Mak 1:22; Luk 4:32; Joh 7:46\x*Zeisu in hih thute a gen khit ciangin mi honpite in a thuhilhna lamdang a sa mahmah uh hi. 
\v 29 Banghang hiam cihleh \w thukhamhilh siate\w* bangin hilh loin thuneipa bangin a hilh hi. 
\c 8 
\s1 Miphak Khat 
\r Mak 1:40-45; Luk 5:12-16 
\p 
\v 1 Zeisu mual tung pan hong kumsuk khit ciangin mi honpite in amah a zui uh hi. 
\v 2 \x + \xo 8:2 \xt Siam 13:45; Luk 5:12\x*Tua ciangin, en in, miphak khat hong pai in amah bia a, “Topa aw, hong damsak nuam lecin nong damsak thei hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 3 Zeisu in a khut zanin amah lawng a, “Kong damsak nuam hi, damta in,” ci a, thu a piak ciangin thakhatin a dam pah hi. 
\v 4 \x + \xo 8:4 \xt Siam 14:2-32; Mak 5:43; Luk 4:41; 17:14\x*Tua ciangin Zeisu in ama kiangah, “Hih thu kuama kiangah gen kei in. Ahi zongin pai inla siampipa kiangah va kilak in. Amaute tungah teci ahi dingin Moses hong thupiakna bangin biakpiakna khat va pia in,” a ci hi. 
\s1 Galkap 100 Ukpa Upna 
\r Luk 7:1-10; Joh 4:34-54 
\p 
\v 5 Capernaum khua ah Zeisu a lut ciangin galkap 100 ukpa khat hong pai in thum a, 
\v 6 “Topa aw, ka inn ah ka nasempa a pumzaw in lumcip a, genthei mahmah hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 7 Zeisu in ama kiangah, “Hong pai in amah ka damsak ding hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 8 \x + \xo 8:8 \xt Lat 107:20\x*Tua ciangin galkap 100 ukpa in dawngkik a, “Topa aw, ka inn sunga nong lut ding ka kilawm kei hi. Thu pia ziau leteh ka nasempa a dam ding hi. 
\v 9 Banghang hiam cihleh kei zong mi khutnuai a om khat ka hi a, ka khutnuai ah zong galkapte a om uh hi. Amaute khat kiangah, ‘Pai in,’ ka cih ciangin pai a, a dang khat kiangah, ‘Hong pai in,’ ka cih ciangin a hong pai hi. Ka nasempa kiangah, ‘Hih sem in,’ ka cih ciangin a sem hi,” a cisak hi. 
\p 
\v 10 Zeisu in tua thu a zak ciangin lamdangsa mahmah a, amah a zui mite kiangah, “Note kiang ken kong cih in ah Israelte sung nangawn ah hi zah a a lian upna ka mu kei hi! 
\v 11 \x + \xo 8:11 \xt Lat 107:3; Isa 49:12; Mal 1:11; Luk 13:29\x*Ken kong cih in ah nisuahna le nitumna lam panin mi tampi hong pai in Abraham, Isaac le Jacobte tawh vantung kumpigam sungah a tukhawm ding uh hi. 
\v 12 \x + \xo 8:12 \xt Luk 13:28\x*Ahi zongin tua kumpigam tate ahih leh a pualam khuamial lakah a lawnkhia ding hi. Tua munah kahna leh hagawina a om ding hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 13 Tua khit ciangin Zeisu in galkap 100 ukpa kiangah, “Ciahkik in. Na upna bangin nang aa dingin piang tahen,” a ci hi. Tua hun lian mahin a nasempa a dam hi. 
\s1 Zeisu In Peter Sunghnu Damsak 
\r Mak 1:29-31; Luk 4:38-39 
\p 
\v 14 Tua khit ciangin Peter inn ah Zeisu hong hawh in Peter sunghnu nattun in lupna tunga lum a mu hi. 
\v 15 Amah in tua nu khut a lawn ciangin a natna dam a, tho in amaute zin a do pah hi. 
\s1 Zeisu In Mi Tampi Kidamsak 
\r Mak 1:32-34; Luk 4:40-41 
\p 
\v 16 Nitak lam ciangin dawilut mi tampi Zeisu kiangah hong paipih uh a, tua dawite kam khat pauna bek tawh a hawlkhia ziau hi. Cina khempeuh zong a damsak hi. 
\v 17 Hih thu pen kamsangpa Isaiah in, 
\b 
\q1 \qt “Amah in i zawngkhalna teng lakhia in, i cinatna teng a pua hi,”\qt*\f + \fr 8:17 \ft \+xt Isa 53:4\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* 
\m ci a, a gensa thu a tangtunna ahi hi. 
\s1 Zeisu Nungzui Dingte 
\r Luk 9:57-62 
\p 
\v 18 \x + \xo 8:18 \xt Mak 4:35\x*Zeisu in ama kima om mi honpite a muh ciangin galkhat lamah galkah dingin a nungzuite thu a pia hi. 
\v 19 Tua laitakin \w thukhamhilh siate\w* khat ama kiangah hong pai a, “Sia aw, na paina peuhah kong zui ding hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 20 \x + \xo 8:20 \xt Dan 7:13; Mak 2:10\x*Zeisu in ama kiangah, “Ngiate in kua nei uh a, vana leng vasate in zong bu a nei uh hi. Ahih hangin \w Mihing Tapa\w* in a lutang ngakh nading mun a nei kei hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 21 Tua khit ciangin ama nungzuite khat in, “Topa aw, ka pa vui dingin hong paisak masa phot in,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 22 Ahih hangin Zeisu in ama kiangah, “Hong zui in. Misi pen misite mahin na vui uh hen,” a ci hi. 
\s1 Zeisu In Huihpi Daisak 
\r Mak 4:36-41; Luk 8:22-25 
\p 
\v 23 Gunkuang sungah amah a kahtoh ciangin a nungzuite in zong a zui uh hi. 
\v 24 Tua ciangin tuilipi tungah thakhatin huih khauh mahmah hong nung a, tuihual in gunkuang a tum dekdek hi. Zeisu ahih leh a ihmu hi. 
\v 25 A nungzuite ama kiangah pai in phong uh a, “Topa aw, a simang khin ding ka hita uh hi, hong hon in!” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 26 \x + \xo 8:26 \xt Lat 65:7; 107:29\x*Zeisu in, “Upna neu mite aw, banghang in hi zahtakin lau zawzen na hi uh hiam?” a cih khit ciangin tho a, huihpi le tuihual a taii leh a dai pah hi. 
\p 
\v 27 Amaute in lamdangsa mahmah uh a, “Hihpa bangci bang mi hi zawzen ahi hiam? Huihpi le tuihualte nangawn in ama thu a mang tazen uh hi,” a ci uh hi. 
\s1 Dawilut Mi Nih Kidamsak 
\r Mak 5:1-20; Luk 8:26-39 
\p 
\v 28 Zeisu tuilipi galkhat a om Gergesa mite teenna kuam a tun ciangin dawilut mi nih han pan hong paikhia uh a, amah a na dawntuah uh hi. Amaute gilo in gamhtat mahmah uh ahih manin kuamah in tua lampi a tawn ngam kei uh hi. 
\v 29 \x + \xo 8:29 \xt Thuk 11:12; 2Sa 16:10; 1Ku 17:18; Mak 1:24; Joh 2:4; 2Pe 2:4\x*Amaute thakhatin awng uh a, “Pasian Tapa Zeisu aw, nang tawh ka kisaina uh bang om ahi hiam? A hun tung nai lopi in kote bawlsia dinga hong pai na hi hiam?” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 30 Amaute tawh a kigamla simsim ah vok honpi gamta in a om hi. 
\v 31 Dawite in ama kiangah, “Nong hawlkhiat leh hualai a vok honte sungah hong lutsak in,” ci in a thum uh hi. 
\p 
\v 32 Tua ciangin Zeisu in, “Pai un,” ci in thupia a, tua dawite paikhia in vok honte sungah a lut uh hi. Thakhat thu mahin vok hon khempeuh ken lakah taiphialsuk uh a, tuilipi sung kidenna in a si khin uh hi. 
\v 33 Vok cingte tai pah vingveng uh a, dawilut mite tunga thupiang khempeuh khua sungah a va gen uh hi. 
\p 
\v 34 \x + \xo 8:34 \xt Luk 5:8; Saw 16:39\x*Tua ciangin tua khua mite a khuazang un Zeisu en dingin hong paikhia uh a, a muh uh ciangin amau gam panin a paikhiat nading a ngen uh hi. 
\c 9
\s1 Pumzaw Mi Khat Kidamsak
\r Mak 2:1-12; Luk 5:17-26
\p
\v 1 Tua ciangin Zeisu gunkuang tuangin galkah a, ama khua a tung hi.
\v 2 \x + \xo 9:2 \xt Luk 7:48; Joh 16:33\x*Tua leh, en in, pumzaw mi khat a lupna tawh zawngin ama kiangah hong paipih uh hi. Zeisu in amaute upna a muh ciangin pumzawpa kiangah, “Ka ta aw, lungnuam in na mawhnate hong kimaisak zo hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 3 \x + \xo 9:3 \xt Joh 10:33\x*Tua thu a zak phetun \w thukhamhilh siate\w* pawlkhat in a lungsim uhah, “Hihpa Pasian tungah a pausia hi!” a ci pah uh hi.
\p
\v 4 \x + \xo 9:4 \xt Lat 94:11; Luk 6:8; Joh 2:25\x*Zeisu in amaute ngaihsutna thei ahih manin, “Banghang in note lungsim sungah thusia ngaihsun na hi uh hiam?
\v 5 ‘Na mawhnate hong kimaisak zo hi,’ cih ding le, ‘Tho inla lampai in,’ cih ding koi baih zaw ahi hiam?
\v 6 Ahi zongin \w Mihing Tapa\w* in leitung ah mawhmaisak theihna thuneihna a neih lam na theih nadingun,” a cih khit ciangin pumzawpa kiangah, “Tho in, na lupna pua inla, na inn ah ciah in,” a ci hi.
\v 7 Tua pa zong tho in a inn ah a ciah hi.
\p
\v 8 \x + \xo 9:8 \xt Luk 7:16; Joh 15:8; Saw 4:21\x*Mi honpite in hih thupiang a muh uh ciangin, lamdangsa mahmah uh a, mihingte tungah tua bang vangliatna a pia Pasian a phat uh hi.
\s1 Zeisu In Matthew Sam
\r Mak 2:13-17; Luk 5:27-32
\p
\v 9 Tua mun panin Zeisu paisuak a, siahdonna buuk sunga a tu Matthew kici mi khat a muh ciangin, “Hong zui in,” a ci hi. Matthew zong dingkhia in Zeisu a zui hi.
\p
\v 10 Inn sungah Zeisu an ne in a tut laitak, en in, \w siahdongte\w* le mawhneite tampitak hong pai in Zeisu le a nungzuite tawh ankuang a umkhawm uh hi.
\v 11 \x + \xo 9:11 \xt Luk 5:30; Gal 2:15\x*\w Pharisee\w* pawlte in a muh uh ciangin a nungzuite kiangah, “Banghang in na siapa un siahdongte le mawhneite tawh an nekhawm ahi hiam?” a ci uh hi.
\p
\v 12 Tua thu a zak ciangin Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Cidamte aa dingin siavuan kisam lo a, cinate aa ding bekin kisam hi.
\v 13 \x + \xo 9:13 \xt Mic 6:6-8; Luk 19:10; 1Ti 1:15\x*Ahih hangin va pai unla, \qt ‘Gangawh biakna sangin hehpihna ka deih zaw hi,’\qt*\f + \fr 9:13 \ft \+xt Hos 6:6\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* a cihna thu a khiatna va kantel phot un; banghang hiam cihleh mi dikte sam dinga hong pai ka hi kei hi. Mawhneite a kisikkik theih nadingun a sam dinga hong pai ka hi hi,” a ci hi.
\s1 Antanna Thu
\r Mak 2:18-22; Luk 5:33-39
\p
\v 14 \x + \xo 9:14 \xt Luk 18:12\x*Tua khit ciangin John nungzuite a kiangah hong pai uh a, “Kote le Phariseete in an ka tang zelzel uh hi; banghang in na nungzuite in antang lo uh ahi hiam?” a ci uh hi.
\p
\v 15 \x + \xo 9:15 \xt Joh 3:29; Saw 13:2-3\x*Tua ciangin Zeisu in, “Zineipa tawh a omkhop sungun a lawm a gualte thum le tau in ombuang ding uh ahi hiam? Ahih hangin amaute kiang pan zineipa a kilakkhiat hun hong tung ding a, tua ciangin bel an a tang ding uh hi.
\p
\v 16 “Puan lui a kiphop ciangin kuamah in a ton nai lo puanbek a thak tawh a phop kei hi. Tua bangin phop leh a phopna puanbek a thak in puan lui kaikek in, a kekna a zai semsem ding hi.
\v 17 Kuamah in savun um lui sungah lenggahzu thak a thun kei hi. Tua bangin kithun leh savun um puakkham in lenggahzu teng luangkhia ding a, savun um zong a kisia ding hi. Lenggahzu thakte savun um thak sung mahah a kithun hi. Tua hi leh a nih tuakin bitkhawm in sawtveipi kikoih thei hi,” a ci hi.
\s1 Numeino Hinkikna Le Siluang Numei Damna
\r Mak 5:21-43; Luk 8:40-56
\p
\v 18 \x + \xo 9:18 \xt Mak 5:23\x*Hih thute a gengen laitakin, en in, makaipa khat hong pai in amah bia a, “Ka tanu tu mahmahin a si hi. Ahi zongin nang hong pai in a tungah na khut nga leteh a hing ding hi,” a ci hi.
\v 19 Zeisu dingkhia in amah zui a, a nungzuite in zong a zui uh hi.
\p
\v 20 \x + \xo 9:20 \xt Mak 3:10; Luk 6:19\x*Tua laitakin kum sawm le kum nih sung siluang natna a vei numei khat in Zeisu nung lam pan zuanin a puanmongtep thakhatin a va lawng hi.
\v 21 Amah in a lungsim sungah, “A puan va lawng beek leng zong ka dam ding hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 22 \x + \xo 9:22 \xt Mak 10:52; Luk 7:50; Joh 16:33\x*Zeisu a nung lam ah kihei a, amah a muh ciangin, “Ka tanu aw, lungnuam in, na upna in hong damsak zo hi,” a ci hi. Tua hun lian mahin tua numei a dam hi.
\p
\v 23 \x + \xo 9:23 \xt 2Kh 35:25; Jer 9:17-18\x*Makaipa inn sungah Zeisu a lut ciangin tamngai tumte le kap a gamlum ngeingai mi honpi a mu hi.
\v 24 \x + \xo 9:24 \xt Lat 76:5; Dan 12:2; Joh 11:11-14; Saw 20:10; 1Co 11:30; 1Th 4:13-16\x*Tua ciangin amah in tua mite kiangah, “Na awn un. Numeino a si hi loin a ihmu ahi hi,” a cih leh amaute in zahpihin a nuihsan uh hi.
\v 25 \x + \xo 9:25 \xt Luk 7:14\x*Ahih hangin Zeisu in mi honpi a pusuahsak khit ciangin inn sungah lut a, numeino khut a let ciangin numeino a tho hi.
\v 26 \x + \xo 9:26 \xt Mak 1:28; Luk 4:14, 37\x*Hih thu tua gam mun khempeuh ah a kizel hi.
\s1 Mittaw Nih In Khua Mukik
\p
\v 27 \x + \xo 9:27 \xt Mak 10:47\x*Tua mun pan Zeisu a paikhiat ciangin, mittaw nih in amah zui uh a, “David Tapa aw, kote hong hehpih in!” ci in a kiko uh hi.
\p
\v 28 \x + \xo 9:28 \xt Saw 14:9\x*Inn sungah amah a lut ciangin, mittaw nihte in zong a zui uh hi. Tua ciangin Zeisu in, “Na mit uh a vaksak thei dingin nong um uh hiam?” ci in dong a, amaute in, “Kong um uh hi Topa aw,” a ci uh hi.
\p
\v 29 Tua ciangin amah in a mit uh lawnsak a, “Na upna bangun, note tungah hong piang tahen,” a cih leh,
\v 30 a mit uh kihong pah hi. Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Hih thu kuamah theisak peuhmah kei un,” ci in khauhtakin thu a pia hi.
\v 31 \x + \xo 9:31 \xt Mak 7:36\x*Ahih hangin amaute paikhia uh a, tua gam sung khempeuh ah ama thu a kizelsak uh hi.
\s1 Pauthei Lo Khat Pau
\p
\v 32 Tua mi nihte a paikhiat laitak mah un, en in, a pauthei lo dawilut mi khat ama kiangah hong paipih uh hi.
\v 33 \x + \xo 9:33 \xt Mak 2:12\x*Amah in dawi a hawlkhiat ciangin, a pauthei lo pa hong pauthei pah hi. Mi honpi in lamdangsa mahmah uh a, “Israelte lakah hih bang i mu ngei kei hi!” a ci uh hi.
\p
\v 34 Ahih hangin, Phariseete in, “Amah in dawi mangpipa min suangin dawite a hawlkhia ahi hi,” a ci uh hi.
\s1 Nasem Ding Tawmlua
\p
\v 35 Tua bangin khuapi khuata kici tengah Zeisu zin kawikawi in amaute kikhopna innte ah thu a hilh hi. Kumpigam lungdamna thu tangko in cina le natna tuamtuam a nei mi khempeuh a damsak hi.
\v 36 \x + \xo 9:36 \xt Gam 27:17; 1Ku 22:17; Eze 34:5-6; Zec 10:2; Mak 8:2\x*Amah in mi honpite a et ciangin hehpihhuai a sa mahmah hi; banghang hiam cihleh amaute a cing om lo, a thabei, a kithehthang zelzul tuute tawh kibang uh hi.
\v 37 \x + \xo 9:37 \xt Luk 10:2; Joh 4:35\x*Tua hi a, a nungzuite kiangah, “An lak ding tam mahmah napi nasemte a tawm hi.
\v 38 Tua ahih manin an la ding nasemte hong sawl nadingin an nei Topa kiangah ngen un,” a ci hi.
\c 10 
\s1 Nungzuite Teelna 
\r Mak 3:13-19; Luk 9:1-6 
\p 
\v 1 \x + \xo 10:1 \xt Mak 3:13-15; Luk 4:36\x*Zeisu in a nungzui sawm le nihte sam a, dawigilote hawlkhiat theih nading le cinatna nam khempeuh le natna namkim a damsak theih nadingun thuneihna a pia hi. 
\p 
\v 2 Tua sawltak sawm le nihte minin a khatna ah Peter kici Simon le a sanggampa Andrew, Zebedee tapa James le a sanggampa John, 
\v 3 Philip le Bartholomew, Thomas le siahdongpa Matthew, Alphaeus tapa James, Thaddaeus a kici Lebbaeus, 
\v 4 \x + \xo 10:4 \xt Mak 14:10; Saw 1:16\x*Minamveipa Simon le amah a lehhekpa Judas Iscariot ahi uh hi. 
\s1 Sawm Le Nihte Sawlkhia 
\r Mak 6:7-13; Luk 9:1-6 
\p 
\v 5 \x + \xo 10:5 \xt 1Ku 16:24; 2Ku 17:24; Luk 9:52; Joh 4:4-9; Saw 8:5, 25\x*Zeisu in tua sawm le nihte sawlkhia in amaute kiangah, “Gentilete kiangah pai kei unla, \w Samaria mite\w* khua ah zong lut kei un. 
\v 6 \x + \xo 10:6 \xt Jer 50:6\x*Tuu banga a gammang Israel innkuante kiang bekah pai un. 
\v 7 Na pai ciangun, ‘Vantung kumpigam hong nai ta hi,’ ci in tangko un. 
\v 8 Cinate damsak unla, miphakte damsak un. Misite thosak in dawite hawlkhia un. Man piak loh a na ngah bangun manngen loin na pia un. 
\v 9 \x + \xo 10:9 \xt Luk 22:35\x*Kham, ngun le sumngote sumbawm sungah keng kei un. 
\v 10 \x + \xo 10:10 \xt 1Ti 5:18\x*Lampi a na zat ding uh thungip, puanak nih, khedap le ciangkhut cihte zong keng kei un; banghang hiam cihleh nasempa in a nekkhop a ngah dingin a kilawm hi. 
\p 
\v 11 “Khuapi khuata mun khatpeuh ah na lut uh ciangin, zintun nadingin a kilawm mi kan unla, na paikhiat matengun tua inn ah tamsuak un. 
\v 12 \x + \xo 10:12 \xt 1Sa 25:6\x*Inn khatpeuh ah na lut uh ciangun hopih un. 
\v 13 Tua innkuan in nopna ngah dinga a kilawm leh note piak nopna ngah henla, a kilawm keileh note tungah tua nopna hong tungkik hen. 
\v 14 \x + \xo 10:14 \xt Neh 5:13; Mak 6:11; Luk 9:5; Saw 13:51\x*Note hong sang nuam loin na thu uh a ngai nuam lo mi khatpeuh a om leh tua inn hiam tua khua hiam pan na ciah uh ciangin note khe tunga leivuite singkhia un. 
\v 15 \x + \xo 10:15 \xt Saw 17:31; 2Pe 2:6; 1Jn 4:17; Jud 1:7\x*Note kiangah a man takpi kong cihin ah, thukhen ni ciangin Sodom le Gomorrah khuate thuakna in tua khua thuakna sangin a thuak nop zaw lai ding hi! 
\s1 Hong Tung Ding Bawlsiatnate 
\r Mak 13:9-13; Luk 21:12-17 
\p 
\v 16 \x + \xo 10:16 \xt Luk 10:3; Saw 20:29; 1Co 14:20\x*“En un, ngiahon laka a kikhah tuute bangin note kong sawlkhia hi. Tua ahih manin gul bangin pilvang unla, vakhu bangin migi un. 
\v 17 \x + \xo 10:17 \xt Mak 13:9; Saw 5:40\x*Mite in thukhente tungah note hong ap in kikhopna innte ah hong sat ding uh ahih manin kidawm un. 
\v 18 \x + \xo 10:18 \xt Saw 25:24-26\x*Keima hangin kumpite le mangpite mai ah hong kipuak ding a, tua in amaute le Gentilete tungah teci na suah nading uh ahi hi. 
\v 19 \x + \xo 10:19 \xt Pai 4:12\x*Amaute in hong ap uh ciangin bang thu genin bangci gen ding cih lungkham khol kei un; banghang hiam cihleh na thu gen ding uh a hun lianin hong kihilh ding hi. 
\v 20 \x + \xo 10:20 \xt Luk 12:11-12\x*A gen ding note hi loin note sung panin na Pa uh Kha in a gen ding hi. 
\p 
\v 21 \x + \xo 10:21 \xt Mak 13:12\x*“Unau khat le khat a sih nadingun a kilehhek ding uh hi. Pa in a tate lehhek ding a, tate in a nu le a pa langpan in a si dingin a lehhek ding uh hi. 
\v 22 \x + \xo 10:22 \xt Mak 13:13; Luk 21:19; Joh 15:21; Kil 2:10\x*Keima min hangin mi khempeuh in note hong mudah ding uh hi. Ahi zongin a tawp donga a kipte in hotkhiatna a ngah ding uh hi. 
\v 23 \x + \xo 10:23 \xt Luk 17:30\x*Hih khua ah hong kibawlsiat leh khua dang khat ah tai un. A man takpi kong cihin ah, Israel gam khua khempeuh na khit ma un \w Mihing Tapa\w* hong pai ding hi. 
\p 
\v 24 \x + \xo 10:24 \xt Joh 13:16\x*“Nungzuipa in a siapa sangin lianzaw lo a, nasempa in a topa sangin lianzaw lo hi. 
\v 25 \x + \xo 10:25 \xt Mak 3:22\x*Nungzuipa in a siapa tawh hong kibang a, nasempa in a topa tawh a kibat leh phazo hi. A inntekpipa \w Beelzebub\w* hi ci khin uh ahih teh a innkuanpih dangte bel nakcih zawkan lo ding uh ahi hiam! 
\s1 Kua Kihta Ding 
\r Mak 9:41; Luk 12:2-9, 51-53; 14:26-27 
\p 
\v 26 \x + \xo 10:26 \xt Mak 4:22; Luk 8:17\x*“Tua ahih manin amaute kihta kei un; banghang hiam cihleh a kilang lo dinga a kisincip thei le a kithei lo dinga a ki-iimcip thei bangmah a om kei hi. 
\p 
\v 27 “Khuamial sunga kong gen thute khuavak ah gen un. Na zak thute uh innkhumzang panin tangkokhia un. 
\v 28 \x + \xo 10:28 \xt Isa 8:12-13; Heb 10:31\x*Pumpi bek that thei a kha a that thei lote kihta kei un. Ahi zongin kha le pumpi a nihin \w hell\w* sungah a khia theipa kihta un. 
\v 29 Kawlgit nih ciangin dangkasan tang khat tawh kizuak hi lo ahi hiam? Tuate khat nangawn na Pa uh deihna om loin lei ah a mawkkiat kei hi. 
\v 30 \x + \xo 10:30 \xt 1Sa 14:45; 2Sa 14:11; 1Ku 1:52; Luk 21:18; Saw 27:34\x*Note luzang a samzang om teng a vekpi in a kisim khinzo hi. 
\v 31 Tua ahih manin lau kei un. Kawlgit tampi sangin na manpha zaw uh hi. 
\s1 Mite Mai Ah Khazih Pulakna 
\r Luk 12:8, 9 
\p 
\v 32 \x + \xo 10:32 \xt Rom 10:9\x*“Tua hi a, mite mai ah kei a hong pulak mi peuhmah vana ka Pa mai ah zong ka pulak ding hi. 
\v 33 \x + \xo 10:33 \xt Mak 8:38; 2Ti 2:12\x*Mite mai ah kei a hong nial mi peuhmah vana ka Pa mai ah zong ka nial ding hi. 
\p 
\v 34 “Leitung ah kilemna bawl dinga hong pai hi ci in hong ngaihsun kei un. Ahi zongin kilemna bawl ding hi loin namsau khah dinga hong pai ka hi zaw hi. 
\v 35 Banghang hiam cihleh, 
\b 
\q1 \qt Tapa le a pa a kilangpansak ding,\qt* 
\q1 \qt Tanu le a nu a kilangpansak ding,\qt* 
\q1 \qt Monu le a teknu a kilangpansak dinga hong pai ka hi hi.\qt* 
\q1 
\v 36 \qt Mi khat gal pen ama innkuanpihte mah ahi ding hi.\qt*\f + \fr 10:36 \ft \+xt Mic 7:6\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* 
\b 
\p 
\v 37 \x + \xo 10:37 \xt Luk 14:26\x*“Kei sangin a nu ahih keileh a pa a it zawte kei tawh kituak lo a, kei sangin a tanu ahih keileh a tapa a it zawte kei tawh kituak lo hi. 
\v 38 \x + \xo 10:38 \xt Luk 14:27\x*Ama singlamteh pua loin ka nung hong zuite zong kei tawh kituak lo hi. 
\v 39 \x + \xo 10:39 \xt Joh 12:25\x*A nuntakna a huu nuam mi in a nuntakna tan ding a, keima hanga a nuntakna a tan mi in nuntakna a ngah ding hi. 
\p 
\v 40 \x + \xo 10:40 \xt Pai 16:8; Luk 9:48; Joh 12:44; Gal 4:14\x*“Note hong sang mi in kei hong sang hi a, kei hong sang mi in kei a hong sawlpa zong a sang ahi hi. 
\v 41 Kamsang khat pen kamsang ahih mana a sang mi in tua kamsangpa ngah bangbang thaman a ngah ding hi. Mi dik khat pen mi dik ahih mana a sang mi in tua mi dikpa ngah bangbang thaman a ngah ding hi. 
\v 42 \x + \xo 10:42 \xt Pau 14:31; Mak 9:41; Saw 10:4; Heb 6:10\x*Note kiangah a man takpi kong cihin ah, hih naupangnote khat peuhpeuh keima nungzui ahih mana tuivot hai khat nangawn a suah mi peuhmah in thaman ngah loin a om kei ding hi,” a ci hi. 
\c 11 
\s1 Zeisu Le Tuiphumpa John 
\r Luk 7:18-35 
\p 
\v 1 Zeisu in nungzui sawm le nihte thu a piak khit ciangin khuapite ah thugen ding le thuhilh dingin tua mun panin a paikhia hi. 
\p 
\v 2 John in thong sung panin Khazih nasepnate a zak ciangin a nungzuite nih sawl a, 
\v 3 \x + \xo 11:3 \xt Lat 118:26; Joh 11:27; Heb 10:37\x*“Hong pai ding pa mah na hi hiam, ahih keileh a dang khat lamen lai ding ka hi uh hiam?” ci in a dongsak hi. 
\p 
\v 4 Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Pai unla, na muhsa na zaksa teng uh John kiangah va gen un. 
\v 5 \x + \xo 11:5 \xt Isa 35:4-6; Luk 4:18-19\x*Mittawte in khuamu in khebaite lam a pai uh hi. Miphakte damsiang uh a, bengngongte in khua a za uh hi. Misite kithokiksak a, mi zawngte tungah lungdamna thu a kihilh hi. 
\v 6 Keima hanga a puk lo mi in mi hampha ahi hi,” ci in a dawng hi. 
\p 
\v 7 Amaute a paikhiat khit uh ciangin John tawh kisai Zeisu in mi honpite kiangah a genin ah, “Gamlak ah bang en dinga pai na hi uh hiam? Huih in a mut cianga a kihuang diamdiam \w pumpeng\w* kung peuh a en dinga pai na hi uh hiam? 
\v 8 Ahih keileh bang en ding na hi uh hiam? Puansilh nel niknek tawh a kizem khatpeuh en dinga paikhia na hi uh hiam? En un, puannel niknek a silhte in kumpi inn sunga a teengte ahi uh hi. 
\v 9 \x + \xo 11:9 \xt Luk 1:76\x*Tua ahih leh bang en dinga pai na hi uh hiam? Kamsangpa khat a en dinga pai na hi uh hiam? Hi mah hi. Ken kong cihin ah, kamsang khat sangin a lianzawpa ahi hi. 
\v 10 \x + \xo 11:10 \xt Mak 1:2; Luk 7:27; Joh 3:28\x*Banghang hiam cihleh \w Lai Siangtho\w* ah a kigelh mah bangin, 
\b 
\q1 \qt ‘En in, nangma lampi a sialkhol dingin,\qt* 
\q1 \qt Na mai ah ka kamtaipa ka sawl ding hi,’\qt*\f + \fr 11:10 \ft \+xt Mal 3:11\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* 
\m a cihpa in amah ahi hi. 
\b 
\p 
\v 11 “Note kiangah a man takpi kong cihin ah, numei sung panin a suak mite lakah Tuiphumpa John sanga a lianzaw kuamah a om kei hi. Ahih hangin vantung kumpigam sunga a om a neupenpa in John sangin a lianzaw hi. 
\v 12 Tuiphumpa John hun a kipan tuhun dong vantung kumpigam in zawhthawh bawlna thuak a, a zawhthawh bawlte in thagum suangin a la uh hi. 
\v 13 \x + \xo 11:13 \xt Luk 16:16\x*Banghang hiam cihleh thukham le kamsangte khempeuh in John hun donga a piang ding thute a genkhol hi. 
\v 14 \x + \xo 11:14 \xt Mal 4:5; Luk 1:17; Joh 1:21\x*Note in na san nop uh leh hong pai ding hi ci a kigenpa Elijah in amah ahi hi. 
\v 15 \x + \xo 11:15 \xt Mak 4:23; Luk 14:35; Kil 2:7\x*Zak nading bil a nei mi in za tahen! 
\p 
\v 16 “Hih khang mite bang tawh genteh ding ka hi hiam? Sumbuuk ah tu in a lawmte kiangah, 
\q1 
\v 17 ‘Tamngai ka tumtum uh hangin, 
\q1 Na lam tuan kei uh a, 
\q1 Ka tamlawh uh hangin lah, 
\q1 Na kap tuan kei uh hi,’ 
\m a ci naupangte tawh kibang uh hi. 
\b 
\p 
\v 18 \x + \xo 11:18 \xt Luk 1:15\x*“Banghang hiam cihleh John hong pai in an ne lo, tuidawn loin a om ciangin amaute in, ‘Dawilawm nei hi,’ a ci uh hi. 
\v 19 \w Mihing Tapa\w* hong pai a, anne tuidawn in a om ciangin lah, ‘En un, anhaipa, zuhaipa, \w siahdongte\w* le mimawhte lawmpa hi,’ a ci zel uh hi. Ahih hangin ciimna in a gamtatnate panin hong kilangkhia hi,” a ci hi. 
\s1 A Kisikkik Lo Khuapite 
\r Luk 10:13-15 
\p 
\v 20 Zeisu in nalamdang a tam pen a bawlna khuapite a mawhna uh kisikkik lo uh ahih manin, 
\v 21 \x + \xo 11:21 \xt Amo 1:9; Mak 6:45; Luk 9:10; Joh 1:44; Saw 12:20\x*mawhsaka a taii in ah, “Chorazin khua aw, gimna na thuak ding hi! Bethsaida khua aw, gimna na thuak ding hi! Banghang hiam cihleh note sunga kibawl nalamdangte, Tyre le Sidon khua ah kibawl hi leh, amaute sawtpi lai in a mawhna uh kisikkikin ippipuan silhin vut a kibuak ding uh hi. 
\v 22 Tua ahih manin ken kong cih in ah thukhen ni ciangin Tyre khua le Sidon khuate thuakna in note thuakna sangin a thuak nop zaw ding hi. 
\v 23 \x + \xo 11:23 \xt Isa 14:13-15\x*Vantung donga hong kilamto Capernaum khua aw, \w Hades\w* dongah hong kikhiasuk ding hi; banghang hiam cihleh nangma sunga hong kibawl nalamdangte Sodom khua ah a kibawl hi leh tuni dongin tua khua kip lai ding hi. 
\v 24 Tua ahih manin note kiang ken kong cih in ah thukhen ni ciangin Sodom khua thuakna in nangma thuakna sangin a thuak nop zaw ding hi,” a ci hi. 
\s1 Tawldamna 
\r Luk 10:21-22 
\p 
\v 25 \x + \xo 11:25 \xt Luk 22:42; Joh 11:41\x*Tua laitak mahin Zeisu in dawng a, “Vantung le leitung Topa ahi ka Pa aw, mi pil misiamte tungah hih thute iim in naungekte tungah na lah manin nang kong phat hi. 
\v 26 Hi mah hi. Pa aw, hih in nangma lungkimna ahi hi. 
\p 
\v 27 \x + \xo 11:27 \xt Joh 3:35; 10:15\x*“Ka Pa in na khempeuh kei tungah hong ap khinzo hi. Pa simloh kuamah in Tapa a thei kei hi. Tapa le Tapa in a theihsak nop mite simloh kuamah in Pa a thei kei hi. 
\p 
\v 28 \x + \xo 11:28 \xt Pai 33:14\x*“Vangik pua a gim mi khempeuhte aw, ka kiangah hong pai ta un, tawldamna kong pia ding hi. 
\v 29 \x + \xo 11:29 \xt Lat 116:7; Jer 6:16; Joh 13:15; Phi 2:5; 1Pe 2:21; 1Jn 2:6\x*Keima hakkol kisuan unla, ka kiangah hong kisin un; banghang hiam cihleh keimah in lungnemin a kiniamkhiat mi ka hi hi. Tua hi leh lungsim tawldamna na ngah ding uh hi. 
\v 30 \x + \xo 11:30 \xt 1Jn 5:3\x*Banghang hiam cihleh keima hakkol puak nop a, ka van zong a zang hi,” a ci hi. 
\c 12
\s1 Sabbath Ni A Uk Topa
\r Mak 2:23-28; Luk 6:1-5
\p
\v 1 \x + \xo 12:1 \xt Thu 23:25\x*Tua hun sung \w Sabbath\w* ni khat in buhlei kantanin Zeisu a pai hi. A nungzuite gilkial uh a, buhvuite zutin a bak uh hi.
\v 2 \x + \xo 12:2 \xt Pai 20:10; Thu 5:14; Luk 13:14; Joh 5:10\x*Phariseete in a muh uh ciangin, “En in, na nungzuite in Sabbath ni in amaute in thukham tawh kituak loin gamta uh hi!” a ci uh hi.
\p
\v 3 \x + \xo 12:3 \xt 1Sa 21:6\x*Ahih hangin Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “David le a pawlte a gilkial laitak un,
\v 4 \x + \xo 12:4 \xt Siam 24:5, 9\x*Pasian inn sungah lut uh a, amah le a pawlte nek theih ding a hi lo, siampite bek nek theih ding Ompihna Anlumte ne uh hi, cih thu sim ngei lo na hi uh hiam?
\v 5 \x + \xo 12:5 \xt Gam 28:9-10; Joh 7:22-23\x*Ahih keileh Sabbath ni in siampite in \w biakinnpi\w* sungah Sabbath ngeina a palsat uh hangin mawhna in kiciamteh lo ahihlam thukham laibu sungah sim ngei lo na hi uh hiam?
\v 6 Note kiang ken kong cih in ah biakinnpi sangin a lianzawpa hi lai ah a om hi.
\v 7 \x + \xo 12:7 \xt Mic 6:6-8\x*Ahih hangin, \qt ‘Gangawh biakna sangin hehpihna ka deih zaw hi,’\qt*\f + \fr 12:7 \ft \+xt Hos 6:6\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* a cihna thu theitel hi le uh teh khialhna a nei lo mipa na mawhsak kei ding uh hi.
\v 8 Banghang hiam cihleh \w Mihing Tapa\w* in Sabbath ni zong a Ukpa ahi hi,” a ci hi.
\s1 Sabbath Ni In Cina Damsak
\r Mak 3:1-6; Luk 6:6-11
\p
\v 9 Tu in tua mun panin amah paikhia in amaute \w kikhopna inn\w* sungah a lut hi.
\v 10 \x + \xo 12:10 \xt Mak 3:2; Luk 11:54\x*En in, tualai ah a khut langkhat a si mi khat a om hi. Amaute in Zeisu a mawhmat nop manun, “Sabbath ni in cina damsak ding thukham tawh a kituak hiam?” ci in a dong uh hi.
\v 11 \x + \xo 12:11 \xt Luk 14:5\x*Tua ciangin Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Sabbath ni in tuu khat bek a neih guam sungah kia leh a lakhia lo ding note lakah kua om na hi uh hiam?
\v 12 Tuu khat sangin mihing khat manpha zaw mahmah hi lo ahi hiam? Tua ahih manin Sabbath ni in a pha bawl ding thukham tawh kituak hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 13 Tua khit ciangin mipa kiangah, “Na khut zan in,” a ci hi. A zan ciangin a langkhat lam mah bangin a dam hi.
\v 14 \x + \xo 12:14 \xt Pian 37:18; Lat 71:10; Mak 3:6; Luk 6:11; Joh 5:18\x*Tua khit ciangin Phariseete paikhia in amah thah theih nading a vaihawm uh hi.
\s1 Pasian Teel Nasempa
\r Mak 3:7-12
\p
\v 15 Zeisu in tua thu a theih ciangin tua mun pan paikhia a, mi honpi in a zui uh hi. Amah in amaute khempeuh a damsak hi.
\v 16 Ama thu kuama kiangah a gen loh nadingun a kham hi.
\v 17 Hih in kamsangpa Isaiah gensa thu a tangtun nading ahi hi.
\p
\v 18 \x + \xo 12:18 \xt Joh 3:34\x*Isaiah in,
\b
\q1 \qt “En un! hih in ka teelsa ka nasempa,\qt*
\q1 \qt Ka itpa le ka lung hong damsak mahmah pa ahi hi!\qt*
\q1 \qt Ama tungah ka Kha ka koih ding a,\qt*
\q1 \qt Gentilete tungah thuman a hilh ding hi.\qt*
\q1
\v 19 \qt Amah in thu sel loin,\qt*
\q1 \qt A aw sangkhai lo ding a,\qt*
\q1 \qt Kongzing lakah zong kuamah in,\qt*
\q1 \qt Ama aw a za kei ding hi.\qt*
\q1
\v 20 \qt Thuman thutang a gualzawhsak matengin,\qt*
\q1 \qt Amah in a kitamzan pumpeng kuaitan loin,\qt*
\q1 \qt A tanglai meivak a sumit kei ding hi.\qt*
\q1
\v 21 \qt Gentilete in ama min a muang ding uh hi,”\qt*\f + \fr 12:21 \ft \+xt Isa 42:1-4\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f*
\m a ci hi.
\s1 Zeisu Le Beelzebub
\r Mak 3:20-30; Luk 11:14-23
\p
\v 22 Tua khit ciangin a mittaw in a pauthei lo dawilut mi khat Zeisu kiangah hong paipih uh hi. Zeisu in tua pa damsak ahih manin mittaw in a pauthei lo pa pauthei in khua zong a mu thei hi.
\v 23 Tua ciangin mipi khempeuh in lamdangsa mahmah uh a, “Hihpa in David Tapa hi thei ding ahi hiam?” a ci uh hi.
\v 24 \x + \xo 12:24 \xt Mak 3:22\x*Tu in Phariseete in hih thu a zak uh ciangin, “Hihpa in dawite mangpipa \w Beelzebub\w* min suangin dawite a hawlkhia ahi hi,” a cihsan uh hi.
\p
\v 25 Zeisu in amaute ngaihsutnate thei ahih manin amaute kiangah, “Kumpigam khat peuhpeuh amah le amah kilangkhen a, a kido leh a mangthang lel ding hi. Khua sung khat ahi a, innkuan khat ahi zongin amau le amau a kilem kei uh leh ding zo lo ding uh hi.
\v 26 \w Satan\w* in Satan hawlkhia in amah le amah kilem keileh ama kumpigam bangci in kip thei ding ahi hiam?
\v 27 \x + \xo 12:27 \xt Saw 19:13\x*Beelzebub suangin dawite hawlkhia ka hih leh na tate un kua min suangin dawite hawlkhia uh ahi hiam? Tua ahih ciangin amaute in note tungah thu a hong khente a suak ding uh hi.
\v 28 Ahih hangin Pasian Kha tawh dawite hawlkhia ka hih manin note tungah Pasian kumpigam hong tung zo hi.
\v 29 Ahih keileh mi thahatpa hencip masa loin kua in ama inn sungah lutin a neihsate laksak zo ding ahi hiam? Amah a kihencip khit ciang bekin a inn a kiluh zo pan ding hi.
\v 30 \x + \xo 12:30 \xt Mak 9:40; Luk 11:23\x*Kei lam a pang lo peuhmah kei hong langpan mi hi a, kei hong kaihkhoppih lo peuhmah a thehthang mi ahi hi.
\s1 A Kimaisak Thei Lo Mawhna
\p
\v 31 \x + \xo 12:31 \xt Mak 3:28-29; Luk 12:10\x*“Tua hi a, note kiang ken kong cih in ah mawhna namkim le Pasian tunga pausiatna peuhmah a kimaisak ding hi. Ahi zongin Kha tunga pausiatnate a kimaisak kei ding hi.
\v 32 \x + \xo 12:32 \xt Mak 10:30; Luk 20:34-35; Eph 1:21; Heb 6:5\x*Mihing Tapa langpanin a gensia peuhmah kimaisak ding a, Kha Siangtho langpanna kam a paute ahih leh tu khang le hong tung ding khang dongin a kimaisak kei ding hi.
\p
\v 33 \x + \xo 12:33 \xt Mat 7:15-20; Luk 6:43-44\x*“Singkung a hoih leh a gah hoih a, singkung a hoih keileh a gah hoih lo hi; banghang hiam cihleh singkungte a gah panin a kithei hi.
\v 34 \x + \xo 12:34 \xt Luk 6:45\x*Gul gupha suante aw! Mi hoih lote na hih manun kamhoih bangci zat theih ding na hi uh hiam? Banghang hiam cihleh lungsim sunga a dimlet thute kam panin a hong phulkhia ahi hi.
\v 35 Mi hoihin a lungsim sungah thuhoih kholin, thuhoih mah genkhia a, mi hoih loin thusia khol in thusia mah a genkhia hi.
\v 36 Ken kong cih in ah mite in kimanna nei lo, a mawkpauna kammalte uh hangin thukhen ni ciangin sittelna a thuak ding uh hi.
\v 37 \x + \xo 12:37 \xt Job 15:6; Pau 10:14; Jam 3:2\x*Banghang hiam cihleh na kampauna zui in dik hong kitangsak ding a, na kampauna mah zui in hong kimawhsak ding hi,” a ci hi.
\s1 Jonah Tawh Kisai Lim
\r Luk 11:29-32
\p
\v 38 \x + \xo 12:38 \xt Mak 8:11-12; Luk 11:16; Joh 2:11, 18; 1Co 1:22\x*Tua ciangin thukhamhilh siate le Phariseete pawlkhat in, “Sia aw, limlamdang khat nang hong lak leteh ka mu nuam uh hi,” a ci uh hi.
\p
\v 39 \x + \xo 12:39 \xt Luk 11:29\x*Tua ciangin Zeisu in dawngkik a, “A gilo le a paktat tulai khang mite in limlamdang a nget uh hangin kamsangpa Jonah tunga piang limlamdang longal a dang kilak lo ding hi.
\v 40 \x + \xo 12:40 \xt Jon 1:17\x*Jonah in ngapi gil sungah sun thum le zan thum a om bangin Mihing Tapa zong lei sungah sun thum le zan thum a om ding hi.
\v 41 \x + \xo 12:41 \xt Jon 1:2; 3:5\x*Thukhen ni ciangin Nineveh khua mite hong dingto in tulai khang mite a mawhsak ding uh hi; banghang hiam cihleh Jonah tangkona hangin amaute mawhna a kisikkik uh hi. En un, Jonah sanga a lianzawpa hi lai ah a om hi.
\v 42 \x + \xo 12:42 \xt 1Ku 10:1; 2Kh 9:1\x*Thukhen ni ciangin Leitaw lam gam kumpinu in tulai khang mite tawh dingkhawmin amaute a mawhsak ding hi; banghang hiam cihleh Solomon pilna a ngai dingin lei mong khat panin amah a hong pai hi. En un, Solomon sanga a lianzawpa hi lai ah a om hi.
\p
\v 43 “Dawi gilo in mi khat sung pan a paikhiat khit ciangin tawlngak nading zongin munkeuna tengah a vak kawikawi hangin a mu zo kei hi.
\v 44 Tua ciangin amah in, ‘Ka paikhiatna inn mahah ciahkik ning,’ a ci hi. A tun ciangin tua inn na awngin kiphiat kipuah sinsen a om a mu hi.
\v 45 \x + \xo 12:45 \xt 2Pe 2:20\x*Tua ciangin amah sanga a gilozaw dawi sagih va zawn a, tua inn ah lutpihin a teeng uh hi. Tu a tua pa dinmun in a masa sangin a siazaw hi. A gilo tulai khang mite tungah zong tua bangin a piang ding hi,” a ci hi.
\s1 Zeisu Nu Le Sanggamte
\r Mak 3:31-35; Luk 8:19-21
\p
\v 46 \x + \xo 12:46 \xt Luk 1:43; Joh 2:1-2, 12; Saw 1:14; 1Co 9:5; Gal 1:19\x*Zeisu in mi honpite thu a hilhhilh laitakin a nu le a sanggamte in amah hopih nuamin innpua ah a ding uh hi.
\v 47 Tua ciangin mi khat in, “En in, na nu le na sanggamte in nang hong hopih nuamin innpua ah a ding uh hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 48 Ahih hangin Zeisu in tua mi kiangah, “Ka nu kua hi a, ka sanggamte kua ahi hiam?” ci in
\v 49 a nungzuite lamah a khut zan a, “En un, hih mite in ka nu le ka sanggamte ahi uh hi!
\v 50 \x + \xo 12:50 \xt Joh 15:14\x*Banghang hiam cihleh vantung a om ka Pa deihna bangin a gamta mi khat peuhpeuh ka sanggampa, ka sanggamnu le ka nu ahi uh hi,” a ci hi.
\c 13 
\s1 Khaici Vawhpa Thugentehna 
\r Mak 4:1-20; Luk 8:4-15 
\p 
\v 1 Tua ni mahin inn pan Zeisu paikhia a, tuilipi gei ah a tu hi. 
\v 2 \x + \xo 13:2 \xt Luk 5:3\x*Mi honpite hong kikhawm uh ahih manin gunkuang tungah kahto in tu a, mipi khempeuh ahih leh tuili gei ah a ding uh hi. 
\p 
\v 3 Amah in thugentehna tawh thu tampi a hilhin ah, “Ngai un! Khaici vawhpa khat khaici vawh dingin a kuankhia hi. 
\v 4 Khaici a vawh ciangin khaici pawlkhat lam gei ah tu a, vana vasate hong lengin a nemang uh hi. 
\v 5 Pawlkhatte suang kitawphah lei tawmna munah kia in lei dai ahih manin thakhatin a po pah hi. 
\v 6 Ahih hangin ni hong sa in halvul a, zungkha zo loin, a keumang hi. 
\v 7 Pawlkhatte ling lakah tu a, lingkungte hong khangin tuate a depgawp hi. 
\v 8 \x + \xo 13:8 \xt Pian 26:12\x*Ahih hangin a dangte lei hoihna ah tu a, pawlkhatte a zah 100, pawlkhatte a zah 60, pawlkhatte a zah 30 a gah hi. 
\v 9 Zak nading bil a nei mi in za tahen!” a ci hi. 
\s1 Thugentehna Deihna 
\p 
\v 10 A nungzuite in va naih uh a, “Banghang in gentehna tawh amaute thu hilh na hi hiam?” ci in a dong uh hi. 
\p 
\v 11 \x + \xo 13:11 \xt 1Co 2:10, 14; Col 1:27; 1Jn 2:20, 27\x*Amah in dawngkik a amaute kiangah, “Vantung kumpigam thusimte note theih dingin hong kipiak hangin amaute kipia lo hi. 
\v 12 Banghang hiam cihleh a neite kipiak beh ding a, kicingtakin a nei ding uh hi. A nei lote ahih leh a neih sunsun nangawn uh a kilakkhiatsak ding hi. 
\v 13 \x + \xo 13:13 \xt Thu 29:4; Jer 5:21; Eze 12:2\x*Amaute in enen napi mu thei lo, ngaingai napi za thei loin a theih theih loh nadingun thugentehna tawh ka hilh ahi hi. 
\v 14 Tua mite tungah Isaiah genkholhna a tangtung hi. Amah in, 
\b 
\q1 \qt ‘Note in zaza napi in,\qt* 
\q1 \qt Na tel thei kei ding uh hi.\qt* 
\q1 \qt Mumu napi in na phawk thei kei ding uh hi.\qt* 
\q1 
\v 15 \x + \xo 13:15 \xt Joh 12:40; Saw 28:26-27; Rom 11:8\x*\qt Banghang hiam cihleh hih mite a lungsim uh mawl in,\qt* 
\q1 \qt A bil un khuaza hak mahmah a,\qt* 
\q1 \qt A mit uh zong a sicip uh hi.\qt* 
\q1 \qt Tua hi keileh a mit un khuamu in,\qt* 
\q1 \qt A bil un khua a za ding hi.\qt* 
\q1 \qt A lungsim un theitel in,\qt* 
\q1 \qt Hong kiheikik ding uh a,\qt* 
\q1 \qt Amaute ka damsak ding hi,’\qt*\f + \fr 13:15 \ft \+xt Isa 6:9-10\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* 
\m a ci hi. 
\b 
\p 
\v 16 “Ahih hangin note na hih uh leh na mit un mu in na bil un za ahih manin mi hampha na hi uh hi. 
\v 17 \x + \xo 13:17 \xt Joh 8:56; Heb 11:13; 1Pe 1:10-12\x*A man takpi kong cihin ah, kamsangte le mi dikte in note muhte a muh nop uh hangin a mu kha kei uh hi. Na zakte uh a zak nop uh hangin a za kha kei uh hi. 
\s1 Thugentehna Telgenna 
\p 
\v 18 “Tua ahih ciangin khaici vawhpa tawh thugentehna na ngai un. 
\v 19 Mi khat in vantung kumpigam thu a zak ciangin theitel zo lo ahih manin gilopa hong pai in ama lungsim sunga kivawhsa khaici a lakkhiatsak hi. Tua mi in lamdung a a kia khaici ahi hi. 
\v 20 A nuai ah suang om a, a tungtham lei tawm a omna munah a kia khaici in thu a zak ciangin lungdamna tawh a sang pah mi ahi hi. 
\v 21 Ahih hangin ama sungah zungkha lo ahih manin tawlkhat sung bek a kip hi; banghang hiam cihleh Pasian thu hanga haksatna ahih keileh bawlsiatna hong tun ciangin a lungkia pah hi. 
\v 22 \x + \xo 13:22 \xt 1Ti 6:9-10, 17\x*Tu in ling laka a kia khaici in thu za napi leitung nuntakna aa ding lunghihmawhna le khemna tawh kidim hauh nopna in ama thu sansa depgawp ahih manin a gah zo lo mi ahi hi. 
\v 23 Ahi zongin lei hoihna muna a kia khaici in thu a zak ciangin theitel a, gahsuah in a pungsak mi ahi hi. Pawlkhatte a zah 100, pawlkhatte a zah 60, pawlkhatte a zah 30 a gah uh hi,” a ci hi. 
\s1 Tahum Thugentehna 
\p 
\v 24 \x + \xo 13:24 \xt Mak 4:26, 30\x*Zeisu in thugentehna a dang khat a genin ah, “Vantung kumpigam in lolai a khaici hoih a vawh mi tawh kibang hi. 
\v 25 Ahih hangin mi khempeuh a ihmut kalin ama galpa hong pai in tang lakah tahum tang a vawh khit ciangin a paikhia hi. 
\v 26 Tang tangte hong po in a vuih ciangin tahum kungte zong hong dawkkhia hi. 
\v 27 Lo neipa nasemte hong pai in ama kiangah, ‘Pu aw, na lo a na vawh khaici hoih hi lo ahi hiam? Tahum kungte koi pana hong piang himawk ahi hiam?’ a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 28 “Amah in, ‘Galpa vawh ahi hi,’ a ci hi. 
\p “Nasemte in, ‘Tua ahih leh kote va pai in tahum kungte ka botkhiat ding uh na deih hiam?’ a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 29 “Amah in, ‘Botkhia nai kei un tahum kung le tang kung na botkhawm kha ding uh hi. 
\v 30 Anlak hun dong a nihin khangkhawmsak phot un. Anlak hun ciangin anlate kiangah, “Tahum teng bot masa unla, mei a khul dingin lomhen un. Tang ahih leh ka ansal ah hong sung un,” ci in ka vaikhak ding hi,’~” a ci hi. 
\s1 Ankamtang Thugentehna 
\r Mak 4:30-32; Luk 13:18-21 
\p 
\v 31 \x + \xo 13:31 \xt Luk 17:6\x*Amah in gentehna dang khat a genin ah, “Vantung kumpigam in mi khat in lolai a a vawh ankamtang tawh kibang hi. 
\v 32 \x + \xo 13:32 \xt Lat 104:12; Eze 17:23; Dan 4:12\x*Ankamtang in khaici tang khempeuh lakah a neupen ahih hangin a khan khit ciangin anteh kung dangte sangin golzaw a, a kung lianpi khat hong suak hi. Vana leng vasate in zong a hiang lakah bu a tom thei uh hi,” a ci hi. 
\s1 Silngo Thugentehna 
\r Luk 13:20-21 
\p 
\v 33 \x + \xo 13:33 \xt Pian 18:6; Gal 5:9\x*Amah in thugentehna dang khat a genin ah, “Vantung kumpigam in numei khat in annel lawhbeu thum a tawk dinga a sawh silngo tawh kibang hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 34 \x + \xo 13:34 \xt Joh 16:25\x*Zeisu in hih thute khempeuh thugentehna tawh mi honpite hilh a, thugentehna loin thu a hilh kei hi. 
\v 35 \x + \xo 13:35 \xt Rom 16:25-26; 1Co 2:7; Eph 3:9; Col 1:26\x*Banghang hiam cihleh, 
\b 
\q1 \qt “Thugentehna tawh thu ka hilh ding a,\qt* 
\q1 \qt Leitung piancil a kipan a ki-iimcip thute ka pulak ding hi,”\qt*\f + \fr 13:35 \ft \+xt Lat 78:2\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* 
\m ci a, kamsangpa gensa thu a tangtun nading ahi hi. 
\s1 Tahum Thugentehna Telgenna 
\p 
\v 36 Zeisu in mi honpi a ciahsak khit ciangin inn sungah a lut hi. A nungzuite in amah hong naih uh a, “Lolai a po tahum kung thugentehna a khiatna hong gen in,” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 37 Tua ciangin Zeisu in dawng a, “Khaici hoih vawhpa in \w Mihing Tapa\w* ahi hi. 
\v 38 \x + \xo 13:38 \xt Joh 8:44; 1Jn 3:10\x*Lolai pen leitung hi a, khaici hoihte pen kumpigam sung mite hi in, tahum kungte pen gilopa mite ahi uh hi. 
\v 39 \x + \xo 13:39 \xt Joe 3:13; Kil 14:15\x*Tahumtang a vawh galpa in \w Dawimangpa\w* ahi hi. Anlak hun pen leitung hun beina hi a, tang late in vantungmite ahi uh hi. 
\p 
\v 40 “Tahum kungte botkhia in mei sungah a kikhul bangin hih leitung hun a bei ciangin a piang ding hi. 
\v 41 Mihing Tapa in ama vantungmite sawl ding a, amaute in mi a puksak khempeuh le siatna a bawl mi khempeuh ama kumpigam sung panin a paikhia ding uh hi. 
\v 42 Meikhukpi sungah amaute khul ding a, tua munah kahna le hagawina a om ding hi. 
\v 43 \x + \xo 13:43 \xt Dan 12:3\x*Tua ciangin mi dikte in a Pa uh kumpigam sungah ni bangin a tang ding uh hi. Zak nading bil a nei mi in za tahen! 
\s1 A Kisel Sum Thugentehna 
\p 
\v 44 \x + \xo 13:44 \xt Phi 3:7-8\x*“Tua banah vantung kumpigam in lolai a kisel sum tawh kibang hi. Mi khat in tua sum a muh ciangin selkik in lungdam mahmahin ciah a, a neihsa khempeuh zuak in tua lo a lei hi. 
\s1 Kepsuang Thugentehna 
\p 
\v 45 “Vantung kumpigam in a hoih mahmah kepsuangmanpha a zong sumbawlpa tawh kibang hi. 
\v 46 Amah in a mantam mahmah kepsuangmanpha khat a muh ciangin ciah a, a neihsa khempeuh zuak in tua kepsuang a lei hi. 
\s1 Ngenpi Thugentehna 
\p 
\v 47 “Vantung kumpigam in tuili sungah a kikhuh ciangin ngasa namkim a man ngenpi tawh kibang hi. 
\v 48 Tua ngenpi ah ngasa a dimtak a awk ciangin tuili gei ah kaikhia in tu uh a, a hoih teng bawm sungah guangin a hoih lo teng a paikhia uh hi. 
\v 49 Leitung hun a bei ciangin zong tua mah bangin a piang ding hi. Vantungmite hong pai ding uh a, mi dikte lak panin mi gilote a khenkhia ding uh hi. 
\v 50 Meikhukpi sungah amaute khul ding a, tua munah kahna le hagawina a om ding hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 51 Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Hih thute a vekpi in na theitel ta uh hiam?” ci in a dot ciangin amaute in, “Topa aw, ka theitel ta uh hi,” a ci uh hi. 
\s1 Innneipa Tawh Thugentehna 
\p 
\v 52 Tua ciangin amah in, “Vantung kumpigam thuhilhna a sang khin thukhamhilh sia peuhmah in ama sumkoihna sung panin a lui a thak a lakhia ziauziau thei innneipa tawh kibang hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 53 Zeisu in hih thugentehna khempeuh a gen khit ciangin tua mun panin a paikhia hi. 
\s1 Zeisu Kisang Lo 
\r Mak 6:1-6 
\p 
\v 54 Ama khankhiatna khua a tun ciangin amaute \w kikhopna inn\w* sungah thu a hilh hi. Amaute in lamdangsa mahmah uh a, “Hihpa in hih pilna le nalamdang pipi sep theihnate koi pan ngah ahi hiam? 
\v 55 \x + \xo 13:55 \xt Luk 3:23; Joh 6:42\x*Amah khutsiampa tapa hi lo ahi hiam? A nu zong Mary a kici nu hi a, a sanggamte zong James, Joses, Simon le Judas-te hi lo uh ahi hiam? 
\v 56 Ama sanggam numei khempeuh zong eite kiangah om hi lo uh ahi hiam? Tua hi napi, hih mipa in hih thu teng koi pan ngahkhia ahi hiam?” a ci uh hi. 
\v 57 \x + \xo 13:57 \xt Luk 4:24; Joh 4:44; 6:61\x*Tua ahih manin ama hangin a lungkia uh hi. Ahih hangin Zeisu in, “Kamsang kici peuhmah ama khua le ama innkuan sung simloh mundang khempeuh ah pahtawina ngah loin a om kei hi,” a ci hi. 
\v 58 Amaute in um lo uh ahih manin tualai ah nalamdang tampi a bawl kei hi. 
\c 14 
\s1 Tuiphumpa John Sihna 
\r Mak 6:14-29; Luk 9:7-9 
\p 
\v 1 \x + \xo 14:1 \xt Mak 8:15; Luk 3:1, 19; 9:7-9; Saw 4:27\x*Tua huna \w gam uk mangpa\w* Herod in Zeisu thu a za hi. 
\v 2 Tua ciangin a nasemte kiangah, “Tuiphumpa John misite lak pan hong thokik zo a, hih vangliatnate amah in a nei ahi hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 3 \x + \xo 14:3 \xt Luk 3:19-20\x*Herod in a sanggampa Philip zi Herodias tawh kisai in John man in hen a, thong sungah a khum hi. 
\v 4 \x + \xo 14:4 \xt Siam 18:16; 20:21\x*Banghang hiam cihleh John in ama kiangah, “Na sanggampa zi na teenpih pen thukham tawh kituak lo hi,” ci in a gen ngei hi. 
\v 5 Herod in John a thah nop hangin mipite a kihta hi; banghang hiam cihleh mi honpite in kamsang khat in John ngaihsun uh hi. 
\p 
\v 6 Herod in ama suahpawi bawl a, amaute mai ah Herodias tanu a lam hi. Tua ciangin amah lungdam mahmah a, 
\v 7 “Nong nget peuhpeuh kong pia ding hi,” ci in kamciam a pia hi. 
\v 8 Tua nu in a nu sawlna bangin, “Tuiphumpa John lutang kuangdai sung khat ah hong pia in,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 9 Kumpipa dah mahmah a, ahi zongin a kiciamna sa le amah tawh omkhawm mite hangin tua nu ngetna piak dingin thu a pia hi. 
\v 10 Tua bangin mi sawl pah a, thong sunga om John ngawng a tansak hi. 
\v 11 Amaute in John lutang kuangdai tawh hong tawi in nungaknonu pia uh a, nungaknonu in a nu kiangah a puak hi. 
\v 12 \x + \xo 14:12 \xt Saw 8:2\x*Tua ciangin John nungzuite hong pai in a luang la in vui uh a, tua khit ciangin Zeisu kiangah a va ko uh hi. 
\s1 Zeisu In Mi 5,000 Anvak 
\r Mak 6:30-44; Luk 9:10-17; Joh 6:1-15 
\p 
\v 13 Tu in, hih thu Zeisu in a zak ciangin tua mun panin gamdaihna mun khat ah gunkuang tuangin a kihemkhia hi. Ahih hangin mi honpi in hih thu a zak uh ciangin amau khua ciat pan khe tawh hong pai in amah a zuan uh hi. 
\v 14 Zeisu gamdaihna mun a hong tun ciangin mi honpite mu a, amaute hehpihhuai sa ahih manin cinate a damsak hi. 
\p 
\v 15 Nitak lam ciangin a nungzuite ama kiangah hong pai uh a, “Hih mun in gamlak ahih banah ni niam ta ahih manin mihonte an lei dingin khua sungah paisak in,” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 16 Zeisu in, “Amaute mundang a paikhiat ding uh kul lo hi. A nek ding uh bang khat peuhpeuh pia un,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 17 Amaute in, “Anlum nga le ngasa nih bek ka nei uh hi,” ci in dawng uh hi. 
\p 
\v 18 Amah in, “Tuate ka kiangah hong la un,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 19 \x + \xo 14:19 \xt 1Sa 9:13; Mak 8:6; Luk 9:16; Saw 2:42; 1Co 10:16; 1Ti 4:4\x*Tua khit ciangin mi honpite lopa tungah a tusak hi. Anlum nga le ngasa nihte la in, vantung lam ento a thupha a piak khit ciangin anlumte balkham in nungzuite pia a, nungzuite in mi honpite lakah a hawm uh hi. 
\v 20 A vekpi un gilvahtakin ne uh a, a kikhamval a themneng teng a khop uh ciangin lawh sawm le lawh nih dim a ngah uh hi. 
\v 21 Anne mi peuhmah numei le naupang simloh pasal bekbek 5,000 bang a pha uh hi. 
\s1 Tui Tungah Zeisu Lampai 
\r Mak 6:45-56; Joh 6:16-24 
\p 
\v 22 Zeisu in mi honpite a ciahsak laitakin a nungzuite zong gunkuang tungah tuangsak mengmeng a, ama mai ah a galkahsak hi. 
\v 23 \x + \xo 14:23 \xt Luk 3:21\x*Mi honpite a ciahkhiatsak khit ciangin thungen dingin mual tung ah amah bek a kahto hi. Khuamial ciangin tualai ah amah guak a om hi. 
\v 24 Ahih hangin gunkuang pen tuili laizang ah om a, huih in lehmut ahih manin tuihual in a lokgawp hi. 
\p 
\v 25 Zanvil lina\f + \fr 14:25 \fk Zanvil lina\ft : Zingsang nai 3 pan nai 6 kikal hi.\f* ciangin amaute lam manawh in Zeisu tui tungah hong pai hi. 
\v 26 \x + \xo 14:26 \xt Luk 24:37\x*Nungzuite in amah tui tunga pai a muh uh ciangin patau uh a, “Sikha hi!” ci in lau in a kiko uh hi. 
\p 
\v 27 \x + \xo 14:27 \xt Dan 10:12; Luk 1:13, 30; Saw 18:9; 23:11; Kil 1:17\x*Zeisu in zong, “Lungnuam un! Keimah ka hi hi. Lau kei un,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 28 Peter in, “Topa aw, nangmah na hih leh tui tungtawnin nang kiangah kong pai theih nading thu hong pia in,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 29 Zeisu in, “Hong pai in,” a cih ciangin gunkuang pan Peter kumkhia in, Zeisu kiang zuanin tui tungah a pai hi. 
\v 30 Ahih hangin huihpi kizial a muh ciangin lau a, tui sungah tum dektak ahih manin, “Topa aw, hong hon in,” ci in a kiko hi. 
\p 
\v 31 Zeisu in thakhatin a khut zanin len a, “Upna neu mipa aw, banghang in muanglah na hi hiam?” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 32 Amau gel gunkuang sung a tun uh ciangin huihpi a dai hi. 
\v 33 \x + \xo 14:33 \xt Mat 4:3\x*Tua ciangin gunkuang sunga mite hong pai in, “Nangmah in Pasian Tapa taktak na hi hi,” ci in amah a bia uh hi. 
\p 
\v 34 A galkhat ah a kah khit uh ciangin Gennesaret gam ah a pai uh hi. 
\v 35 Tua muna om mite in amah ahihlam a theih uh ciangin khuakim khuapam ah thu zasak uh a, cina khempeuh ama kiangah hong paipih uh hi. 
\v 36 Ama puanmongtep tawm a lawnziau theih nadingun ngen uh a, a lawng kha peuhmah a dam siang uh hi. 
\c 15 
\s1 A Siang Le A Siang Lo 
\r Mak 7:1-13 
\p 
\v 1 Tua khit ciangin Jerusalem khuapi a om \w thukhamhilh siate\w* le \w Pharisee\w* pawlte Zeisu kiangah hong pai uh a, 
\v 2 “Na nungzuite in banghang in tanglai ngeina palsat in khutsil lopi in an ne uh ahi hiam?” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 3 Zeisu in dawngin amaute kiangah, “Banghang in note in zong tanglai ngeina paulam in Pasian thupiak palsat na hi uh hiam? 
\v 4 \x + \xo 15:4 \xt Eph 6:2\x*Banghang hiam cihleh Pasian in, \qt ‘Na nu le na pa zahtak in,’\qt*\f + \fr 15:4 \ft \+xt Pai 20:12; Thu 5:16\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* ci a, \qt ‘A nu ahi a, a pa ahi zongin a samsiate in thahna thuak tahen,’\qt*\f + \fr 15:4 \ft \+xt Pai 21:17; Siam 20:9\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* ci in thu hong pia hi. 
\v 5 Ahi zongin note in, ‘Mi khat in a nu le a pa kiangah, “Kei tung pana na ngah ding khempeuh uh Pasian ka pia khinzo hi,” 
\v 6 ci peuh leh a nu le a pa piak kul nawn lo hi,’ na ci uh hi. Tua bangin tanglai ngeina paulam in Pasian thupiakna a mawkna na suaksak uh hi. 
\v 7 A kineihkhem mite aw! Isaiah in note thu a genkholhna a man mahmah hi. 
\b 
\p 
\v 8 “Amah in, 
\q1 \qt ‘Hih mite in a kam uh tawh kei hong zuanin,\qt* 
\q1 \qt A kam uh tawh hong pahtawi uh hangin,\qt* 
\q1 \qt A lungsim uh kei tawh kigamla hi.\qt* 
\q1 
\v 9 \x + \xo 15:9 \xt Mal 2:2; Col 2:20-22\x*\qt Mihing bawltawm thukhamte thuhilhna in zang uh ahih manin, \qt* 
\q1 \qt Kei a hong biakna uh a mawkna ahi hi,’\qt*\f + \fr 15:9 \ft \+xt Isa 29:13\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* ci hi,” ci in a gen hi. 
\b 
\p 
\v 10 Amah in mi honpi ama kiangah a sap khit ciangin, “Hih thu ngai unla theitel un. 
\v 11 \x + \xo 15:11 \xt Saw 10:14-15\x*Kam sunga a lutsukte in mihing ninsak lo a, kam sung pan a pusuakte bekin mihing a ninsak hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 12 Tua khit ciangin a nungzuite ama kiangah pai uh a, “Phariseete in hih na thugen zadah mahmah uh hi cih na thei hiam?” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 13 \x + \xo 15:13 \xt Isa 60:21\x*Ahih hangin Zeisu in dawng a, “Vantung a ka Pa in a suan loh peuhmah kibotkhia ding hi. 
\v 14 \x + \xo 15:14 \xt Luk 6:39; Rom 2:19\x*Tua mite awlmawh kei un. Amaute in mittawte a makaih mittaw makaite ahi uh hi. Mittaw in mittaw makaih leh a nihun guam sungah kia ding uh hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 15 Tua ciangin Peter in, “Hih thugentehna a khiatna hong hilh in,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 16 Tua ciangin Zeisu in, “Note nangawn in hih thu tel zo nai lo lailai na hi uh hiam? 
\v 17 Kam sunga a lutsuk peuhmah gilpi sung tung a, tua panin kithakhia hi cih thei lo na hi uh hiam? 
\v 18 \x + \xo 15:18 \xt Luk 6:45; Jam 3:6\x*Ahih hangin kam sung pana a pusuakte in lungsim pan hong paikhia ahih manin mihing a ninsak hi. 
\v 19 \x + \xo 15:19 \xt Gal 5:19-21\x*Banghang hiam cihleh ngaihsut hoih lote, mi thahna, mi zi tawh mawhna, numei pasal mawhna, guktakna, teci man lo le kosiatnate lungsim sung panin hong paikhia ahi hi. 
\v 20 \x + \xo 15:20 \xt Rom 14:14\x*Hite in mi ninsak a, ahih hangin khutsil lo a annekna in mi a ninsak kei hi,” a ci hi. 
\s1 Canaan Numei Upna 
\r Mak 7:24-30 
\p 
\v 21 Tua ciangin tua mun panin Zeisu paikhia in, Tyre le Sidon gam ah a pai hi. 
\v 22 En un, tua gam pana hong pai Canaan numei khat in, “David Tapa, Topa aw, kei hong hehpih in. Ka tanu dawilut a, nasiatakin bawlsiatna a thuak hi,” ci in a kiko hi. 
\p 
\v 23 Ahih hangin Zeisu in kam khat beek a dawng kei hi. A nungzuite zong hong pai in, “Eite nungah hih numei hong kiko niloh ahih manin hawlkhia in,” ci in a kun uh hi. 
\p 
\v 24 \x + \xo 15:24 \xt Rom 15:8\x*Ahih hangin amah in, “Tuu banga a mangthang Israel minamte kiang longal ah kei hong kisawl lo hi,” ci in a dawng hi. 
\p 
\v 25 Tua ciangin tua nu hong pai in, “Topa aw, hong huh in,” ci in a bia hi. 
\p 
\v 26 Zeisu in, “Tate annek lai lakhia in uite piak ding kilawm lo hi,” ci in a dawng hi. 
\p 
\v 27 Tua nu in, “Hi mah hi, Topa aw, ahi zongin uite in a pu sabuai pana anneng kiate ne khasam uh hi lo ahi hiam,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 28 Tua ciangin Zeisu in, “Numei aw, na upna lian hi. Na lunggulhna bangin na tungah piang tahen,” a ci hi. Tua hun lian mahin a tanu a dam pah hi. 
\s1 Zeisu In Mi Tampi Damsak 
\p 
\v 29 Zeisu in tua mun nusia in Galilee tuilipi lamah pai a, mual tung ah kahto in tualai ah a tu hi. 
\v 30 Tua ciangin mi honpite ama kiangah hong pai uh a, khebai, mittaw, pauthei lo le a poite a kipan a dang cina tampi hong paipih uh a, Zeisu khebul ah nga in amah in tuate khempeuh a damsak hi. 
\v 31 A pau thei lote pau thei uh a, a poite damkik in, khebaite lampai thei uh a, mittawte in khua a mukik uh hi. Mi honpite in tuate a muh uh ciangin lamdangsa uh a, Israel Pasian a phat uh hi. 
\s1 Zeisu In Mi 4,000 Anvak 
\r Mak 8:1-10 
\p 
\v 32 Tu in Zeisu in a nungzuite ama kiangah sam in, “Hih mi honpite ni thum tawntung kei tawh omkhawm uh a, nek ding bangmah nei lo uh ahih manin hehpihhuai ka sa hi. Lamkal ah phukhong vei kha ding uh ahih manin gilkialsa in ka ciahsak nuam kei hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 33 Tua ciangin a nungzuite in, “Mihon hi zah kham ding an hih gamlak ah koi pan ngah mawk ding i hi hiam?” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 34 Zeisu in, “Anlum bangzah nei na hi uh hiam?” ci in a dot ciangin amaute in, “Anlum sagih le ngasaneu tawmkha ka nei uh hi,” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 35 Tua ciangin Zeisu in mi honpite leilak ah a tusak hi. 
\v 36 Tua ciangin anlum sagih le ngasa la in lungdam a koh khit ciangin, balnen a, a nungzuite a pia hi. Nungzuite in mi honpite lakah a hawmkhia uh hi. 
\v 37 Amaute khempeuh in khamtak in, a nek khit uh ciangin nungzuite in a kikhamval a themneng teng kaikhawm uh a, lawhbeu gol sagih dim a ngah uh hi. 
\v 38 Anne mi numei le naupang simloh pasal bekbek 4,000 a pha uh hi. 
\v 39 Zeisu in mi honpite a ciahsak khit ciangin, gunkuang tung tuangin Magdala gam ah a pai hi. 
\c 16 
\s1 Lim Khat Kal Uh 
\r Mak 8:11-13 
\p 
\v 1 \x + \xo 16:1 \xt Saw 4:1\x*Tua ciangin Sadduceete le Phariseete hong pai uh a, amah a ze-et nadingun, “Vantung pan theihsakna lim khat hong lak in,” ci in a ngen uh hi. 
\p 
\v 2 Zeisu in, “Note in, ‘Nitak lamin meiisan hong suah leh khua pha ding hi,’ na ci uh hi. 
\v 3 \x + \xo 16:3 \xt Luk 12:54-56\x*Zingsang lam ahih leh, ‘Tuni in meiisan in khua nim ahih manin khuahun a sia ding hi,’ na ci uh hi. A kineihkhem mite aw, tua bangin van maitang khentel thei napi uh cin banghang in a hun zui a piang theihsakna limte khentel thei lo na hi uh hiam! 
\v 4 A gilo le a paktat tulai khang mite in limlamdang a nget uh hangin kamsangpa Jonah tunga piang limlamdang longal a dang kilak lo ding hi,” a ci hi. Tua khit ciangin amaute nusia in a paikhia hi. 
\s1 Pharisee-te Le Sadducee-te Silngo 
\r Mak 8:14-21 
\p 
\v 5 Tu in a nungzuite a galkhat hong tun uh ciangin anlum puak ding a mangngilh uh hi. 
\v 6 \x + \xo 16:6 \xt Luk 12:1\x*Tua ciangin Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Phariseete le Sadduceete silngo kidawm un,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 7 Tua ciangin amaute in, “Anlum i puak loh manin hih bangin hong gen hi ding hi,” ci in a kikum uh hi. 
\p 
\v 8 Ahih hangin Zeisu in tua thu a theih ciangin, “Upna neu mite aw, banghang in anlum na puak loh uh kikum na hi uh hiam? 
\v 9 Theitel nai lo lailai na hi uh hiam? Mihing 5,000 in anlum nga a nek khit uh ciangin a khamval lawh bangzah pha cih mangngilh ta na hi uh hiam? 
\v 10 Mihing 4,000 in anlum sagih a nek khit uh ciangin, a khamval uh lawhbeu gol bangzah pha cih phawk nawn lo na hi uh hiam? 
\v 11 Annek tawh kisai thu gen ka hi kei a, Phariseete le Sadduceete silngo na kidop ding uh a gen ka hih lam banghang in tel zo lo na hi uh hiam?” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 12 \x + \xo 16:12 \xt Saw 4:1\x*Tua ciangin annel laka kisawh silngo hi loin Phariseete le Sadduceete thuhilhna kidawm un Zeisu in a cihna ahihlam amaute in a tel pan uh hi. 
\s1 Zeisu Thu Peter Pulakna 
\r Mak 8:27-30; Luk 9:18-21 
\p 
\v 13 Tu in Caesarea Philippi gam ah Zeisu hong tun ciangin a nungzuite kiangah, “Mite in keimah, \w Mihing Tapa\w*, kua hi hong ci uh hiam?” ci in a dong hi. 
\p 
\v 14 \x + \xo 16:14 \xt Mak 6:15; Joh 1:21\x*Amaute in a genin ah, “Mi pawlkhat in, Tuiphumpa John, pawlkhat in Elijah, pawlkhat in Jeremiah, ahih keileh kamsangte khat peuhpeuh hi hong ci uh hi,” ci in a dawng uh hi. 
\p 
\v 15 Amah in amaute kiangah, “Tua ahih leh note in kei kua hi nong ci uh hiam?” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 16 \x + \xo 16:16 \xt Lat 42:2; Jer 10:10; Saw 14:15; 2Co 6:16; 1Th 1:9; 1Ti 3:15; Heb 10:31\x*Tua ciangin Simon Peter in, “Nang in a nungta Pasian Tapa, Khazih na hi hi,” ci in a dawng hi. 
\p 
\v 17 \x + \xo 16:17 \xt 1Co 15:50; Eph 6:12; Heb 2:14\x*Zeisu in, “Jonah tapa Simon aw, mi hampha na hi hi; banghang hiam cihleh hih thu ci le sa in hong theihsak hi loin vana om ka Pa in hong theihsak ahi hi. 
\v 18 \x + \xo 16:18 \xt Joh 1:42; Eph 2:20\x*Ken kong cih in ah nang in Peter na hi hi. Hih suangpi tungah ka pawlpi ka lam ding a, \w Hades\w* kongpite in a zo kei ding uh hi. 
\v 19 \x + \xo 16:19 \xt Isa 22:22; Joh 20:23; Kil 3:7\x*Vantung kumpigam kong honna tawhtang nang kong pia ding hi. Leitung a na hen khempeuh vantung ah kihen ding a, leitung a na phel khempeuh zong vantung ah kiphel ding hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 20 \x + \xo 16:20 \xt Mak 8:30\x*Tua ciangin amah Zeisu Khazih ahihlam a nungzuite in kuama kiangah a gen loh nadingun khauhtakin a kham hi. 
\s1 Zeisu In A Sih Ding Genkhol 
\r Mak 8:31-9:1; Luk 9:22-27 
\p 
\v 21 \x + \xo 16:21 \xt Lat 22:6; Isa 53:3; Hos 6:2; Mak 9:31; Luk 9:22, 51; 17:25; 24:21, 46; Joh 2:19; 18:22; Saw 2:23; 1Co 15:3-4\x*Tua huna kipan Zeisu in Jerusalem khuapi ah pai in makaite, siampi liante le \w thukhamhilh siate\w* tung panin gimna tampi a thuak nadingte le tua mite in amah thatin a ni thum ni ciangin a kithawhkiksak nading thute a nungzuite kiangah a sianggen hi. 
\p 
\v 22 Tua ciangin Peter in amah samkhia a, “Topa aw, hih thu nang tawh kipelh henla hih thu nang tungah piang kei tapeuh hen,” ci in a taii hi. 
\p 
\v 23 Ahih hangin Peter lamah Zeisu kihei a, “\w Satan\w* aw, ka nunglam ah kihemkhia in. Pasian thu sangin mihing thu ngaihsut in nei zaw na hih manin keima suihkhak ding na na hi hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 24 \x + \xo 16:24 \xt Luk 14:27\x*Tua ciangin Zeisu in a nungzuite kiangah, “Kei hong zui nuam mi peuhmah in ama pumpi deihna nial henla, a singlamteh pua in ka nung hong zui hen. 
\v 25 \x + \xo 16:25 \xt Joh 12:25\x*Banghang hiam cihleh ama nuntakna a huu nuam mi in a nuntakna a tan ding hi. Keima hanga a nuntakna a tan mi in a nuntakna a ngah ding hi. 
\v 26 Banghang hiam cihleh mi khat in leitung buppi a ngah hangin ama nuntakna a suplawh leh bang phattuamna om ding ahi hiam? Ahih keileh mi khatpeuh in ama nuntakna bang tawh khekkik thei ding ahi hiam? 
\v 27 \x + \xo 16:27 \xt Job 34:11; Lat 28:4; 62:12; Pau 24:12; Jer 17:10; Eze 18:20; Luk 17:30; Joh 14:3; Saw 1:11; Rom 2:6; 1Co 1:7; 2Co 5:10; 1Th 2:19; Kil 1:7; 22:12\x*A Pa minthanna le ama vantungmite tawh Mihing Tapa hong pai ciangin mi khempeuh amau sepna ciat zui in thaman a pia ding hi. 
\v 28 A man takpi kong cihin ah, hihlai ah a ding mi pawlkhat in Mihing Tapa, ama kumpigam sungah hong pai a muh matengun sihna a ciam kei ding uh hi,” a ci hi. 
\c 17 
\s1 Mel Kikhelna 
\r Mak 9:2-13; Luk 9:28-36 
\p 
\v 1 Ni guk khit ciangin Zeisu in Peter, James le a sanggampa Johnte samin mual sang khat tungah amau teng bek a paipih hi. 
\v 2 Amaute mai ah ama mel kikhel in a maitang ni bangin tanga a puante khuavak bangin a tee deldel hi. 
\v 3 En in, amaute kiangah Moses le Elijah hong kilangin Zeisu tawh a kiho uh hi. 
\p 
\v 4 Tua ciangin Peter in Zeisu kiangah, “Topa aw, hihlai nuam ka sa uh hi. Hoih na sak leh nang aa ding buuk khat, Moses aa ding buuk khat, Elijah aa ding buuk khat, buuk thum kong lamsak ding uh hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 5 \x + \xo 17:5 \xt Saw 3:22-23\x*Amah a pau laitakin meiingo khat in amaute tuam a, tua meii sung panin, “Hihpa in hong lungdamsak mahmah ka it ka Tapa ahi hi. Ama thu na mang un!” ci in aw khat hong gingkhia hi. 
\p 
\v 6 A nungzuite in tua awging a zak uh ciangin lau mahmah uh a, lei ah a bok uh hi. 
\v 7 Ahih hangin Zeisu hong pai in amaute lawng a, “Tho un. Lau kei un,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 8 Amaute a khuadaktoh uh ciangin Zeisu longal kuamah dang a mu nawn kei uh hi. 
\v 9 \x + \xo 17:9 \xt Mak 8:30\x*Mual tung pan hong kumsuk uh ciangin Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “\w Mihing Tapa\w* misite lak pan a kithawhkiksak matengin hih na muhte uh kuama kiangah gen kei un,” ci in thu a pia hi. 
\v 10 A nungzuite in, “Tua ahih leh \w thukhamhilh siate\w* in banghang in Elijah hong pai masa ding hi ci uh ahi hiam?” ci in a dong uh hi. 
\p 
\v 11 \x + \xo 17:11 \xt Mal 4:6; Luk 1:16-17\x*Zeisu in dawng a, “Elijah hong pai masa takpi dinga na khempeuh a bawlthak ding hi. 
\v 12 Ahih hangin ken kong cih in ah Elijah hong pai khin a, amaute in amah thei lo uh ahih manin a ut bangbang un a bawl uh hi. Tua mah bangin Mihing Tapa in zong tua mite khut sungah gimna a thuak ding hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 13 Tua ciangin a nungzuite in Tuiphumpa John a cihna ahihlam a thei uh hi. 
\s1 Dawilut Khat Kidamsak 
\r Mak 9:14-29; Luk 9:37-43 
\p 
\v 14 Mi honpite kiang a tun uh ciangin mi khat hong pai in ama mai ah khukdin a, 
\v 15 “Topa aw, ka tapa hong hehpih in. Amah in sibup natna vei in nasia mahmah a, meikhuk sung khawng, tuisung khawng ah a tuk pahpah hi. 
\v 16 Na nungzuite kiangah ka paipih hangin a damsak zo kei uh hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 17 Tua ciangin Zeisu in, “Upna a nei lo, a lehtat khang mite aw, bang tanvei hong ompih lai in bang tanvei hong thuak lai ding ka hi hiam? Tua naupang ka kiangah hong paipih un,” a ci hi. 
\v 18 Zeisu in tua dawi a taii ciangin naupangno sung pan taikhia a, thakhatin naupangno a dam hi. 
\p 
\v 19 Tua ciangin nungzuite amau guak Zeisu kiangah hong tuam pai uh a, “Banghang in kote in tua dawi hawlkhia zo lo ka hi uh hiam?” ci in a dong uh hi. 
\p 
\v 20 \x + \xo 17:20 \xt Luk 17:6; 1Co 13:2\x*Zeisu in, “Na up loh man uh ahi hi. A man takpi kong cihin ah, ankamtang cia upna nei le uh teh, ‘Hih mualpi kiangah hih mun panin hualai ah va kikhinkhia in,’ ci le uh teh zong kikhinkhia ding hi. Note aa dingin a piang thei lo bangmah a om kei ding hi. 
\v 21 Ahi zongin hih bang dawi namte thungetna le antanna lo tawh a paikhia kei hi,” a ci hi. 
\s1 Zeisu In A Sih Ding Nihvei A Genkholhna 
\r Mak 9:30-32; Luk 9:43-45 
\p 
\v 22 Galilee gam ah a taam sungun Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Mihing Tapa mite khut ah hong kilehhek ding hita hi. 
\v 23 Amaute in amah that ding uh a, a ni thum ni in a kithokiksak ding hi,” a cih ciangin amaute a dah mahmah uh hi. 
\s1 Siah Piakna 
\p 
\v 24 \x + \xo 17:24 \xt Pai 30:13\x*Capernaum khua a tun uh ciangin Peter kiangah \w biakinnpi siah\w* a dongte va pai uh a, “Na siapa in biakinnpi siah pia lo ahi hiam?” ci in a dot uh ciangin 
\v 25 \x + \xo 17:25 \xt Rom 13:7\x*Peter in, “Pia mah hi,” a ci hi. 
\p Inn sungah Peter a lut phetin Zeisu in na hopih masa a, “Simon aw, bang na ci ngaihsut hiam? Leitung kumpite in mangmu ahi a, mimal \w siah\w* ahi zongin a don uh ciangin a tate uh tung pan dong uh ahi hiam ahih keileh midangte tung pan dong zaw uh ahi hiam?” ci in a dong hi. 
\p 
\v 26 Peter in, “Midangte tung panin dong zaw uh hi,” a cih ciangin Zeisu in, “Tua ahih leh a tate a kimap ahi hi. 
\v 27 \x + \xo 17:27 \xt Joh 6:61\x*Ahi zongin amaute a puksak i suah khak loh nadingin tuili ah pai in ngakawi va siah in. A awk masa penpen a kam phen leteh shekel\f + \fr 17:27 \fk shekel\ft : Greek kam in “stater” hi. A nunga Vantehnate nuai ah “stater” en in.\f* khat na mu ding hi. Tua shekel la inla, nang aa ding le kei aa dingin siah va pia in,” a ci hi. 
\c 18 
\s1 Vantung Kumpigam Sungah Kua Lianpen 
\r Mak 9:33-39; Luk 9:46-48 
\p 
\v 1 Tua laitakin Zeisu kiangah a nungzuite hong pai uh a, “Vantung kumpigam sungah kua lianpen ding ahi hiam?” ci in a dong uh hi. 
\p 
\v 2 Zeisu in naupangno khat samin, amaute laizang ah dingsak a, 
\v 3 \x + \xo 18:3 \xt 1Pe 2:2\x*“A man takpi kong cihin ah, kikhel a naupangnote na bat kei uh leh vantung kumpigam sungah na lut thei ngei kei ding uh hi. 
\v 4 \x + \xo 18:4 \xt Mak 9:35\x*Tua ahih manin hih naupangno bang a, a kiniamkhiatte in vantung kumpigam sungah a lianpen ahi ding uh hi. 
\v 5 Keima min hanga hih bang naupangno khat a sang mi in kei zong a hong sang ahi hi. 
\s1 Naupangnote Khat A Khialsak Mi 
\r Mak 9:42-50 
\p 
\v 6 \x + \xo 18:6 \xt Mak 9:42; Luk 17:2\x*“Ahi zongin, kei hong um hih naupangnote khat a puksak mi khatpeuh in a ngawng ah angawina suang khih henla tuipi sungah kikhia leh ama aa dingin a hoihzaw ding hi. 
\p 
\v 7 \x + \xo 18:7 \xt Luk 17:1\x*“Khialh theih nading thute hangin leitung in gimna a thuak ding hi! Banghang hiam cihleh khialh theih nading thute a om ding mah hi a, ahi zongin a khial sak mi in gimna a thuak ding hi! 
\v 8 Tua ahih manin na khut khat na khe khat in hong khialh sak leh sattan inla pai in. Khutkim khekim tawh tawntung meikuangpi sungah hong kikhiat sangin khuttawng khetawng a poisa in nuntakna sungah lut leteh nang aa dingin a hoihzaw ding hi. 
\v 9 Tua ahih ciangin na mit in hong khialh sak leh khelkhia inla pai in. Mittang nih tawh \w hell\w* meikuang sungah hong kikhiat sangin mittang khat bek tawh nuntakna sungah lut leteh nang aa dingin a hoihzaw hi. 
\s1 Tuu Mang Thugentehna 
\r Luk 15:1-7 
\p 
\v 10 \x + \xo 18:10 \xt Pian 48:16; Lat 34:7; Saw 12:11, 15; Heb 1:14\x*“Hih naupangnote khatpeuh na simmawh khak loh nadingun kidawm un; banghang hiam cihleh amau vantungmite in vana om ka Pa maitang a mu den uh hi. 
\v 11 Banghang hiam cihleh \w Mihing Tapa\w* in a mangthang mite honkhia dinga hong pai ahi hi. 
\p 
\v 12 “Note in bangci ngaihsut na hi uh hiam? Mi khat in tuu 100 a neih lak panin khat gammang leh 99te nusia in, tua a gammang zong dingin mual tung lamah kuankhia lo ding ahi hiam? 
\v 13 Note kiangah a man takpi kong cihin ah, tua tuu mang khat a muh ciangin, a lungdamna pen a gammang lo 99te hanga a lungdamna sangin a lianzaw ding hi. 
\v 14 Tua mah bangin hih naupangnote khat nangawn a kisiat ding vantung a om na Pa un a deih kei hi. 
\s1 A Khial Sanggampa 
\r Luk 17:3, 4 
\p 
\v 15 \x + \xo 18:15 \xt Siam 19:17; Luk 17:3; Gal 6:1; Jam 5:19-20\x*“Tua tham loin mi khat nang tungah hong khialh leh, a kiangah pai inla note gel kia theih in, a khialhna va gen in. Na thu hong man leh tua pa a zo na hi hi. 
\v 16 \x + \xo 18:16 \xt Gam 35:30; Thu 17:6; Joh 8:17; 2Co 13:1; 1Ti 5:19; Heb 10:28\x*Nangma thu a hong man nop keileh, \qt thu khempeuh teci nih bang thum bang thugenna tawh a kip theih nadingin,\qt*\f + \fr 18:16 \ft \+xt Thu 19:15\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* mi khat le nih tawh va pai in. 
\v 17 \x + \xo 18:17 \xt Rom 16:17; 1Co 6:1-6\x*Tua mite thu a nial lai leh pawlpi tungah ko in. Pawlpi thu nangawn a nial leh lawki le \w siahdongte\w* bangin na omsak in. 
\p 
\v 18 \x + \xo 18:18 \xt Mat 16:19; Joh 20:23\x*“A man takpi kong cihin ah, leitung a note hen khempeuh vantung ah kihen ding a, leitung a note phel khempeuh zong vantung ah kiphel ding hi. 
\p 
\v 19 \x + \xo 18:19 \xt Mat 7:7\x*“Khatvei kong genkik in ah leitung ah mi nih kilungtuak a thu a nget uh leh a nget peuhpeuh uh vantung a om ka Pa in a pia ding hi. 
\v 20 \x + \xo 18:20 \xt Mat 28:20\x*Banghang hiam cihleh keima min tawh nih le thum bang a kikhop uh ciangin amaute laizang ah ka om hi,” ci in Zeisu in a gen hi. 
\s1 Hehpihna Nei Lo Nasempa 
\p 
\v 21 \x + \xo 18:21 \xt Mat 6:14; Luk 17:4\x*Tua khit ciangin ama kiangah Peter hong pai a, “Topa aw, ka sanggampa in ka tungah hong khialh leh bangzah vei ka maisak ding hiam? Sagihvei dongin ka maisak ding hiam?” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 22 \x + \xo 18:22 \xt Pian 4:24\x*Zeisu in, “Sagihvei dongin na maisak in kong ci kei hi. 70 mun sagihvei dongin maisak in kong ci hi. 
\v 23 \x + \xo 18:23 \xt Mat 13:24; 25:19\x*Tua ahih manin vantung kumpigam in a nasemte sum sazian a sittel nuam kumpipa tawh kibang hi. 
\v 24 Amah in sum sazian a sit laitakin \w talent\w* 10,000 a bapa khat ama kiangah hong paipih uh hi. 
\v 25 \x + \xo 18:25 \xt Siam 25:39; 2Ku 4:1; Neh 5:5, 8; Luk 7:42\x*Amah in a leiba loh zo lo ahih manin a pu in amah le a zi a tate a kipan a neihsa khempeuh zuak a, a leiba a loh nadingin thu a pia hi. 
\p 
\v 26 “Tua ciangin tua nasempa zong kumpipa mai ah bok in, ‘Pu aw, hong ngak keikai lai in a vekpi in nang kong loh ding hi,’ a ci hi. 
\v 27 A topa in tua nasempa khasiathuaisa ahih manin a leiba teng maisak in a khah hi. 
\p 
\v 28 “Tua nasempa paikhia a, ama sum \w denarius\w* 100 a ba a lawm nasem dang khat tawh a kituak hi. Amah in tua pa manin gawlmek a, ‘Nong sum bat hong loh in,’ a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 29 “A lawm silapa zong a khephung ah bokin, ‘Hong ngak keikai lai in a vekpi in nang kong loh ding hi,’ ci in a thum hi. 
\p 
\v 30 “Ahih hangin tua pa in mang zo lo a, a leiba khempeuh a loh khit mateng a lawmpa thong sungah a khum hi. 
\v 31 A lawm nasem dangte in tua thupiang teng a theih uh ciangin lungnuam het lo uh a, a pu uh kiangah pai in thupiang teng a ko uh hi. 
\p 
\v 32 “Tua ciangin a pu in tua pa samsak a, ‘Nang a gilo nasempa aw, nong thum manin na leiba khempeuh kong maisak hi. 
\v 33 Nang kong hehpih bangin na lawm nasempa na hehpih ding kilawm hi lo ahi hiam?’ a ci hi. 
\v 34 A pu hehlua ahih manin a leiba khempeuh a loh khit matengin mi bawlsiate khut sungah tua nasempa a pia hi. 
\p 
\v 35 \x + \xo 18:35 \xt Jam 2:13\x*“Note in zong na sanggampa nang tunga a hong khialhnate na lungsim panin na maisak keileh vantung a om ka Pa in tua mah bangin nang tungah a hong bawl ding hi,” a ci hi. 
\c 19 
\s1 Kimakna 
\r Mat 5:1-32; Mak 10:2-12; Luk 16:18 
\p 
\v 1 Zeisu in hih thute a gen khit ciangin Galilee gam panin Jordan Gun galkhat a om Judea gam ah a pai hi. 
\v 2 Mi tampi in amah zui uh a, amah in amaute tua munah a damsak hi. 
\p 
\v 3 \w Pharisee\w* pawlte zong hong pai uh a, “Mi khat in thu khatpeuh hangin a zi a mak ding thukham tawh a kituak hiam?” ci in a ze-et uh hi. 
\p 
\v 4 \x + \xo 19:4 \xt Pian 5:2\x*Zeisu in dawngkik a, “Amaute a bawlpa in a kipatcil in \qt pasal le numei a bawl hi\qt*\f + \fr 19:4 \ft \+xt Pian 1:27; 5:2\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* cih thu sim kha ngei lo na hi uh hiam?” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 5 \x + \xo 19:5 \xt 1Co 6:16; Eph 5:31\x*Amah in, “\qt Tua ahih manin pasal in a nu le a pa nusia in a zi tawh kigawm ding a, Amaute gel pumkhat a suak ding uh hi.\qt*\f + \fr 19:5 \ft \+xt Pian 2:24\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* 
\v 6 Tua hi a, amaute nih hi nawn loin pumkhat ahi uh hi. Tua ahih manin Pasian in a gawmsate mihing in khen kei tahen,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 7 \x + \xo 19:7 \xt Thu 24:1-4\x*Tua ciangin amaute in, “Tua ahih leh banghang in Moses in kimakna lai pia a zi mak theih nading thu hong pia ahi hiam?” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 8 Amah in, “Na lungtang uh khauhlua ahih manin zi na mak theih nadingun Moses in hong phal ahi hi. Ahih hangin a kipatcil in tua bang ahi kei hi. 
\v 9 \x + \xo 19:9 \xt Luk 16:18\x*Note kiangah ken kong cih in ah numei pasal mawhna hang longal thu dang hangin a zi ma a numei dang khat a teenpihpa in angkawm ahi hi. A kimasa numei a teenpihpa zong angkawm mah ahi hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 10 Tua ciangin a nungzuite in, “Nupa vai tua bang ding ahih leh zi nei lo a om ding hoihzaw hi,” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 11 \x + \xo 19:11 \xt 1Co 7:7-9, 17\x*Tua ciangin amah in, “Mi khempeuh in hih thu a sangkim zo kei uh hi. Pasian in a tuam vilvel a a piakte bekin a sang zo uh hi. 
\v 12 A nu gil sung panin gehsa banga a suak pawl a om hi. \w A kiget\w* tawm pawl zong oma pawl khatte ahih leh vantung kumpigam thu hangin geh bangin a om uh hi. Hih thu a sang zote in sang un,” a ci hi. 
\s1 Naupangte Thupha Pia 
\r Mak 10:13-16; Luk 18:15-17 
\p 
\v 13 \x + \xo 19:13 \xt Mak 5:23\x*Zeisu in naupangte tungah a khut nga a thu a ngetsak theih nadingin mite in naupangte hong paipih uh hi. Ahih hangin nungzuite in amaute na taiigawp uh hi. 
\p 
\v 14 \x + \xo 19:14 \xt 1Pe 2:2\x*Zeisu in, “Naupangte ka kiangah hong pai ding kham kei unla hong paisak zaw un. Vantung kumpigam in naupang tawh a kibangte aa ahi hi,” a ci hi. 
\v 15 Tua khit ciangin naupangte tungah a khut nga a tua mun panin a paikhia hi. 
\s1 A Hau Tangvalpa 
\r Mak 10:17-31; Luk 18:18-30 
\p 
\v 16 \x + \xo 19:16 \xt Luk 10:25\x*Tu in, en in, ama kiangah mi khat hong pai a, “Sia hoih aw, nuntak tawntungna ka ngah theih nadingin a pha bang ka bawl ding hiam?” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 17 \x + \xo 19:17 \xt Siam 18:5\x*Tua ciangin Zeisu in, “Banghang in mi hoih hong ci na hi hiam? Pasian khatbek longal a hoih kuamah a om kei hi. Ahi zongin, nuntakna sungah na lut nop leh thupiakte na zui in,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 18 \x + \xo 19:18 \xt Jam 2:11\x*Amah in, “Bang thukham teng zui ding ka hi hiam?” a cih ciangin Zeisu in, “\qt Mi that kei in. Angkawm kei in. Gu kei in. A man loin teci pang kei in.\qt* 
\v 19 \qt Na nu le na pa zahtak in\qt*\f + \fr 19:19 \ft \+xt Pai 20:12-16; Thu 5:16-20\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f*. \qt Nang le nang na ki-it bangin na vengpa it in,\qt*\f + \fr 19:19 \ft \+xt Siam 19:18\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f*” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 20 Tangvalpa in, “Tuate khempeuh ka neutunga kipan ka zuihsa ahi hi. Bang kisam lai ka hi hiam?” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 21 \x + \xo 19:21 \xt Mat 5:48; Saw 2:45\x*Zeisu in, “A hoihkim a ut taktak na hih leh pai inla na neihsa teng zuak in mi zawngte pia leteh vantung ah sum na nei ding hi. Tua khit ciangin hong pai inla ka nung hong zui in,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 22 Tangvalpa in tua thu a zak ciangin maikhingsa in a paikhia hi; banghang hiam cihleh amah mi hau mahmah khat ahi hi. 
\p 
\v 23 \x + \xo 19:23 \xt 1Ti 6:9-10\x*Tua khit ciangin Zeisu in a nungzuite kiangah, “A man takpi kong cihin ah, mi haute vantung kumpigam sung a lut nading uh haksa mahmah hi. 
\v 24 Note kiangah khatvei kong cihkik in ah mi hau khat Pasian kumpigam sungah a lut ding sangin kalaoh khat phimbilvang sungah khum ding baih zaw hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 25 A nungzuite in hih thu a zak uh ciangin lamdangsa mahmah uh a, “Tua bang ahih leh kua in hotkhiatna ngah zo ding ahi hiam?” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 26 \x + \xo 19:26 \xt Pian 18:14; Job 42:2; Jer 32:17; Luk 1:37; Rom 4:21\x*Zeisu in amaute en in a genin ah, “Hih thu mihing tawh a piang thei lo mah ahi hi. Ahi zongin Pasian tawh na khempeuh a piang thei hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 27 Tua ciangin Peter in ama kiangah, “En in, kote in na khempeuh nusia in nang hong zui ka hih manun bang ngah ding ka hi uh hiam?” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 28 \x + \xo 19:28 \xt Luk 22:28-30; Kil 3:21\x*Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “A man takpi kong cihin ah, bawlthak hun ah \w Mihing Tapa\w* in ama minthanna kumpi tokhom tungah hong tut hun ciangin kei hong zui note in kumpi tokhom sawm le nih tungah tu in Israel nam sawm le nam nihte tungah thu na khen ding uh hi. 
\v 29 \x + \xo 19:29 \xt Mat 6:33\x*Keima min hangin a inn, a sanggampa, a sanggamnu, a pa, a nu, a zi, a tate le a lote khat peuhpeuh a nusia mi in a zah 100 ngah ding a, nuntak tawntungna zong a luah ding hi. 
\v 30 \x + \xo 19:30 \xt Mak 10:31; Luk 13:30\x*Ahi zongin a masa mi tampite nunung ding uh a, a nunung mi tampite a masa ding uh hi,” a ci hi. 
\c 20
\s1 Lenggahhuan A Nasemte
\p
\v 1 “Banghang hiam cihleh vantung kumpigam in ama lenggahhuan a nasem ding mi a cial dingin zingsang tunga a kuankhia lo neipa tawh kibang hi.
\v 2 Tu in, nitha \w denarius\w* khat piak dingin nasemte tawh kithukim uh a, lenggah huanah amaute a kuansak hi.
\p
\v 3 “Nai thum\f + \fr 20:3 \fk Nai thum\ft : Zingsang nai kua cihna hi.\f* pawl ciangin loneipa a paikhiat leh vanzuakna phual ah sepmel nei loin a mawk om mi pawlkhat a mu hi.
\v 4 Amaute kiangah zong, ‘Ka lenggah huanah va kuan un. Thaman a kilawm zah kong pia ding hi,’ a cih ciangin amaute zong a kuan uh hi.
\v 5 Nai guk\f + \fr 20:5 \fk Nai guk\ft : Sun nai sawm le nai nih cihna hi.\f* le nai kua\f + \fr 20:5 \fk Nai kua\ft : Nitak nai thum a cihna hi.\f* pawlin khatvei, paikhiakik a tua mah bangin a va cial hi.
\v 6 Nai sawm le nai khat\f + \fr 20:6 \fk Nai sawm le nai khat\ft : Nitak nai nga a cihna hi.\f* pawlin zong paikhia a, a mawk om mi pawlkhat a muh ciangin amaute kiangah, ‘Banghang in hihlai ah sun thapai in mawk om na hi uh hiam?’ a ci hi.
\p
\v 7 “Amaute in, ‘Kuamah in hong cial lo hi,’ a cih uh ciangin amah in, ‘Note zong ka lenggah huanah va kuan un. Thaman a kilawm zah kong pia ding hi,’ a ci hi.
\p
\v 8 \x + \xo 20:8 \xt Siam 19:13; Thu 24:15\x*“Nitak ciangin lenggah loneipa in nasem ukpa kiangah, ‘Nasemte sam inla, a kuan nunung pen pan a kuan masa pen dongin a thaman uh pia in,’ a ci hi.
\p
\v 9 “Tua ciangin nai sawm le nai khat\f + \fr 20:9 \fk nai sawm le nai khat\ft : A neu gukna en in.\f* pawla a cialte hong pai uh a, denarius khat ciat a ngah uh hi.
\v 10 A kuan masate hong pai uh ciangin a tamzaw ngah dingin kilamen uh a, ahi zongin amaute in zong denarius khat ciat bek mah a ngah uh hi.
\v 11 Tua banga a ngah uh ciangin lo neipa phunsan uh a,
\v 12 \x + \xo 20:12 \xt Luk 12:55; Jam 1:11\x*‘Hih a kuan nunungte in nai khat sung bek nasem man uh hi napi in sun thapai nisa thuakin a gim mahmah kote tawh thaman a kikim na ngahsak veve hi,’ a ci uh hi.
\p
\v 13 “Ahih hangin loneipa in amaute laka khatpa kiangah, ‘Lawm aw, na tungah ka khial kei hi. Denarius khat piak ding mah a thukim hi lo na hi hiam?
\v 14 Na thaman ding la inla ciah in. Hih a kuan nunung penpa zong nang aa zah mah ka pia nuam hi.
\v 15 \x + \xo 20:15 \xt Thu 15:9; Mak 7:22\x*Keima neihsa ka ut bangbang a ka zek theih hi lel lo ahi hiam? Ka cit, ka siam manin nang heh laizang ding na hi hiam?’ a ci hi.
\p
\v 16 “Tua ahih manin a nunungte masa ding uh a, a masate a nunung ding uh hi; banghang hiam cihleh a kisam mi a tam hangin a kiteel mi a tawm hi,” a ci hi.
\s1 Zeisu In A Sih Ding Genkhol
\r Mak 10:32-34; Luk 18:31-34
\p
\v 17 Tu in Jerusalem khuapi ah Zeisu a paitoh kawmin lampi ah sawm le nihte tuam tonpihin thu a hilh hi.
\v 18 \x + \xo 20:18 \xt Luk 9:51\x*Amah in, “En un, Jerusalem khuapi ah i paito ding hi. Siampi liante le \w thukhamhilh siate\w* tungah \w Mihing Tapa\w* kilehhek ding a, amaute in thah dingin thu a khen ding uh hi.
\v 19 \x + \xo 20:19 \xt Saw 2:23\x*Amaute in Gentilete zahko ding, sat ding le khailup dingin amah pia ding uh a, a ni thum ni in a thokik ding hi,” a ci hi.
\s1 Nupi Khat Ngetna
\r Mak 10:35-45
\p
\v 20 \x + \xo 20:20 \xt Mat 4:21\x*Tua khit ciangin Zebedee tapate nu in nget nop khat nei ahih manin a tapate tawh Zeisu kiangah pai in, a mai ah a khukdin uh hi.
\p
\v 21 Tua ciangin Zeisu in nupinu kiangah, “Bang deih na hi hiam?” ci in a dong hi.
\p Tua nu in, “Na kumpigam sungah hih ka tapa nihte na taklam ah khat na veilam ah khat na tutsak ding ka deih hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 22 \x + \xo 20:22 \xt Isa 51:17, 22; Jer 49:12; Mak 14:36; Luk 22:42; Joh 18:11\x*Ahih hangin Zeisu in, “Nong nget uh bang hiam cih na thei kei uh hi. A sawt lo a ka dawn ding hai dawn zo ding na hi uh hiam? Ka kibaptize na ah kibaptize zo ding na hi uh hiam?” a cih ciangin amaute in, “Ka hih zo ding uh hi,” a ci uh hi.
\p
\v 23 \x + \xo 20:23 \xt Saw 12:2; Kil 1:9\x*Tua ciangin amah in, “Ka dawn ding hai na dawn takpi ding uh a, ka kibaptize na ah zong na kibaptize takpi ding uh hi. Ahih hangin ka taklam le ka veilam a tut theih nading thu pen kei hong piak theih hi loin ka Pa in a sehkholhsa mite aa ding ahi hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 24 \x + \xo 20:24 \xt Luk 22:24-25\x*A dang sawmte in tua thu a zak uh ciangin tua unau nihte tungah a lungkim kei uh hi.
\v 25 Ahi zongin Zeisu in amaute samkhawm a, “Gentilete sungah ukna neite in a mipite uh ukcip uh a, a miliante un a mipite tungah thuneihna zang uh hi cih na thei uh hi.
\v 26 \x + \xo 20:26 \xt Mak 9:35\x*Ahi zongin note sungah tua bang ding hi lo hi. Note lakah a lian a suak nuam peuhmah in note nasem hi tahen.
\v 27 Note lakah a masa pen a suak nuamte in note sila hi tahen.
\v 28 \x + \xo 20:28 \xt Pai 30:12; Isa 42:1; 44:22; Luk 12:37; Joh 13:13-16; 2Co 8:9; Phi 2:7; 1Ti 2:6; Tit 2:14; Heb 9:28; 1Pe 1:18-19\x*Mihing Tapa nangawn ama na a kisepsak dinga hong pai hi lo hi. Midangte na a sepsak ding le a nuntakna pia in mi tampi a tankhia dinga hong pai ahi hi,” a ci hi.
\s1 Mittaw Nihte In Khuamu
\r Mak 10:46-52; Luk 18:35-43
\p
\v 29 Jericho khua pan a paikhiat uh ciangin mi honpi in Zeisu nung a zui uh hi.
\v 30 Tua ciangin lam gei a tu mittaw nihin amaute lamah Zeisu hong pai hi cih a zak uh ciangin, “David Tapa, Topa aw, kote hong hehpih in,” ci in a kiko uh hi.
\p
\v 31 Amaute a daih nadingun mi honpi in a taiihuan uh hi. Ahih hangin amaute in, “David Tapa, Topa aw, kote hong hehpih in,” ci in nakpi in a kiko semsem uh hi.
\p
\v 32 Tua ciangin Zeisu khawla amaute sam in, “Bang kong hihsak ding ut na hi uh hiam?” a ci hi.
\p
\v 33 Amaute in, “Topa aw, khua nong muhsak ding ka ut uh hi,” a ci uh hi.
\p
\v 34 Zeisu in amaute hehpihhuai sa in a mit uh a lawnsak leh thakhatin khuamu pah uh a, ama nung a zui uh hi.
\c 21 
\s1 Gualzo A Lutna 
\r Mak 11:1-10; Luk 19:28-40; Joh 12:12-19 
\p 
\v 1 \x + \xo 21:1 \xt Mak 14:26; Luk 19:37; Joh 8:1; Saw 1:12\x*Amaute in Jerusalem khuapi tun kuan, Olive Mual kianga om Bethphage khua a tun uh ciangin Zeisu in a nungzuite nih sawl a, 
\v 2 “Note mai a khua ah va pai un. Laapi khat kikhih a om na mu pah ding uh a, a no zong a kiangah na om ding hi. Suut unla hong kai un. 
\v 3 Mi khatpeuh in hong paupih leh, ‘Topa in amaute deih hi,’ ci le uh cin, hong phal pah ding hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 4 Hih thute khempeuh in kamsangpa gensa thute a tangtun nadinga piang ahi hi. 
\v 5 \x + \xo 21:5 \xt Isa 62:11; Zec 9:9\x*Amah in, 
\b 
\q1 “\qt Zion tanu kiangah gen in,\qt*\f + \fr 21:5 \ft \+xt Isa 62:11\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* 
\q1 \qt ‘En in, laapi ta laano tungah tuangin,\qt* 
\q1 \qt Na Kumpipa lungnemtak in,\qt* 
\q1 \qt Na kiangah hong pai hi,’ ci in,\qt*”\f + \fr 21:5 \ft \+xt Zec 9:9\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* 
\m a ci hi. 
\b 
\p 
\v 6 Tua ciangin nungzuite gel zong pai uh a, Zeisu thupiak bangin ahih uh hi. 
\v 7 Laapi le laano hong kai uh a, tuate tungah a puante uh phahin Zeisu a tuangsak uh hi. 
\v 8 \x + \xo 21:8 \xt 2Ku 9:13\x*Mihon tampitak in a puante uh lampi ah phah uh hi. Pawlkhatte in singhiangte khiakin phah uh hi. 
\v 9 \x + \xo 21:9 \xt Luk 2:14\x*A nung le a mai a a pai mi honpite kiko uh a, 
\b 
\q1 “\qt David Tapa tungah Hosanna!\qt* 
\q1 \qt Topa min tawh hong paipa in,\qt* 
\q1 \qt Thupha ngah tahen!\qt*\f + \fr 21:9 \ft \+xt Lat 118:25-26\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* 
\q1 \qt A sangbel munah Hosanna!”\qt* ci in a kiko uh hi. 
\b 
\p 
\v 10 Jerusalem khuapi sung a lut ciangin khuapi sunga om mi khempeuh ciak ngeingai uh a, “Hihpa kua ahi hiam?” ci in khat le khat a kidong uh hi. 
\p 
\v 11 \x + \xo 21:11 \xt Thu 18:15; Luk 7:16, 39; Joh 1:21, 25\x*Mi honpi in, “Galilee gam Nazareth khua mi kamsangpa Zeisu ahi hi,” a ci uh hi. 
\s1 Biakinnpi Siansuahna 
\r Mak 11:15-18; Luk 19:45-48 
\p 
\v 12 \x + \xo 21:12 \xt Pai 30:13; Siam 1:14; Thu 14:26\x*Tua khit ciangin Pasian \w biakinnpi\w* huang sungah Zeisu lut a, biakinnpi huang sungah van lei, van zuak a om mi khempeuh a hawlkhia hi. \w Sumkhekte\w* sabuaite le vakhu zuakte tutphahte zong a lumletsak hi. 
\v 13 Tua khit ciangin amaute kiangah, 
\b 
\q1 “\w Lai Siangtho\w* sungah, ‘\qt Ka inn in thungetna inn kici ding hi,\qt*’\f + \fr 21:13 \ft \+xt Isa 56:7\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* 
\m ci in kigelh hi. 
\b 
\m Ahih hangin note in \qt gutate phualpi\qt*\f + \fr 21:13 \ft \+xt Jer 7:11\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* na suaksak uh hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 14 Biakinnpi huang sunga a om laitakin ama kiangah mittawte le khebaite hong pai uh a, amah in amaute a damsak hi. 
\v 15 \x + \xo 21:15 \xt Luk 19:39\x*Siampi liante le \w thukhamhilh siate\w* in ama bawl nalamdangte mu in, “David Tapa tungah Hosanna!” ci in biakinnpi huang sunga a om naupangnote kikona aw a zak uh ciangin a heh mahmah uh hi. 
\p 
\v 16 Tua ciangin ama kiangah, “Hih naupangte kikona aw na za hiam?” a ci uh hi. 
\p Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Ka za hi, 
\b 
\q1 ‘\qt Naupangnote le nawine naungekte kam panin phatna kicing na gingkhiasak hi,\qt*\f + \fr 21:16 \ft \+xt Lat 8:2\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f*’ 
\m a cihna thu sim ngei lo na hi uh hiam?” a ci hi. 
\b 
\p 
\v 17 \x + \xo 21:17 \xt Mak 11:1; Luk 24:50; Joh 11:1, 18\x*Tua khit ciangin amaute nusia in khuapi sung pan Bethany khualam zuanin paikhia a, tua khua ah a giak hi. 
\s1 Theikung Samsiatna 
\r Mak 11:12-14, 20-26 
\p 
\v 18 Zingsang ciangin khuapi lam zuanin Zeisu hong paikik a, a gil a kial hi. 
\v 19 \x + \xo 21:19 \xt Isa 34:4; Jer 8:13\x*Lamgei ah thei kung khat mu in a phungah a va pai leh a teh longal bangmah a mu kei hi. Tua ciangin Zeisu in, “Tu a kipan na gah ngei nawn peuhmah kei in,” a cih ciangin tua thei kung thakhatin a keugaw hi. 
\p 
\v 20 Nungzuite in a muh uh ciangin, lamdangsa mahmah uh a, “Banghang in hih thei kung keugaw pah zawzen ahi hiam?” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 21 \x + \xo 21:21 \xt Luk 17:6; 1Co 13:2; Jam 1:6\x*Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “A man takpi kong cihin ah, lunghiang loin um taktak le uh teh hih thei kung tunga thupiang bang bek hi loin hih mualpi kiangah zong, ‘Kihemkhia inla tuipi sung kidenna in,’ ci le uh cin tua bangin a piang ding hi. 
\v 22 Upna tawh na nget uh leh na nget peuhpeuh uh a vekpi in na ngah ding uh hi,” a ci hi. 
\s1 Zeisu Thuneihna Kidong 
\r Mak 11:27-33; Luk 20:1-8 
\p 
\v 23 \x + \xo 21:23 \xt Saw 4:7\x*Biakinnpi huang sungah Zeisu lutin thu a hilh laitakin siampi liante le Judah mite makaite ama kiangah va pai uh a, “Bang thuneihna tawh hih nate sem na hi hiam? Hih thuneihna kua in nang hong pia ahi hiam?” ci in a dong uh hi. 
\p 
\v 24 Zeisu in, “Ken zong thu khat kong dong ding hi. Nong dawn theih uh leh hih nate kua thuneihna tawh hih ka hi hiam cih kong gen pan ding hi. 
\v 25 John tuiphumna thu vantung pana thuneihna tawh ahi hiam, mihing pana thuneihna tawh ahi hiam?” a ci hi. 
\p Tua ciangin amaute kikum uh a, “~‘Vantung pana thuneihna tawh hi,’ ci lehang, ‘Tua ahih leh banghang in amah um lo na hi uh hiam?’ hong ci ding hi. 
\v 26 ‘Mihing thuneihna tawh hi,’ ci lehang lah mi khempeuh in John pen kamsangpa a a san khitsa uh ahih manin mihonte kihtakhuai hi,” a kici uh hi. 
\p 
\v 27 Tua ahih manin, “Ka thei kei uh hi,” ci in a dawng uh hi. 
\p Tua ciangin Zeisu in, “Ken zong hih nate bang thuneihna tawh sem ka hi hiam cih note kong gen kei ding hi. 
\s1 Tapa Nih Thugentehna 
\p 
\v 28 “Ahi zongin hih kong gen ding thu bang na ci ngaihsut uh hiam? Mi khat in tapa nih a nei hi. A ta uzawpa kiangah va pai a, ‘Ka ta aw, tuni in ka lenggahhuan ah va kuan in,’ a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 29 “Tua a tapa in, ‘Ka kuan nuam kei hi,’ a cih hangin a nung ciangin kisikkikin a kuan hi. 
\p 
\v 30 “Tua khit ciangin a nauzawpa kiangah pai a, tua mah bangin a gen hi. A tapa in, ‘Pa aw, ka kuan ding hi,’ ci in dawng napi a kuan kei hi. 
\p 
\v 31 \x + \xo 21:31 \xt Luk 7:29, 50\x*“Tua ta nihte kua zaw in a pa deihna mang ahi hiam?” a cih ciangin amaute in, “A upapen in a mang zaw hi,” a ci uh hi. 
\p Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “A man takpi kong cihin ah, \w siahdongte\w* le numei kizuakte in Pasian kumpigam sungah note ma in a lut uh hi. 
\v 32 \x + \xo 21:32 \xt Luk 3:12-13; 7:36-50\x*Banghang hiam cihleh John hong pai in thuman lampi hong lah hangin amah na um kei uh hi. Ahi zongin siahdongte le numei kizuakte in amah a um uh hi. Note in hih thu na muh khit nangawn un kisikin amah na um tuan kei uh hi. 
\s1 Lenggahhuan Le A Khote Thugentehna 
\r Mak 12:1-12; Luk 20:9-19 
\p 
\v 33 \x + \xo 21:33 \xt Lat 80:8; Isa 5:1-7\x*“A dang thugentehna khat na ngai un. Lo neipa khat in lenggahhuan khat bawlin a kimah phung ciangin um a, lenggah cilna phual khat bawlin tausang khat zong a dawh hi. Tua khit ciangin lenggahhuan kho dingin mi cial a, khual gamlapi khat ah a zinkhia hi. 
\v 34 Tu in lenggah lak hun hong nai ta a, lenggahte a kaikhawm dingin lokhawh thalawhte kiangah a nasemte a sawl hi. 
\p 
\v 35 \x + \xo 21:35 \xt 2Kh 24:21; Heb 11:36-37\x*“Lokhawh thalawhte in a nasemte man uh a, khat vuagawp in khat that uh a, a dang khat pen suang tawh a denglum uh hi. 
\v 36 Tua ciangin huan neipa in a sawl masakte sangin a tamzaw a nasemte pawlkhat sawlkik leuleu a, tuate zong a masate a bawl mah bangun a bawl veve uh hi. 
\v 37 A tawpna ah huan neipa in, ‘Ka tapa zahtak kha ding uh hi,’ ci in a tapa a paisak hi. 
\p 
\v 38 \x + \xo 21:38 \xt Lat 2:8; Heb 1:2\x*“Ahih hangin lokhawh thalawhte in a tapa a muh uh ciangin kikum uh a, ‘Hihpa innluah ding pa ahi hi. Pai dih un, amah thatin a luah ding teng sut ni,’ a kici uh hi. 
\v 39 Tua ciangin amah man uh a, lenggahhuan pualam ah kaikhia in a that uh hi. 
\p 
\v 40 “Tua hi a, lenggahhuan neipa hong pai ciangin tua lokhawh thalawhte bang a ci bawl ding hiam?” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 41 \x + \xo 21:41 \xt Saw 13:46\x*Amaute in, “Amah in tua mi gilote nasiatakin a susia ding hi. Lenggah lak hun ciangin loneipa tungah lenggah a ngah zah ding a pia ding a dang lokhawh thalawhte a khosak ding hi,” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 42 \x + \xo 21:42 \xt Saw 4:11\x*Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Lai Siangtho sungah, 
\b 
\q1 ‘\qt Innlamte in a nilkhiat uh suang,\qt* 
\q1 \qt Innkiusuang bulpi a suak hi.\qt* 
\q1 \qt Hih in Topa sep hi a,\qt* 
\q1 \qt Eite muhna ah lamdang hi,\qt*’\f + \fr 21:42 \ft \+xt Lat 118:22-23\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* 
\m ci in a kigelh thu sim ngei lo na hi uh hiam? 
\b 
\p 
\v 43 “Tua ahih manin note kianga kong genin ah, note tung panin Pasian kumpigam kilakhia ding a, a gahsak ding \w minam dangte\w* khat tungah kipia ding hi. 
\v 44 \x + \xo 21:44 \xt Luk 2:34\x*Hih suang tungah mi khatpeuh a kiat leh kitamkham ding a, hih suangin mi khatpeuh a den leh a zanciim ding hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 45 Tu in siampi liante le \w Pharisee\w* pawlte in ama thugentehnate a zak uh ciangin amaute a cihna ahihlam a thei uh hi. 
\v 46 Zeisu mat a sawm uh hangin mi honpi in kamsangpa hi ci in um khin uh ahih manin mi honpi a kihta zel uh hi. 
\c 22 
\s1 Mopawi Thugentehna 
\r Luk 14:15-24 
\p 
\v 1 Zeisu in amaute dawngin thugentehna tawh thu a gen in ah, 
\v 2 “Vantung kumpigam in a tapa aa ding mopawi a bawl kumpipa tawh kibang hi. 
\v 3 Amah in mopawi sim dinga a khohsate sam dingin a nasemte a sawl ciangin tua a khohsate a pai nuam kei uh hi. 
\p 
\v 4 “Amah in nasem dangte sawl leuleu a, ‘Ka khohsate kiangah hih bangin va gen un. “En un, nitak an min khin ta hi. Bawngtalte le ganthaute kigo zo a, na khempeuh a baihsa in om khin hi. Mopawi ah hong pai ta un,” va ci un,’ a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 5 “Ahih hangin amaute in thusim loin, amau utna ciatah a pai uh hi. Khat in lo kuansan a, a dang khat in sumbawl dingin a zinkhiatsan hi. 
\v 6 A dangte in a nasemte manin bawlsia in a that uh hi. 
\v 7 \x + \xo 22:7 \xt Luk 19:27\x*Kumpipa in tua thu a zak ciangin heh mahmah a, a galkapte kuansak in tua mi thatte a thahsak khit ciangin a khua uh zong a haltumsak hi. 
\p 
\v 8 “Tua khit ciangin a nasemte kiangah, ‘Mopawi ankuang kilui khinzo hi. Ahih hangin ka khohsate tua pawi an ne dingin a kilawm kei uh hi. 
\v 9 \x + \xo 22:9 \xt Eze 21:21\x*Tua ahih ciangin lam lianpite ah va pai kawikawi unla mi na muh peuhpeuh uh mopawi ah hong sam un,’ a ci hi. 
\v 10 Tua ciangin nasemte zong lam lianpite ah va pai in mi a muh khempeuh uh mi sia, mi pha a kaihkhop uh ciangin mopawi inn sungah mi a dim hi. 
\p 
\v 11 “Tua pawisimte en dingin kumpipa a lut ciangin mopuan a silh lo mi khat a mu hi. 
\v 12 Tua ciangin amah in, ‘Lawm aw, mopuan silh lopi in banghang in hih mun hong tung thei na hi hiam?’ a cih ciangin tua pa in a dawng thei kei hi. 
\p 
\v 13 “Tua ciangin kumpipa in a nasemte kiangah, ‘Hihpa a khut le a khe hen unla kaikhia in pualam khuamial lakah lawnkhia un. Tualai ah kahna le hagawina a om ding hi.’ 
\p 
\v 14 \x + \xo 22:14 \xt Kil 17:14\x*“A kisam mi a tam hangin a kiteel mi a tawm hi,” a ci hi. 
\s1 Phiangsiah Piakna 
\r Mak 12:13-17; Luk 20:20-26 
\p 
\v 15 Tua khit ciangin \w Pharisee\w* pawlte paikhia uh a, ama kampau mah tawh Zeisu a awksak theih nadingun a kikum uh hi. 
\v 16 \x + \xo 22:16 \xt Mak 3:6\x*Tua khit ciangin amau nungzuite le Herod pawlte Zeisu kiangah a sawl uh hi. Amaute in, “Sia aw, nang mi thuman khat na hi hi. Maitang zahtak tuam nei lo na hih manin angvantuam zong na nei kei a, a mantakin Pasian thu na hilh hi cih kong thei uh hi. 
\v 17 Tua ahih ciangin \w Caesar\w* kumpipa tungah mimal \w siah\w* piakhuai hiam piakhuai lo hiam na ngaihsutna hong gen in,” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 18 Ahih hangin, Zeisu in amaute gitloh gelna thei ahih manin, “A kineihkhem mite aw, banghang in hong ze-et na hi uh hiam? 
\v 19 Mimal siah dinga na piak uh dangkatang khat hong lak un,” a cih ciangin \w denarius\w* tang khat a pia uh hi. 
\p 
\v 20 Amah in, “Hih in kua lim le kua min ahi hiam?” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 21 \x + \xo 22:21 \xt Rom 13:7\x*Amaute in, “Caesar kumpipa min le lim ahi hi,” a ci uh hi. Tua ciangin Zeisu in, “Caesar kumpipa neihsate Caesar kumpipa pia unla Pasian neihsate Pasian pia un,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 22 \x + \xo 22:22 \xt Mak 12:12\x*Amaute in hih thu a zak uh ciangin lamdangsa mahmah uh a, amah nusia in a paikhia uh hi. 
\s1 Thawhkikna Le Kiteenna 
\r Mak 12:18-27; Luk 20:27-39 
\p 
\v 23 \x + \xo 22:23 \xt Saw 4:1; 23:8; 1Co 15:12\x*Tua ni mahin thawhkikna om lo hi a ci Sadduceete pawlkhat hong pai in thu a dong uh hi. 
\v 24 Amaute in, “Sia aw Moses in, \qt ‘Mi khat in ta nei loin a sih leh a naupa in a zi luah henla, a upa aa dingin suan le khak tawisak hen,’\qt*\f + \fr 22:24 \ft \+xt Thu 25:5\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* ci in thu hong pia hi. 
\v 25 Tu in ko kiangah unau pasal sagih a om hi. A upapen in zi nei a, suan le khak nei loin a si hi. Tua ciangin a naupa in a zi a luah hi. 
\v 26 A nihna le a thumna pa a kipan a sagihna dongin tua bangin a piang hi. 
\v 27 A nunung penin tua numei zong a si hi. 
\v 28 Tua ahih teh thawhkik ni ciangin tua numei in unau pasal sagihte sung panin kua pen zi in om ding ahi hiam? Banghang hiam cihleh a vekpi un tua numei a teenpih khin uh hi,” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 29 \x + \xo 22:29 \xt Joh 20:9\x*Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “\w Lai Siangtho\w* ahi a, Pasian vangliatna ahi zongin thei lo na hih manun na sangkhial uh hi. 
\v 30 Thawhkik ni ciangin kipi kiteenna om nawn lo ding a, vana om Pasian vantungmite tawh a kibang ding uh hi. 
\v 31 Misite thawhkikna thu Pasian hong genna sim ngei lo na hi uh hiam? 
\v 32 \x + \xo 22:32 \xt Saw 7:32\x*Amah in, \qt ‘Keimah in Abraham Pasian, Isaac Pasian, Jacob Pasian ka hi hi,’\qt*\f + \fr 22:32 \ft \+xt Pai 3:6, 15\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* a ci hi. Pasian in misite Pasian hi loin, a nungta mite Pasian ahi hi,” ci in a dawng hi. 
\p 
\v 33 Mi honpi in hih thu a zak uh ciangin ama thuhilhna lamdang a sa mahmah uh hi. 
\s1 Thukham Lianpen 
\r Mak 12:28-34 
\p 
\v 34 \x + \xo 22:34 \xt Saw 4:1\x*Zeisu in \w Sadducee\w* pawlte cih nading thei loin a koih lam Pharisee pawlte in a zak uh ciangin a kikhawm uh hi. 
\v 35 \x + \xo 22:35 \xt Luk 7:30\x*Amaute lak panin thukhamhilh sia khatin, Zeisu a ze-etna in thu dong a, 
\v 36 “Sia aw, thukham sung panin a lianpen thupiak bang ahi hiam?” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 37 Zeisu in, “~\qt ‘Na lungsim khempeuh, na nuntakna khempeuh le na ngaihsutna khempeuh tawh Topa na Pasian it in.’\qt*\f + \fr 22:37 \ft \+xt Thu 6:5\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* 
\p 
\v 38 “Hih in a masa le a lianpen thupiak ahi hi. 
\v 39 A nihna in a masa mah tawh a kibang hi a, \qt ‘Nang le nang na ki-it bangin na vengpa na it in,’\qt*\f + \fr 22:39 \ft \+xt Siam 19:18\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* cih thu ahi hi. 
\p 
\v 40 \x + \xo 22:40 \xt Luk 10:25-28\x*“Thukham le Kamsangte laibute khempeuh in hih thupiak nihte pana hong mengkhia ahi hi,” a ci hi. 
\s1 Khazih Kua Tapa hiam? 
\r Mak 12:35-37; Luk 20:41-44 
\p 
\v 41 Phariseete a kikaihkhop laitakun Zeisu in, 
\v 42 “Khazih bang na cih ngaihsut uh hiam? Amah kua tapa ahi hiam?” ci in a dong hi. 
\p Amaute in, “David Tapa ahi hi,” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 43 Zeisu in, “Tua ahih leh banghang in David in Kha theihsakna tawh amah Topa ci thei ahi hiam? 
\v 44 \x + \xo 22:44 \xt 1Ku 5:3; Saw 2:34-35; 1Co 15:25; Heb 1:13\x*David in a genna ah, 
\b 
\q1 \qt ‘Topa in ka Topa kiangah,\qt* 
\q1 \qt “Na galte na khengakna ka suahsak khit mateng in,\qt* 
\q1 \qt Ka taklam ah na tu in,” ci hi,’\qt*\f + \fr 22:44 \ft \+xt Lat 110:1\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* 
\m a ci hi. 
\b 
\p 
\v 45 “David in amah Topa ci ahih leh banghang in ama tapa hi thei zel ding ahi hiam?” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 46 \x + \xo 22:46 \xt Mak 12:34; Luk 20:40\x*Kuamah in kam khat beek dawng thei lo uh ahih manin tua ni a kipan kuamah in thu a dong ngam nawn kei uh hi. 
\c 23 
\s1 Gimna Nam Sagih 
\r Mak 12:38-40; Luk 20:45-47 
\p 
\v 1 Tua khit ciangin Zeisu in mi honpite le a nungzuite thu a hilh hi. 
\v 2 \x + \xo 23:2 \xt Ezr 7:6, 25\x*Amah in, “\w Thukhamhilh siate\w* le \w Pharisee\w* pawlte in Moses tutna a luah uh hi. 
\v 3 Tua ahih manin zuih dinga hong gen khempeuh uh zui unla sem un. Ahi zongin amaute in a gen bangun gamta lo uh ahih manin amaute gamtat bangin gamta kei un. 
\v 4 \x + \xo 23:4 \xt Luk 11:46; Saw 15:10; Gal 6:13\x*Banghang hiam cihleh amaute in midangte liangko tungah a puak hak thei thei ding vangik suan napi uh amaute in tuate a khutme dawn nangawn uh tawh a lawng nuam kei uh hi. 
\p 
\v 5 \x + \xo 23:5 \xt Pai 13:9; Gam 15:38; Thu 6:8; 22:12\x*“A sep a bawl khempeuh uh mite muh theih theih dingin ahih uh hi. Thunget cianga a zat uh \w talsuan\w* le banbulhte a gol thei thei zangin a puanmongtepte uh a sau thei thei in a bawl uh hi. 
\v 6 \x + \xo 23:6 \xt Luk 11:43\x*Pawi annekna ah mun hoih penpen ngah nuam uh a, kikhopna innte ah tutna thupi tata a deih uh hi. 
\v 7 \x + \xo 23:7 \xt Joh 1:38, 49\x*Sumbuuk ah mite in, ‘\w Rabbi\w* aw, Rabbi aw,’ ci in a hopih ding uh a ut uh hi. 
\p 
\v 8 “Khazih khat bek note Siapa hi a, note khempeuh unau khat na hih manun kuamah ‘Rabbi,’ kicisak kei un. 
\v 9 \x + \xo 23:9 \xt Mal 1:6\x*Vantung a om Pa khat bek nei na hih manun leitung ah kuamah pa ci kei un. 
\v 10 Khazih khat bek na Siapa uh ahih manin kuamah sia kicisak kei un. 
\v 11 \x + \xo 23:11 \xt Mak 9:35\x*Note laka a lianpenpa in note nasem ahi ding hi. 
\v 12 \x + \xo 23:12 \xt 1Sa 2:8; Lat 18:27; Pau 3:34; Isa 57:15; Eze 21:26; Luk 1:52\x*Amah le amah a kilamsang mi peuhmah in niamkhiatna thuak dinga a kiniamkhiat mi peuhmah a kilamsang ding hi. 
\p 
\v 13 \x + \xo 23:13 \xt Luk 11:52\x*“A kineih thukhamhilh siate le Pharisee pawlte aw, gimna na thuak ding uh hi! Banghang hiam cihleh vantung kumpigam kong na khak uh a, note lah lut loin a lut nuamte zong na lutsak kei uh hi. 
\v 14 A kineih thukhamhilh siate le Pharisee pawlte aw, gimna na thuak ding uh hi! Meigongte neihsa teng na nektumsak uh a, kineih tawmin thu sau pipi ngen na hih manun a nasiazaw mawhsakna na thuak ding uh hi. 
\p 
\v 15 \x + \xo 23:15 \xt Saw 13:43\x*“A kineih thukhamhilh siate le Pharisee pawlte aw, gimna na thuak ding uh hi! Banghang hiam cihleh mi khat na ngah\f + \fr 23:15 \fk mi khat na ngah\ft : Upna hanga Judah mi a kisuaksakte genna ahi hi.\f* nadingun leitung tuitung tengah na zin kawikawi uh a, na ngah khit uh ciangin note sanga a zah nihin a siazaw \w hell\w* tapa na suaksak uh hi. 
\p 
\v 16 \x + \xo 23:16 \xt Isa 9:16\x*“Lamhilh mittawte aw, gimna na thuak ding uh hi! ‘Mi khatpeuh \w biakinnpi\w* tawh a kiciam leh phamawh loin a sunga kham tawh a kiciam leh a kiciamna in a khih hi,’ na ci uh hi. 
\v 17 \x + \xo 23:17 \xt Pai 30:29\x*Mi hai le mittawte aw! Tua kham le tua kham a siangthosak biakinnpi, koi thupi zaw ahi hiam? 
\v 18 ‘Mi khatpeuh biaknatau tawh a kiciam leh phamawh loin tua tau tunga Pasian a kipia nate tawh a kiciam leh a kiciamna in a khih hi,’ na ci uh hi. 
\v 19 \x + \xo 23:19 \xt Pai 29:37\x*Mi hai le mittawte aw! Pasian a kipia na le tua nate a siangthosak biaknatau koi thupi zaw ahi hiam? 
\v 20 Tua ahih ciangin \w biaknatau\w* tawh a kiciam mi in, biaknatau le a tunga om na khempeuh tawh a kiciam ahi hi. 
\v 21 \x + \xo 23:21 \xt 1Ku 8:13; Lat 26:8\x*Biakinnpi tawh a kiciam mi in biakinnpi le a sunga a teengpa tawh a kiciam ahi hi. 
\v 22 \x + \xo 23:22 \xt Lat 11:4\x*Vantung tawh a kiciam mi in Pasian tokhom le tua tunga a tupa tawh a kiciam ahi hi. 
\p 
\v 23 \x + \xo 23:23 \xt Siam 27:30; Mic 6:8; Luk 11:42\x*“A kineih thukhamhilh siate le Pharisee pawlte aw, gimna na thuak ding uh hi! Banghang hiam cihleh \w lengmasel\w*, samong sapa teh\f + \fr 23:23 \fk samong sapa teh\ft : Samong sapa teh hi lian lo napi a kinai mahmah singteh nam khat hi.\f* le cummin\f + \fr 23:23 \fk cummin\ft : Meh lakah a kisawh (masala) a tang neu nam khat hi.\f*-te sawm a khat na piak uh hangin thukham sunga a thupi zaw ahi mantak a thukhenna, hehpihna le upnate na thudon kei uh hi. A dangte thudon lo tuan loin hih nate na hih veve ding uh ahi hi. 
\v 24 Lamhilh mittawte aw, thosi thovaite na valh khak loh nadingun tui na khaih uh hangin kalaoh na nawmvalh zel uh hi! 
\v 25 \x + \xo 23:25 \xt Mak 7:4; Luk 11:39\x*A kineih thukhamhilh siate le Pharisee pawlte aw, gimna na thuak ding uh hi! Banghang hiam cihleh hai le kuangte a pualam na silsiang uh a, ahi zongin a sunglam huaihamna le uangtat nopna lungsim tawh a kidim hi. 
\v 26 Mittaw Pharisee pawlte aw! Hai le kuangte a pualam a sian theih nadingin a sunglam silsiang masa un. 
\p 
\v 27 \x + \xo 23:27 \xt Luk 11:44; Saw 23:3\x*“A kineihkhem thukhamhilh siate le Pharisee pawlte aw, gimna na thuak ding uh hi! Banghang hiam cihleh a pualam leikang a kizut han tawh na kibang uh hi. Tua hante a pualam a etlawm hangin a sungah misi guh le a kihhuai na khempeuh a dim hi. 
\v 28 Tua mah bangin note zong na puatham uh mi dik tawh na kibat uh hangin note sungah kineihna le siatna a dimtakin a om hi. 
\p 
\v 29 \x + \xo 23:29 \xt Luk 11:47-48\x*“A kineih thukhamhilh siate le Pharisee pawlte aw, gimna na thuak ding uh hi! Banghang hiam cihleh kamsangte hante na bawl uh a, mi dikte hante na zem uh hi. 
\v 30 Tua ciangin, ‘I pu i pate khanlai in a om kha hi lehang, kamsangte a thatte lakah i kihel kei ding hi,’ na ci tazen uh hi. 
\v 31 Tua ahih ciangin kamsangte a that mite tu le tate na hih lam uh no le no in teci na pang uh hi. 
\v 32 \x + \xo 23:32 \xt Eze 20:4; 1Th 2:16\x*Tua hi in, na pu na pate uh mawhna zah mah no zong mawhvet un. 
\p 
\v 33 “Gul gupha suante le gul hangsante aw! Hell thukhenna tawh bangci kipelh theih ding na hi uh hiam? 
\v 34 \x + \xo 23:34 \xt Luk 11:49\x*Note kiangah kamsangte, mi pilte le thukhamhilh siate kong sawl hi. Tuate pawlkhat thatin pawlkhat na khailum ding uh hi. Pawlkhatte na kikhopna innte vuah na sat ding uh a, khua khat pan khua khat ah na bawlsia ding uh hi. 
\v 35 \x + \xo 23:35 \xt Pian 4:8; 2Kh 24:21; Zec 1:1; Heb 11:4\x*Tua banga na bawl manun mi dikpa Abel sisan a kipan biakinnpi le biaknatau kikal a na thah uh Berechiah tapa Zechariah sisan dongin leitung a na luansak uh mi dikte sisan khempeuh note tungah hong kisik ding hi. 
\v 36 \x + \xo 23:36 \xt Luk 11:50-51\x*Note kiang ah a man takpi kong cihin ah, hih thu khempeuh tulai khang mite tungah hong tung ding hi. 
\s1 Zeisu In Jerusalem A Tamlawhna 
\r Luk 13:34-35 
\p 
\v 37 \x + \xo 23:37 \xt 2Kh 24:21; Lat 57:1; Isa 31:5\x*“Kamsangte that a, no kianga hong kisawl mite suang tawh a denglum Jerusalem khuapi, Jerusalem khuapi aw, aakpi in a note a khanuai ah a huai bangin na tate ka huai nop hangin na ut kei hi. 
\v 38 \x + \xo 23:38 \xt 1Ku 9:7-8; Jer 22:5\x*En un, na innte uh kilawi ding a, gamkhing a suak ding hi. 
\v 39 A man takpi kong cihin ah, 
\b 
\q1 \qt ‘Topa min tawh hong paipa in thupha ngah tahen,’\qt*\f + \fr 23:39 \ft \+xt Lat 118:26\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* 
\m na cih hun uh hong tung ding hi. 
\b 
\p “Tua hun a tun matengin tu a kipanin kei nong mu nawn kei ding uh hi,” a ci hi. 
\c 24 
\s1 Zeisu In Mailam Thu Genkhol 
\r Mak 13:1-2; Luk 21:5-6 
\p 
\v 1 Tua ciangin \w biakinnpi\w* huang sung pan Zeisu a paikhiat laitak biakinnpi innte a lak dingin a nungzuite hong pai uh hi. 
\v 2 \x + \xo 24:2 \xt Luk 19:44\x*Tua ciangin Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Hih na khempeuh mu hi lo na hi uh hiam? A man takpi kong cihin ah, suang khat tungah suang khat nangawn kiciang nawn loin kiphelkhia ding hi,” a ci hi. 
\s1 Hun Bei Ding A Lak Limte 
\r Mak 13:3-13; Luk 21:7-19 
\p 
\v 3 \x + \xo 24:3 \xt Luk 17:30\x*Olive Mual tungah Zeisu a tut laitakin, a nungzuite kia hong pai uh a, “Hih thute cik ciangin hong piang ding a, nong pai nading le hun bei nading theihsakna bang lim tawh hong kilang ding ahi hiam hong gen in,” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 4 \x + \xo 24:4 \xt Mak 13:5\x*Tua ciangin Zeisu in dawngin amaute kiangah, “Kuamah in hong khem zawh loh nadingin kikem un. 
\v 5 \x + \xo 24:5 \xt 1Jn 2:18\x*Keima minin mi tampi hong pai ding a, ‘Keimah in Khazih ka hi hi,’ ci in mi tampi a khem ding uh hi. 
\v 6 Gal kidona thu le gal hong tung ding hi cih thuthangte na za ding uh hi. Tua ciangin patau kei un; banghang hiam cihleh hih thu khempeuh a pian loh a phamawh hi a, ahi zongin beina a tung nai kei ding hi. 
\v 7 \x + \xo 24:7 \xt Isa 19:2; Saw 11:28\x*Minam khat le minam khat, kumpigam khat le kumpigam khat hong kido ding uh hi. Kialpi le pulnatnate hong tung ding hi. Mun tuamtuam ah zin hong ling ding hi. 
\v 8 Hihte khempeuh in nausuah kuana natna tawh a kibang haksatna kipatna ahi hi. 
\p 
\v 9 \x + \xo 24:9 \xt Joh 15:21; 16:2\x*“Tua ciangin bawlsiatna thuak dingin note hong ap ding uh a, hong that ding uh hi. Keima min hangin minam khempeuh in note hong mudah ding uh hi. 
\v 10 Tua ciangin mi tampi lungkia ding uh a, khat le khat kilehhek in a kimudah ding uh hi. 
\v 11 \x + \xo 24:11 \xt Mak 13:5\x*Kamsang zuau tampi hong piang ding a, mi tampi a khem ding uh hi. 
\v 12 Siatna hong khang ding a, mi tampi in ki-itna a nei nawn kei ding uh hi. 
\v 13 Ahi zongin a tawp donga a kipte in hotkhiatna a ngah ding uh hi. 
\v 14 \x + \xo 24:14 \xt Luk 2:1; Saw 11:28; Rom 10:18; Kil 3:10\x*Minam khempeuh tungah teci ahi dingin Pasian kumpigam lungdamna thu leitung khempeuh ah kitangko ding a, tua khit ciangin beina a tung ding hi. 
\s1 Gimna Lianpi Hun 
\r Mak 13:14-23; Luk 21:2-24 
\p 
\v 15 \x + \xo 24:15 \xt Dan 11:31; 12:11; Saw 6:13\x*“Kamsangpa Daniel in \qt a lipkhaphuai siatna\qt*\f + \fr 24:15 \ft \+xt Dan 9:27\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* thu tawh kisai gen khin hi. Tua mipa in biakinnpi a siangtho mun ah a din hun na muh uh ciangin (a sim mi in thei tahen), 
\v 16 Judea gam a om mite mual tung ah tai uh hen. 
\v 17 \x + \xo 24:17 \xt 1Sa 9:25; Luk 12:3; Saw 10:9\x*Innkhum zanga om mi in na khatpeuh a la dingin inn sungah kumsuk kei hen. 
\v 18 Lokuante zong \w puan\w* la dingin inn ah ciahkik kei uh hen. 
\v 19 \x + \xo 24:19 \xt Luk 23:29\x*Tua hun ciangin naupaite le nawine lai naungek a nei nupite a genthei mahmah ding uh hi! 
\v 20 Na tai hun uh phalbi laitak le \w Sabbath\w* ni ahih khak loh nadingin thungen un. 
\v 21 \x + \xo 24:21 \xt Eze 5:9; Dan 12:1; Joe 2:2\x*Banghang hiam cihleh leitung piancil a kipan tudong in a piang ngei nai lo tunung ciangin zong a piang ngei nawn lo ding gimna lianpi tua hun ciangin a piang ding hi. 
\v 22 Pasian in tua nite a tomsak keileh kuamah a suakta zo kei ding hi. Ahih hangin a teelsa mite a khualna in tua nite a tomsak ding hi. 
\v 23 \x + \xo 24:23 \xt Luk 17:23\x*Tua hun ciangin mi khatpeuh in, ‘En in, hihlai ah Khazih om hi. Hualai ah Khazih om hi,’ hong cih uh hangin um kei un. 
\v 24 \x + \xo 24:24 \xt Pai 7:11; 2Th 2:9-11; Kil 13:13\x*Banghang hiam cihleh Khazih manlote le kamsang zuaute hong piang ding hi. Amaute in hi thei hi leh a teelsa mite nangawn a khem zawh nadingun lim lamdang le nalamdang lianpite a piangsak ding uh hi. 
\v 25 En un, a hun hong tun ma in kong genkhol zo hi. 
\p 
\v 26 “Amaute in, ‘En un, amah gamlak ah om hi!’ hong cih uh hangin zui kei un. ‘En un, amah inndeite sungah om hi!’ hong cih uh hangin um kei un. 
\v 27 \x + \xo 24:27 \xt Luk 17:24, 30\x*Banghang hiam cihleh nisuahna lam panin khua hong phia a, nitumna dong a tansuak bangin \w Mihing Tapa\w* hong pai ciangin tua bangin a piang ding hi. 
\v 28 \x + \xo 24:28 \xt Luk 17:37\x*Misi luang omna peuhah musanete a kikhawm ding uh hi. 
\s1 Mihing Tapa Hong Pai 
\r Mak 13:24-37; Luk 21:25-36 
\p 
\v 29 \x + \xo 24:29 \xt Isa 13:10; 34:4; Eze 32:7; Joe 2:10, 31; Zep 1:15; Kil 6:12-13\x*“Tua gimna lianpi hun a bei khit phetin, ni hong mial ding a, kha a tang nawn kei ding hi. Van panin aksite hong kia ding a, vantung vangliatnate kiling ding hi. 
\p 
\v 30 \x + \xo 24:30 \xt Dan 7:13; Kil 1:7\x*“Tua laitakin vantung ah Mihing Tapa tawh kisai limlamdang hong kilang ding a, leitung minam khempeuh a kap ding uh hi. Mihing Tapa vantung panin vangliatna le minthanna lianpi tawh meii tung tuanga hong pai a mu ding uh hi. 
\v 31 \x + \xo 24:31 \xt Isa 27:13; Zec 9:14; 1Th 4:16; Kil 8:2\x*Amah in a ngaih mahmah pengkul aw tawh ama vantungmite sawl ding a, amaute in lei kiuli le van mong khat pan mong khat donga om a teelsa mite a kaikhawm ding hi. 
\s2 Theikung Tawh Gentehna 
\p 
\v 32 “Tu in theikung tawh kong gentehna panin hih thu na thei un. Theikung a hiangte meng a, a tehte hong sel ciangin khuakhal hong nai ta hi ci in na thei uh hi. 
\v 33 \x + \xo 24:33 \xt Jam 5:9\x*Tua mah bangin hih thu khempeuh hong piang na muh uh ciangin tua hun nai mahmah ta a, kongbiang dong hong tung ta hi ci in na thei un. 
\v 34 Note kiangah a man takpi kong cihin ah, tulai khang mite a bei ma teitei in hih thu khempeuh hong piang ding hi. 
\v 35 Van le lei mangthang ding a, ahi zongin ka thute a mangthang peuhmah kei ding hi. 
\s2 Noah Hun Tawh Gentehna 
\p 
\v 36 \x + \xo 24:36 \xt Saw 1:7\x*“A ni le a nai ding kuamah in a thei kei hi. Vana om vantungmite in zong a thei kei uh hi. Ka Pa bekin a thei hi. 
\v 37 \x + \xo 24:37 \xt Pian 6:5\x*Noah hun lai bangin Mihing Tapa hong pai ciangin zong tua bang hi ding hi. 
\v 38 \x + \xo 24:38 \xt Luk 17:27\x*Tuiciin tun ma a mite in Noah tembaw sungah a lut ni ciangdong, zukham ankham, kipi kiteeng in a om uh hi. 
\v 39 \x + \xo 24:39 \xt Luk 17:30\x*Tuiciin tunga amaute khempeuh a tupmang dongin khuaphawk loin a om uh hi. Mihing Tapa hong pai ciangin zong tua mah bangin a piang ding hi. 
\v 40 \x + \xo 24:40 \xt Luk 17:34\x*Tua hun ciangin lokuan mi nih khat kila in khat kinusia ding hi. 
\v 41 \x + \xo 24:41 \xt Luk 17:35\x*An sukhawm numei nih khat kila in khat kinusia ding hi. 
\p 
\v 42 \x + \xo 24:42 \xt Luk 12:40\x*“Na Topa uh hong pai ding hun thei lo na hih manun kiging den un. 
\v 43 \x + \xo 24:43 \xt Luk 12:39\x*Ahi zongin hih thu thei un. Inn neipa in gutapa pai ding hun theikhol hi leh pang gige in a inn a luhsak kei ding hi. 
\v 44 \x + \xo 24:44 \xt 1Th 5:6\x*Tua ahih ciangin na lamet loh laitakun Mihing Tapa hong pai ding ahih manin note zong kigingsa in om un. 
\s1 Nasem Pil Le Nasem Hai 
\r Luk 12:41-48 
\p 
\v 45 “Inn sung vai khempeuh hawm a, annek huna inn sung mite an manman in a pia dinga a topa in a koih, a muanhuai le a pil nasem kua ahi hiam? 
\v 46 \x + \xo 24:46 \xt Kil 16:15\x*A topa hong tun ciangin tua banga om nasem a muh nasempa in mi hampha ahi hi. 
\v 47 Note kiangah a man takpi kong cihin ah, amah in a neihsa khempeuh tua nasempa a uksak ding hi. 
\v 48 Ahih hangin a hoih lo nasempa in a lungsim sungah, ‘Ka topa hong zekai lai ding hi,’ ci in ngaihsun henla, 
\v 49 \x + \xo 24:49 \xt Luk 21:34\x*a naseppih a lawmte satgawp in, zukhamte tawh nekhawm dawnkhawm in na om leh, 
\v 50 a lamet loh ni le a theih loh kalin a topa hong tungvat ding hi. 
\v 51 A topa in amah tumnih suahin a kineihkhem mite tawh a thuakkhawmsak ding hi. Tualai ah kahna le hagawina a om ding hi,” a ci hi. 
\c 25 
\s1 Nungak Siangtho Sawm Thugentehna 
\p 
\v 1 \x + \xo 25:1 \xt Luk 12:35-38; Saw 20:8; Kil 4:5\x*“Tua banah, vantung kumpigam in zipipa dawn dinga a kuankhia meivak a tawi nungak siangtho sawmte tawh kibang hi. 
\v 2 Tuate lakah ngate pil uh a, a dang ngate a hai uh hi. 
\v 3 A hai ngate in meivak a ken uh hangin meitui a keng kei uh hi. 
\v 4 A pil ngate in ahih leh meivak a ken mah bangun meitui zong thawl sungah a keng uh hi. 
\v 5 \x + \xo 25:5 \xt 1Th 5:6\x*Ahih hangin zipipa hong tung hak ahih manin amaute khempeuh lusu in a ihmu uh hi. 
\p 
\v 6 “Zankim laitakin kikona aw khat hong ging a, ‘Ngai un, zipipa hong paikhia ta hi. Amah dawn dingin hong pai un,’ a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 7 “Tua ciangin tua nungak siangthote a vekpi un tho in a meivak ciat uh vak dingin a kipan uh hi. 
\v 8 \x + \xo 25:8 \xt Luk 12:35\x*A haite in a pilte kiangah, ‘Ka meitui uh bei ahih manin na meitui uh hong hawm un,’ a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 9 “A pilte in, ‘Kong hawm zo kei ding uh hi. Ko aa ding le no aa ding kicing lo ding ahih manin meitui zuakte kiangah pai in va lei un,’ a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 10 \x + \xo 25:10 \xt Kil 19:9\x*“Amaute meitui lei dingin a pai kal un zipipa hong tung hi. Kigingsa a om mite zipipa tawh mopawi bawlna sungah lutkhawm uh a, tua ciangin kong a kikhak hi. 
\p 
\v 11 “Tua khit ciangin nungak siangtho dang teng hong tungkik uh a, ‘Topa aw, Topa aw, kong hong hon in,’ a ci uh hi. 
\v 12 Ahih hangin amah in, ‘A man takpi kong cihin ah, note kong thei kei hi,’ a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 13 \x + \xo 25:13 \xt Mak 13:35; Luk 12:40\x*“Tua ahih ciangin, \w Mihing Tapa\w* hong pai ding a ni le a nai thei lo na hih manun kigingkhol tawntung un. 
\s1 Sumtang Talent Thugentehna 
\p 
\v 14 \x + \xo 25:14 \xt Luk 19:12\x*“Vantung kumpigam in a nasemte sama a neihsa teng a ap khit ciangin khual gamlapi ah a zinkhia mipa tawh kibang hi. 
\v 15 Amah in amaute siamna zui in khatpa \w talent\w* nga, khatpa talent nih, a dang khatpa talent khat a piak khit ciangin a zinkhia hi. 
\v 16 Talent nga a sangpa in a metbawl ciangin a met talent nga a ngah hi. 
\v 17 Tua mah bangin talent nih a sangpa in zong a met talent nih a ngah hi. 
\v 18 Ahih hangin talent khat a sangpa in lei to in a topa sum a phum hi. 
\p 
\v 19 “Hun sawtpi khit ciangin tua nasemte topa hong ciah a, a sum sazian a sit hi. 
\v 20 Talent nga a sangpa in a dang talent nga hong tawi a, ‘Topa aw, sum talent nga nong ap hi. En in, a met talent nga ka ngah hi,’ a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 21 \x + \xo 25:21 \xt Luk 16:10\x*“A topa in, ‘Hoih mahmah hi. A muanhuai nasem hoihpa aw, a tawmno khat tungah citak na hih manin na tampi kong uksak ding hi. Na topa tawh hong lungdamkhawm in,’ a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 22 “Talent nih a sangpa zong hong pai a, ‘Topa aw, sum talent nih nong ap hi. En in, a met talent nih ka ngah hi,’ a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 23 “A topa in, ‘Hoih mahmah hi. A muanhuai nasem hoihpa aw, a tawmno khat tungah citak na hih manin na tampi kong uksak ding hi. Na topa tawh hong lungdamkhawm in,’ a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 24 “Tua khit ciangin talent khat a sangpa hong pai a, ‘Topa aw, khaici na tuh lohna munah an na la a, khaici na theh lohna munah an a kaikhawm, migenhak na hih lam kong thei hi. 
\v 25 Tua ahih manin kong kihta a, lei sungah na sum ka phum hi. En in, na sum hihlai ah a om hi,’ a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 26 “A topa in dawng a, ‘A gilo le a thadah nasempa aw, khaici ka tuh lohna munah an la in, ka theh lohna munah an ka kaihkhop lam hong thei na hih leh, 
\v 27 summet bawlte kiangah ka sum na ap beek leteh kong tun ciangin ka sum le a met ka ngahkhawm thei ding hi. 
\p 
\v 28 “~‘Tua ahih ciangin ama tunga om talent khat la unla talent sawm a neipa pia un. 
\v 29 \x + \xo 25:29 \xt Mak 4:25; Luk 8:18\x*Banghang hiam cihleh a neite kipiak beh ding a, kicingtakin a nei ding uh hi. A nei lote ahih leh a neih sunsun nangawn uh a kilakkhiatsak ding hi. 
\v 30 Tua ahih manin kimanna a nei lo tua nasempa a pualam khuamial sungah paikhia un. Tualai ah kahna le hagawina om ding hi,’ a ci hi. 
\s1 Tuu Le Kel 
\p 
\v 31 \x + \xo 25:31 \xt Luk 17:30\x*“Mihing Tapa in a minthanna le ama \w vantungmi\w* siangthote khempeuh tawh hong pai ciangin ama minthanna kumpi tokhom tungah hong tu ding hi. 
\v 32 \x + \xo 25:32 \xt Eze 34:17, 20; Mal 3:18\x*Tua ciangin ama mai ah minam khempeuh kikhawmsak ding a, tuucingpa in tuu le kel a khen bangin amaute a khen ding hi. 
\v 33 Tuute a taklam ah kelte a veilam ah a koih ding hi. 
\p 
\v 34 \x + \xo 25:34 \xt Saw 20:32; 1Co 15:50; Gal 5:21; Heb 4:3; Jam 2:5; Kil 13:8\x*“Tua khit ciangin Kumpipa in a taklama omte kiangah, ‘Ka Pa thupha piakte aw, hong pai unla leitung piancil a kipan note aa dingin a kibawlkholsa kumpigam hong luah un. 
\v 35 \x + \xo 25:35 \xt Job 31:32; Heb 13:2\x*Banghang hiam cihleh ka gilkial lai in an nong pia uh hi. Ka dangtak lai in ka dawn ding tui nong pia uh a, khualzin mi ka hihlai in zin nong do uh hi. 
\v 36 \x + \xo 25:36 \xt Isa 58:7; Eze 18:7; 2Ti 1:16; Jam 1:27; 2:15-16\x*\w Puan\w* nei lo a ka omlai in puansilh nong pia uh hi. Ka cinat lai in nong veh uh a, thong ka kiat lai in nong hawh uh hi,’ a ci ding hi. 
\p 
\v 37 “Tua ciangin mi dikte in dawng a, ‘Topa aw, na gilkial lam cik in hong mu a, an hong pia ka hi uh hiam? Na dangtak lam cik in hong mu a, na dawn ding tui hong pia ka hi uh hiam? 
\v 38 Khualzin mi na hih lam cik in hong mu a, zin hong do ka hi uh hiam? Puan na neih loh lam cik in hong mu a, puansilh hong pia ka hi uh hiam? 
\v 39 Na cinat, na thongkiat cik in hong mu a, hong veh ka hi uh hiam?’ ci in a dawng ding uh hi. 
\p 
\v 40 \x + \xo 25:40 \xt Heb 13:2\x*“Tua ciangin Kumpipa in, ‘A man takpi kong cihin ah, hih ka sanggamte a neupen khat tunga na bawl peuhmah uh kei tunga hong bawl na hi uh hi,’ ci in a dawng ding hi. 
\p 
\v 41 \x + \xo 25:41 \xt Isa 66:24; Mak 9:43; Luk 3:17; 2Pe 2:4; Jud 1:7\x*“Tua khit ciangin a veilam a omte kiangah, ‘Samsiatna a ngah mite aw, ka kiang panin paikhia un. \w Dawimangpa\w* le a pawlte aa dingin a kibawlkholsa, a kuang tawntung meilipi sungah pai un. 
\v 42 Banghang hiam cihleh ka gilkial lai in an nong pia kei uh a, ka dangtak lai in dawn ding tui nong pia kei uh hi. 
\v 43 Khualzin mi ka hihlai in zin nong do kei uh a, puan nei lo a ka omlai in puansilh nong pia kei uh hi. Ka cinat lai le thong ka kiat lai in zong nong veh kei uh hi,’ a ci ding hi. 
\p 
\v 44 “Tua ciangin amaute in, ‘Topa aw, na gilkial lai, na dangtak lai, khualzin mi na hihlai, puan nei lo a na omlai, na cinat lai le na thongkiat laitak cik in hong mu a, hong don kha lo ka hi uh hiam?’ a ci ding uh hi. 
\p 
\v 45 \x + \xo 25:45 \xt Pau 14:31\x*“Tua ciangin Kumpipa in, ‘A man takpi kong cihin ah, hih mite a neupen khat tungah na bawl loh khempeuh uh, kei tungah zong a hong bawl lo na hi uh hi,’ ci in a dawng ding hi. 
\p 
\v 46 \x + \xo 25:46 \xt Dan 12:2; Joh 3:15-16, 36; Saw 24:15; Rom 2:7; Gal 6:8; 1Jn 1:2\x*“Tua ciangin a tawntung gawtna a thuak dingin amaute paikhia ding uh a, mi dikte ahih leh nuntak tawntungna munah a pai ding uh hi,” a ci hi. 
\c 26
\s1 Zeisu Thah Sawm Uh
\r Mak 14:1, 2; Luk 22:1, 2
\p
\v 1 Zeisu in hih thute khempeuh a gen khit ciangin, a nungzuite kiangah,
\v 2 \x + \xo 26:2 \xt Joh 11:55\x*“Ni nih khit ciangin \w Paisan Pawi\w* hong tung ding hi cih na thei uh hi. Tua ni ciangin khailup dingin \w Mihing Tapa\w* a kipia ding hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 3 \x + \xo 26:3 \xt Lat 2:2; Luk 3:2; Joh 11:47-50; Saw 4:6\x*Tua ciangin siampi liante, \w thukhamhilh siate\w* le Judah mite makaite, \w Siampi Ukpa\w* Caiaphas inntual ah a kikhawm uh hi.
\v 4 Amaute in thukawi, thuzuau tawh Zeisu manin thah ding a sawm uh hi.
\v 5 Ahi zongin, “Mi honpi hong lungso kha ding uh ahih manin pawi hun sungin hih kei ni,” a kici uh hi.
\s1 Zeisu Sathau Kinilh
\r Mak 14:3-9; Joh 12:1-8
\p
\v 6 Tu in, Bethany khua a teeng Simon miphakpa a kici pa inn ah Zeisu an ne in a tut laitak,
\v 7 numei khat in a manpha mahmah sathau namtui \w suangkang thawl\w* khat tawi in hong pai a, Zeisu lu tungah a buak hi.
\p
\v 8 Ahih hangin a nungzuite in a muh uh ciangin lungkim lo uh a, “Banghang in hih sathau namtui tuaci thangbawl ahi hiam?
\v 9 Sum tampi tawh zuak in mi zawngte kipia zaw leh,” a ci uh hi.
\p
\v 10 Ahih hangin Zeisu in tua thu a theih ciangin amaute kiangah, “Banghangin tua numeinu nawngkaisak na hi uh hiam? Amah in kei tungah nasep hoih khat hong bawl khin hi.
\v 11 \x + \xo 26:11 \xt Thu 15:11\x*Mi zawngte note tawh om den uh a, kei ka hih leh note tawh ka omkhawm den kei ding hi.
\v 12 \x + \xo 26:12 \xt Joh 19:40\x*Amah in ka pumpi hih sathau namtui hong buah pen a kivui ding ka pumpi hong puahkhol ahi hi.
\v 13 Note kiangah a man takpi kong cihin ah, hih lungdamna thu a kitangkona leitung mun khempeuh ah hih numeinu a kiphawk nadingin kei tungah a hong bawlna zong a kigen ding hi,” a ci hi.
\s1 Zeisu Lehhek Ding Judas Thukim
\r Mak 14:10, 11; Luk 22:3-6
\p
\v 14 Tua khit ciangin sawm le nihte lakah Judas Iscariot kici pa siampi liante kiangah va pai a,
\v 15 \x + \xo 26:15 \xt Pai 21:32; Zec 11:12\x*“Note khut ah amah hong pia hi leng kei bang hong pia ding na hi uh hiam?” a ci hi. Amaute in \w nguntang\w*\f + \fr 26:15 \fk nguntang\ft : Nguntang khat ciangin drachma tang li tawh kikim hi. A nunga Vantehnate nuai ah “drachma” en in.\f* 30 piak dingin a kithukim uh hi.
\v 16 Tua huna kipanin Judas in Zeisu a lehhek nading hun hoih a zong hi.
\s1 Topa Tawh Nitak Anne
\r Mak 14:12-26; Luk 22:7-23
\p
\v 17 \x + \xo 26:17 \xt Pai 12:18-20; Thu 16:5-8\x*Silngo Sawhloh Anlum Pawi a kipat ni in nungzuite Zeisu kiangah hong pai uh a, “Paisan Pawi an na nek nading koilai ah hong bawlkholhsak le ung na ut hiam?” a ci uh hi.
\p
\v 18 \x + \xo 26:18 \xt Mak 14:35, 41; Joh 7:6, 8\x*Amah in, “Khua sungah va pai unla, kong gensa mipa kiangah, ‘Siapa in, “Ka hun hong nai ta ahih manin ka nungzuite tawh na inn ah Paisan Pawi ka bawl ding hi,” ci hi,’ va ci un,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 19 Nungzuite in Zeisu cih bangin hih uh a, Paisan Pawi an a bawlkhol uh hi.
\p
\v 20 Nitak hong tun ciangin sawm le nihte tawh Zeisu a tukhawm hi.
\v 21 \x + \xo 26:21 \xt Luk 22:21-23; Joh 13:21\x*Amaute in an a nek laitakun amah in, “A man takpi kong cihin ah, note lakah khat in kei nong lehhek ding uh hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 22 Amaute dah mahmah uh a, ama kiangah, “Topa aw, kei ka hi hiam?” ci in a dong ciat uh hi.
\p
\v 23 \x + \xo 26:23 \xt Lat 41:9; Joh 13:18\x*Zeisu in dawng a, “Ankuang ka sawkkhoppih pa in kei hong lehhek ding hi.
\v 24 \x + \xo 26:24 \xt Isa 50:6; Dan 9:26; Mak 9:12; Luk 24:25-27; Saw 17:2-3; 1Pe 1:10-11\x*\w Lai Siangtho\w* sungah ama thu a kigelhsa bangin Mihing Tapa a pai ding mah ahi hi. Ahi zongin Mihing Tapa a lehhekpa in gimna a thuak ding hi! Tua pa mihing in a piangkhia lo hivet leh ama aa dingin hoihzaw ding hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 25 Amah a lehhekpa Judas in, “\w Rabbi\w* aw, kei ka hi hiam?” a cih ciangin amah in, “Na cih bangin na hi hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 26 Amaute in an a nek laitakun, Zeisu in anlum la a, lungdam a koh khit ciangin balkham in, “La unla, ne un. Hih in ka pumpi ahi hi,” ci in nungzuite a pia hi.
\p
\v 27 \x + \xo 26:27 \xt 1Co 10:16\x*Hai zong la a, lungdam a koh khit ciangin, “Na vekpi un dawn un.
\v 28 \x + \xo 26:28 \xt Pai 24:6-8; Zec 9:11; Mal 2:5; Mak 1:4; Heb 9:20\x*Hih in mi tampi mawhna a mai nadinga a luangkhia, \w thuciamna\w* thak ka sisan ahi hi.
\v 29 \x + \xo 26:29 \xt Saw 10:41\x*Note kong genin ah ka Pa kumpigam sungah note tawh lenggahzu a thak ka dawn ni matengin tu a kipan ka dawn nawn kei ding hi,” ci in a pia hi.
\p
\v 30 Amaute in biakna la khat a sak khit uh ciangin Olive Mual zuanin a paikhia uh hi.
\s1 Peter Nial Ding Kigenkhol
\r Mak 14:27-31; Luk 22:31-34; Joh 13:31-38
\p
\v 31 \x + \xo 26:31 \xt Joh 16:32\x*Tua khit ciangin Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Tu zan ciangin keima hangin na vekpi un na puk ding uh hi; banghang hiam cihleh Lai Siangtho sungah,
\b
\q1 \qt ‘Tuucingpa ka sat ding a,\qt*
\q1 \qt Tuu honte a kithehthang ding uh hi,’\qt*\f + \fr 26:31 \ft \+xt Zec 13:7\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f*
\m ci in a kigelh hi.
\b
\p
\v 32 “Ahih hangin ka thawhkik khit ciangin Galilee gam ah note ma in ka na paikhol ding hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 33 Peter in, “Nangma hangin mi khempeuh a puk zongin kei ka puk ngei kei ding hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 34 \x + \xo 26:34 \xt Joh 13:38\x*Tua ciangin Zeisu in, “A man takpi kong cihin ah, tuzan aak a khuan ma in thumvei nong nial ding hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 35 \x + \xo 26:35 \xt Joh 13:37\x*Peter in, “Nang tawh sihkhawm nading ahi zongin kong nial peuhmah kei ding hi,” a ci hi. Nungzui khempeuh in zong tua bangin a ci ciat uh hi.
\s1 Gethsemane Huan Sungah
\r Mak 14:32-42; Luk 22:39-46; Joh 18:1
\p
\v 36 Gethsemane kici mun khat ah Zeisu a tun ciangin a nungzuite kiangah, “Hua pam lamah thu ka va nget sungin hihlai ah na tu un,” a ci hi.
\v 37 Amah in Peter le Zebedee tapa nihte tonpih a, nakpitak a dahna le lunggim hong kipan hi.
\v 38 \x + \xo 26:38 \xt Joh 12:27\x*Tua khit ciangin amaute kiangah, “A si zo ding zahin ka lungsim gim lua mahmah hi. Hihlai ah om unla kei hong ngak un,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 39 \x + \xo 26:39 \xt Lat 40:6-8; Isa 50:5; Joh 4:34\x*Amah a gamla zawdeuh ah pai in boksuk a, “Ka Pa aw, hih hai tawh ka kipelh theih ding leh hong kipelhsak in. Ahi zongin, kei deihna bang hi loin, nang deihna bang hi zaw tahen,” ci in thu a ngen hi.
\p
\v 40 Nungzuite kiang a tun ciangin amaute ihmu a om a mu hi. Amah in Peter kiangah, “Nai khat sung nangawn hong ngak zo lo na hi uh hiam?
\v 41 Ze-etna sungah na lut khak loh nadingun thungenin kiging un. Lungsim a ut mahmah hangin pumpi a thanem hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 42 Tua ciangin a nihveina va paikhiakikin thungen a, “Pa aw, hih hai kei tawh kipelh thei lo a, ka dawn loh a phamawh ahih leh nangma deihna bang hi tahen,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 43 Amah hong paikik ciangin nungzuite hak zo mahmah lo uh ahih manin ihmu in a om uh a mukik hi.
\v 44 Tua ciangin amaute nusia in va paikhiakik a, a nget ngei teng mah a thumveina a va ngen leuleu hi.
\p
\v 45 Tua khit ciangin a nungzuite kiangah hong pai a, “Note ihmu mu lai in, tawlnga lailai ding na hi uh hiam? En in, Mihing Tapa mawhneite khut sungah a kipiak ding hun hong tungta hi.
\v 46 Tho unla pai ni. En un, kei hong lehhekpa hong nai mahmah ta hi,” a ci hi.
\s1 Zeisu Kiman
\r Mak 14:43-51; Luk 22:47-53; Joh 18:2-11
\p
\v 47 Tua banga a gengen laitakin sawm le nihte lakah khat ahi Judas in siampi liante le Judah mite makaite in a sawl mi honkhat hong tonpih a, tua mite in namsau le molhtumte a tawi uh hi.
\v 48 Amah a lehhekpa in mihonte kiangah, “Ka nap mipa amah ahi hi man pah un,” ci in a theihsakna lim ahi hi.
\p
\v 49 Amah in thakhatin Zeisu kiang hong naih a, “Rabbi aw, na dam hiam!” ci in a \w nam\w* hi.
\p
\v 50 Zeisu in ama kiangah, “Lawm aw, bang hih dinga hong pai na hi hiam?” a ci hi. Tua khit ciangin mi honpi hong pai uh a, Zeisu man in a paipih uh hi.
\v 51 \x + \xo 26:51 \xt Luk 22:36, 38; Joh 18:10\x*Tua ciangin Zeisu tawh a omkhawmte khat in thakhatin a namsau dokin Siampi Ukpa nasempa a sat leh a bil a satkhia hi.
\p
\v 52 \x + \xo 26:52 \xt Pian 9:6; Pai 21:12; Kil 13:10\x*Tua ciangin Zeisu in tua pa kiangah, “Na namsau a paai ah siatkik in. Namsau tawi peuhmah namsau mah tawh a si ding uh hi.
\v 53 \x + \xo 26:53 \xt 2Ku 6:17; Dan 7:10\x*Tu mahmahin ka Pa kiangah a ngen thei lo hong sa na hi uh hiam? Ngen leng \w vantungmi\w* \w legion\w* sawm le nih sanga a tamzaw hong pia pah ding hi.
\v 54 Tua bangin a ngen hi leng hih banga a piang dingin Lai Siangtho sunga kigensa thute koici tangtun thei ding ahi hiam?” a ci hi.
\p
\v 55 \x + \xo 26:55 \xt Mak 12:35; Luk 21:37; Joh 7:14, 28\x*Tua hun mahin Zeisu in mi honpite kiangah, “Guta buluh khat man ding bangin namsau le molhtum tawi in kei man dingin hong kuan na hi uh hiam? \w Biakinnpi\w* huang sungah thuhilh in nisimin note tawh ka omkhawm a, ahih hangin nong man kei uh hi.
\v 56 Ahi zongin kamsangte gelhsa Lai Siangtho a tangtun nadingin hihte khempeuh a sem na hi uh hi,” a ci hi.
\p Tua khit ciangin nungzuite khempeuh in amah nusia in a taikek uh hi.
\s1 Caiaphas Le Sanhedrin-te Mai Ah Zeisu
\r Mak 14:53-65; Luk 22:54
\p
\v 57 Zeisu a mante in \w thukhamhilh siate\w* le makaite kituahkhopna Siampi Ukpa Caiaphas kiangah amah a paipih uh hi.
\v 58 \x + \xo 26:58 \xt Mak 14:66; Luk 11:21; 22:55; Joh 18:15\x*Peter in Siampi Ukpa inntual dong a galzuih khit ciangin bang thu hong piang peuhmah hiam cih a en dingin huang sungah va lutin biakinn cingte tawh a tukhawm hi.
\p
\v 59 Siampi liante, makaite le thukhente khempeuh in Zeisu a thah theih nadingun zuauthu tawh thu a kawi zonzon uh hangin a mu zo kei uh hi.
\v 60 \x + \xo 26:60 \xt Thu 19:15; Lat 27:12; Saw 6:13\x*A man lo teci pang mi tampi hong pai uh hangin amah thah theih nading thu kician a mu zo kei uh hi. A tawpna ah a man lo teci a pang mi nih hong pai uh a,
\v 61 \x + \xo 26:61 \xt Joh 2:19\x*“Hihpa in, ‘Pasian biakinnpi susia in ni thum sungin ka lam kik ding hi,’ ci hi,” a ci uh hi.
\p
\v 62 Tua ciangin Siampi Ukpa dingto in Zeisu kiangah, “Kam khat beek dawng lo ding na hi hiam? Na langa hih mite tecipanna bang thu ahi hiam?” a ci hi.
\v 63 \x + \xo 26:63 \xt Siam 5:1; Mak 14:61; Luk 22:67\x*Ahih hangin Zeisu a pau tuan kei hi.
\p Siampi Ukpa in ama kiangah, “Pasian Tapa Khazih na hih leh na hih loh nong gen nadingin a nungta Pasian min tawh kong sawl hi!” a ci hi.
\p
\v 64 \x + \xo 26:64 \xt Mak 16:19; Luk 22:70; Kil 1:7\x*Zeisu in, “Na gen bangin ka hi hi. Ahi zongin note tungah kong genin ah, tu a kipan Vangliatna taklam ah Mihing Tapa tu in vana meiipi tawh a hong paina mailam ah na mu ding uh hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 65 \x + \xo 26:65 \xt Mak 14:63\x*Tua ciangin Siampi Ukpa in a \w puan\w* balkek a, “Hihpa Pasian tungah a pausia zo hi! Teci dang kisam lai ahi hiam? En un, Pasian tunga a pausiatna na za zo uh hi.
\v 66 \x + \xo 26:66 \xt Siam 24:16; Joh 19:7\x*Bangci ngaihsut na hi uh hiam?” a ci hi.
\p Amaute in, “A si dingin a kilawm hi,” ci in a dawng uh hi.
\s1 Mite In Zeisu Zahpih
\r Mak 14:65; Luk 22:63-65; Joh 18:22-23
\p
\v 67 Tua khit ciangin a maitang cilphih in a tumgawp uh hi. A dangte in a khutpek uh tawh a pang beng uh a,
\v 68 \x + \xo 26:68 \xt Luk 22:63-65\x*“Tu a nang hong beng kua ahi hiam? Kamsanna tawh hong gen dih in, Khazih aw!” a ci uh hi.
\s1 Peter In Zeisu Nial
\r Mak 14:66-72; Luk 22:54-62; Joh 18:15-18, 25-27
\p
\v 69 Tua laitakin a pualam inntual ah Peter tu in a om hi. Nasem numeino khat ama kiangah va pai a, “Nang zong Galilee mi Zeisu tawh a kithuahpa na hi hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 70 Ahih hangin Peter in, “Na thugen ka thei kei hi,” ci in amaute khempeuh mai ah a nial hi.
\p
\v 71 Amah paikhia in innlim ah a om laitak numeino dang khat in mu a, tualai a om mite kiangah, “Hihpa zong Nazareth mi Zeisu tawh a kithuah khat ahi hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 72 Amah in, “Tua pa ka thei kei hi!” ci in kiciam kawmin a nialkik hi.
\p
\v 73 Tawlkhat khit ciangin a gei a ding mite Peter kiangah hong pai in, “Nang zong amaute khat hingel teh, na awkaihin kithei hi,” a ci uh hi.
\p
\v 74 Tua ciangin Peter in, “Tua pa ka theih ngeitak leh!” ci in kihamsiat in a kiciam hi.
\p Tua khit phetin aak a khuang hi.
\v 75 \x + \xo 26:75 \xt Joh 13:38\x*Tua ciangin Peter in, “Aak a khuan ma in thumvei nong nial ding hi,” ci a, Zeisu in ama kianga a gensa thu phawkkik a, a pualam ah paikhia in nakpitakin a kap hi.
\c 27 
\s1 Sanhedrin Mai Ah Zeisu 
\r Mak 15:1; Luk 22:66-23:1 
\p 
\v 1 \x + \xo 27:1 \xt Mak 15:1; Luk 22:66\x*A zingsang ciangin siampi liante le Judah mite makaite khempeuh in Zeisu a thah theih nadingun a vaihawm uh hi. 
\v 2 \x + \xo 27:2 \xt Mak 15:1; Luk 13:1; Saw 3:13; 1Ti 6:13\x*Tua ciangin amah henin paikhiatpih uh a, mangpipa Pontius Pilate khut ah a piakhia uh hi. 
\s1 Judas Gui-awk 
\r Saw 1:18-19 
\p 
\v 3 Tua ciangin a lehhekpa Judas in sihna daan thuak dingin Zeisu tungah thu kikhen zo hi cih a theih ciangin khial kisa mahmah a, siampi liante le makaite kiangah \w nguntang\w*\f + \fr 27:3 \fk nguntang\ft : Nguntang khat ciangin drachma tang li tawh kikim hi. A nunga Vantehnate nuai ah “drachma” en in.\f* 30 a va piakik hi. 
\v 4 Amah in, “Mawhnei lopa lehhek kha ka hih manin ka khial zo hi,” a ci hi. 
\p Amaute in, “Tua thu le ko bang kisai nawn ka hi uh hiam? Na suah nop peuh suah in,” a cihsan uh hi. 
\p 
\v 5 \x + \xo 27:5 \xt Luk 1:9, 21; Saw 1:18\x*Tua ciangin Judas in a nguntang teng \w biakinnpi\w* sungah pai a, paikhia in a gui-awk hi. 
\p 
\v 6 Siampi liante in tua nguntang teng la uh a, “Hih sum sisan man ahih ciangin sumpi laka hel dingin kilawm lo hi,” a ci uh hi. 
\v 7 Tua banga a kikup khit uh ciangin khualmite a kivui nading belsekpa leitang leina in a nei uh hi. 
\v 8 \x + \xo 27:8 \xt Saw 1:19\x*Tua ahih manin tua leitang pen tuni dongin Sisan Leitang, kici hi. 
\v 9 Hih in kamsangpa Jeremiah in a gensa thu a tangtunna ahi hi. Amah in, \qt “Israelte in ama man ding seh uh a, nguntang 30 a mansak uh hi.\qt* 
\v 10 \qt Amaute in tua sum la uh a, TOPA in kei hong lamlahna bangin belsekpa leitang man dingin a pia uh hi,”\qt*\f + \fr 27:10 \ft \+xt Jer 32:6-9; Zec 11:12-13\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* a ci hi. 
\s1 Pilate Mai Ah Zeisu A Kipuak Masakna 
\r Mak 15:25; Luk 23:2-7; Joh 18:28-38 
\p 
\v 11 Tua ciangin Pilate mangpipa mai ah Zeisu ding a, mangpipa in, “Nang Judah mite Kumpipa na hi hiam?” ci in a dong hi. 
\p Zeisu in, “Na cih bangin ka hi hi,” a ci hi. 
\v 12 \x + \xo 27:12 \xt Mak 14:61\x*Siampi liante le makaite in amah a mawhmatna thu a gengen uh hangin kam khat beek a dawng kei hi. 
\p 
\v 13 Tua ciangin Pilate in ama kiangah, “Hih zahta in nang hong langpan a hong mawhmatna uh za lo na hi hiam?” a ci hi. 
\v 14 \x + \xo 27:14 \xt Mak 14:61\x*Zeisu in kam khat beek a dawn loh ciangin mangpipa in lamdang a sa mahmah hi. 
\s1 Pilate Mai Ah Zeisu Nihvei A Kipuakna 
\r Mak 15:6-15; Luk 23:13-25; Joh 18:39-19:16 
\p 
\v 15 \x + \xo 27:15 \xt Joh 18:39\x*\w Paisan Pawi\w* a tun sialin mangpipa in mipi deih thongkia khat peuhpeuh a khahkhiat zel pen ngeina khat ahi hi. 
\v 16 Tua laitakin Barabbas kici a gilo a minthang thongkiapa khat a om hi. 
\v 17 Tua ahih manin amaute a kikhop laitakun Pilate in amaute kiangah, “Barabbas le Khazih a kici Zeisu, kua zaw kong khahkhiat ding na deih uh hiam?” ci in a dong hi. 
\p 
\v 18 Banghang hiam cihleh amaute in a hazat manun amah a piakkhiat uh ahihlam Pilate in a thei gige hi. 
\p 
\v 19 \x + \xo 27:19 \xt Pian 20:6; Gam 12:6; Job 33:14-16; Joh 19:13\x*Thukhenna tokhom tungah Pilate a tut laitakin a zi in ama kiangah mi khat sawl a, “Tua mi dikpa tawh bangmah na kisawh kha kei in. Tuzan ka mang sungah tua pa hangin gimna nakpi in ka thuak hi,” ci in a zasak hi. 
\p 
\v 20 \x + \xo 27:20 \xt Saw 3:14\x*Tu in siampi liante le makaite in Barabbas khah a Zeisu a kithah nading a ngen dingin mi honpi a holhthawh uh hi. 
\p 
\v 21 Mangpipa in, “Hih mi nihte kuapen hong khahsak leng na ut uh hiam?” ci in a dotkik ciangin amaute in, “Barabbas!” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 22 Tua ciangin Pilate in, “Tua ahih leh Khazih a kici Zeisu bang ka cih ding hiam?” a cih ciangin amaute khempeuh in, “Amah kikhailum hen!” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 23 Tua ciangin mangpipa in, “Amah in bang siatna bawl ahi hiam?” a ci hi. Ahih hangin amaute in, “Singlamteh ah khailum in!” ci in nakpi in a kiko semsem uh hi. 
\p 
\v 24 \x + \xo 27:24 \xt Thu 21:6-8; Lat 26:6\x*Pilate in ama deihna lah tangtung lo, mipite zong hong so zaw semsem cih a muh ciangin tui la in mipi mai ah a khut sil a, “Hih mi dikpa sisan tungah kei ka siang hi. Na suah nop peuh uh suah un,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 25 \x + \xo 27:25 \xt Jos 2:19; Saw 5:28\x*Tua ciangin mi khempeuh in, “Ama sisan phu ko le ka tu ka tate uh tungah hong tung tahen,” ci in a dawng uh hi. 
\p 
\v 26 \x + \xo 27:26 \xt Isa 53:5; Joh 19:1\x*Tua khit ciangin Pilate in Barabbas khahsak a, Zeisu ahih leh a satsak khit ciangin khailup dingin a piakhia hi. 
\s1 Galkapte In Zeisu Zahko 
\r Mak 15:16-20; Luk 22:63-65; Joh 19:2, 3 
\p 
\v 27 \x + \xo 27:27 \xt Joh 18:28\x*Tua ciangin galkapte in \w mangpipa inn\w* ah Zeisu paipih uh a, galkaphon teng zong ama kiangah a kikhawm uh hi. 
\v 28 \x + \xo 27:28 \xt Joh 19:2\x*Amaute in Zeisu puan a suahsak khit uh ciangin puantual san khat a silhsak uh hi. 
\v 29 \x + \xo 27:29 \xt Isa 53:3; Joh 19:2-3\x*A kumpi lukhu dingin linglukhu bawlin khusak uh a, a taklam khut ah \w pumpeng\w* ciang khat a tawisak uh hi. Tua khit ciangin ama mai ah khukdin in, “Judah mite Kumpipa aw, na ci dam tahen!” ci in a zahko uh hi. 
\v 30 Tua ciangin cilphih uh a, a pumpeng tawi la in a lutang a sat uh hi. 
\v 31 \x + \xo 27:31 \xt Isa 53:7\x*A zahko khit uh ciangin a puantual suahkhiatsak in ama puante a silhsakkik uh hi. Tua khit ciangin khailup dingin a paikhiatpih uh hi. 
\s1 Singlamteh Ah Kikhailum 
\r Mak 15:21-32; Luk 23:26-43; Joh 19:17-27 
\p 
\v 32 \x + \xo 27:32 \xt Mak 15:21; Luk 23:26; Saw 2:10; Heb 13:12\x*Tua banga a paikhiat laitakun Simon kici Cyrene mi khat tawh kituak uh a, zawhthawhthu tawh Zeisu singlamteh a puasak uh hi. 
\v 33 \x + \xo 27:33 \xt Joh 19:17\x*Luguh Mun cih khiatna nei, \w Golgotha\w* kici mun a tun uh ciangin, 
\v 34 \x + \xo 27:34 \xt Lat 69:21\x*a dawn dingin tuikha a kihel lenggahzu thuk a pia uh hi. Amah in tawm ciam a ahih hangin a dawn nuam kei hi. 
\v 35 \x + \xo 27:35 \xt Lat 22:18\x*Tua ciangin amaute in singlamteh tungah khai uh a, lai-ai san in a puante a hawm uh hi. Tua in “Amaute in ka puante hawm uh a, ka puan silh a ngah na dingun lai-ai a san uh hi,” ci a kamsangpa gensa thu a tangtun na ding ahi hi. 
\p 
\v 36 Amaute in tua munah tusukin Zeisu a en uh hi. 
\v 37 A lu tungah, “HIHPA IN JUDAH MITE KUMPIPA ZEISU AHI HI,” ci in mawhmatna lai khat a suang uh hi. 
\v 38 \x + \xo 27:38 \xt Isa 53:12\x*Guta nih zong a taklam ah khat, a veilam ah khat amah tawh a kikhaikhawm hi. 
\v 39 \x + \xo 27:39 \xt Lat 22:7; Kah 2:15\x*Tua mun tawna a pai mite in amah zahko in a lu uh peisan in, 
\v 40 \x + \xo 27:40 \xt Joh 2:19\x*“Biakinnpi susia a, ni thum sunga a lam kik ding pa aw, nang le nang kihonkhia in! Pasian Tapa na hih leh singlamteh tung panin hong kumkhia in,” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 41 Siampi liante, \w thukhamhilh siate\w* le makaite in zong tua mah bangin a zahko uh hi. 
\v 42 \x + \xo 27:42 \xt Joh 1:49\x*Amaute in, “Amah in midangte hon zo napi amah le amah a kihonkhia zo kei hi. Israelte Kumpipa ahih takpi leh singlamteh tung panin tu in hong kumkhia hen. Tua hi leh amah i um ding hi. 
\v 43 \x + \xo 27:43 \xt Lat 22:8\x*Amah in Pasian muang in, ‘Pasian Tapa ka hi hi,’ ci ahih manin Pasian in a hotkhiat nop leh tu in honkhia tahen,” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 44 Amah tawh a kikhaikhawm gutate in zong tua mah bangin a zahko uh hi. 
\s1 Zeisu Si 
\r Mak 15:33-41; Luk 23:44-49; Joh 19:25-37 
\p 
\v 45 \x + \xo 27:45 \xt Amo 8:9\x*Tu in, nai guk\f + \fr 27:45 \fk nai guk\ft : Sun nai sawm le nai nih cihna hi.\f* a kipan nai kua\f + \fr 27:45 \fk nai kua\ft : Nitak nai thum a cihna hi.\f* ciangdong leitung bup ah khim a zing hi. 
\v 46 Nai kua\f + \fr 27:46 \fk Nai kua\ft : A neu 45 en in.\f* pawlin Zeisu nakpi in kiko a, “Eli, Eli, lama sabachthani,” a ci hi. Tua in, \qt “Ka Pasian, ka Pasian aw, banghang in hong nusia na hi hiam?”\qt*\f + \fr 27:46 \ft \+xt Lat 22:1\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* a cihna ahi hi. 
\p 
\v 47 Tua muna a ding mi pawlkhat in a zak uh ciangin, “Hihpa in Elijah sam hi!” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 48 \x + \xo 27:48 \xt Lat 69:21\x*Amaute lak panin thakhatin mi khat va tai a, tuihupna khat la in lenggahtui thuk sungah a diah khit ciangin pumpeng dawn ah suangin a dawn dingin a tahto hi. 
\v 49 A dangte in, “Hi ci omsak phot dih un. Amah hon dingin Elijah hong pai hiam en dih ni,” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 50 \x + \xo 27:50 \xt Joh 19:30\x*Nakpitakin Zeisu a kikokik khit ciangin a huu tawpna a sangkhia hi. 
\p 
\v 51 \x + \xo 27:51 \xt Pai 26:31-33; Heb 9:3, 8\x*Tua ciangin, en in, biakinnpi sunga kideina puan kikek a, a lu panin a taw dong phelnih a suak hi. Zin zong lingin suangtumte kitam a, 
\v 52 hante zong kihongin a ihmu khinsa mi siangtho tampite kithokiksak hi. 
\v 53 Zeisu a thawhkik khit ciangin amaute han sung pan hong pusuakkhia uh a, khuapi siangtho sungah lutin mi tampi kiangah a kilang uh hi. 
\p 
\v 54 Tua ciangin Zeisu a cing galkap 100 ukpa le a lawmte in zinling le thupiang teng a muh uh ciangin lau mahmah uh a, “Hihpa in Pasian Tapa taktak ahi hi,” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 55 \x + \xo 27:55 \xt Luk 8:2-3\x*Zeisu panpihin a zui Galilee gam pana numei tampite in zong amah a galet uh hi. 
\v 56 \x + \xo 27:56 \xt Mak 15:47; Luk 24:10; Joh 19:25\x*Tuate lakah Magdala khua mi Mary, James le Joses-te nu Mary a kipan Zebedee tate nu zong a om hi. 
\s1 Zeisu Kivui 
\r Mak 15:42-47; Luk 23:50-56; Joh 19:38-42 
\p 
\v 57 Nitak lam ciangin Joseph a kici Arimathea khua a mi haupa khat hong pai hi. Amah zong Zeisu nungzui khat ahi hi. 
\v 58 Pilate kiangah amah va pai a Zeisu luang a ngen hi. Tua ciangin amah piak dingin Pilate in thu a pia hi. 
\v 59 Joseph in Zeisu luang lakhia in puanpak siangtho tawh a tun hi. 
\v 60 \x + \xo 27:60 \xt Mak 16:4; Saw 13:29\x*Tua khit ciangin suang a kikhuak ama bawlsa han thak sungah sial a, suangtumpi khat khuk in hankong a khak khit ciangin a ciah hi. 
\v 61 Magdala khua mi Mary le Mary a dang khat zong han lam nga in a tu uh hi. 
\s1 Hankong Kicinna 
\p 
\v 62 A zingciang ahi \w Kigin Ni\w* in siampi liante le \w Pharisee\w* pawlte Pilate kiangah a va kikhawm uh hi. 
\v 63 Amaute in, “Sia aw, tua zuau genpa in a nuntak lai in, ‘Ni thum khit ciangin ka thokik ding hi,’ ci in a gen thu ka phawkkik uh hi. 
\v 64 Tua ahih ciangin ni thum sung ama han a kicin nadingin thu pia in. Tua hi keileh a nungzuite zanin hong pai in a luang gukhia ding uh a, mite kiangah, ‘Misite lak panin amah thokik zo hi,’ a ci ding uh hi. Tua hi leh a masa khemna sangin a nunung khemna suksia zaw ding hi,” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 65 Pilate in amaute kiangah, “A cing ding galkapte nei na hih uh ciangin pai unla na hih theih zahzah un a muanhuai thei thei in bawl un,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 66 \x + \xo 27:66 \xt Thu 6:17\x*Tua ciangin amaute pai in a muanhuai thei thei in a han suangtumpi tungah ciaptehna khen uh a, a cing ding mi zong a koih uh hi. 
\c 28 
\s1 Zeisu Thokik 
\r Mak 16:1-14; Luk 24:1-12; Joh 20:1-18 
\p 
\v 1 \x + \xo 28:1 \xt Luk 8:2\x*Tu in \w Sabbath\w* ni a bei khit nipi kal sunga ni masa pen ni zingsang phalvak tungin Magdala khua mi Mary le Mary dang khat daihawh dingin a pai uh hi. 
\p 
\v 2 \x + \xo 28:2 \xt Joh 20:12; Saw 5:19\x*Tua ciangin, en in, zin nakpi in hong ling hi; banghang hiam cihleh Topa \w vantungmi\w* khat vantung pan hong kumsuk a hankong hukna suangtumpi likkhia in a tungah a tu hi. 
\v 3 \x + \xo 28:3 \xt Dan 7:9; Mak 9:3; Joh 20:12\x*Ama mel khuaphialep tawh kibangin a puan vuk bangin a ngo hi. 
\v 4 Han cingte in amah kihta lua uh ahih manin linggawp uh a, misi tawh kibang uh hi. 
\p 
\v 5 Ahih hangin vantungmi in numeite kiangah, “Lau kei un. Singlamteh tunga a thah uh Zeisu a zong na hi uh hi cih kong thei hi. 
\v 6 A hong gensa bangin amah thokik zo ahih manin, hihlai ah om nawn lo hi. Hong pai unla, Topa luang kisialna mun hong en un. 
\v 7 Pai mengmeng unla a nungzuite kiangah, ‘Amah misite lak panin thokik zo hi. Galilee gam ah amah na pai masa ding a, tualai ah na mu ding uh hi,’ ci in gen un. En un, hih thu note kiangah kong gen zo hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 8 Tua ciangin numeite lau le lungdam kawmsa in han pan ciah pah vingveng uh a, nungzuite kiangah tua thu a ko dingin a tai uh hi. 
\v 9 \x + \xo 28:9 \xt Joh 20:14-18\x*A nungzuite kiangah thuko dingin a pai laitakun, Zeisu in amaute na dawntuah a, “Lungdam un!” a ci hi. Amaute in Zeisu khe va kawi in amah a bia uh hi. 
\v 10 \x + \xo 28:10 \xt Mak 3:34; Joh 20:17; Heb 2:11-13, 17\x*Tua ciangin Zeisu in, “Lau kei un. Pai unla ka sanggamte kiangah, Galilee gam ah hong pai le uh hong mu ding uh hi ci in va gen un,” a ci hi. 
\s1 Hancingte Thugenna 
\p 
\v 11 Numeite a pai laitakun hancingte pawlkhat khuapi sungah pai in thupiang khempeuh siampi liante kiangah a va ko uh hi. 
\v 12 Siampi liante in zong makaite kaikhawm in thu a kikup khit uh ciangin galkapte sum tampi pia uh a, 
\v 13 “~‘Zan ka ihmut kal un a nungzuite hong pai in a luang na gukhia uh hi,’ ci in hong gen un. 
\v 14 Hih thu mangpipa in a zak leh zong amah ka na lungkimsak ding uh a, note kong sukhasak kei ding uh hi,” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 15 Tua ciangin galkapte in zong a sum teng la in a kisawl bangin a gen uh hi. Amau thugen bangin hih thu Judah mite lakah tuni dongin a kigen lai hi. 
\s1 Sawlna Lianpen 
\r Mak 16:15-18; Luk 24:44-49 
\p 
\v 16 Tua khit ciangin nungzui sawm le khatte Galilee gama Zeisu vaikhakna mual ah pai uh a, 
\v 17 amah a muh uh ciangin a bia uh hi. Ahih hangin pawlkhatte a lunghiang lai uh hi. 
\p 
\v 18 \x + \xo 28:18 \xt Dan 7:13-14; Luk 10:22; Joh 3:35; 1Co 15:27; Eph 1:20-22; Phi 2:9-10\x*Tua ciangin Zeisu hong pai in amaute kiangah, “Vantung le leitung a om thuneihna khempeuh kei a hong kipia zo hi. 
\v 19 \x + \xo 28:19 \xt Isa 49:6; Mak 16:15-16; Luk 24:47; Saw 1:8; Rom 6:3-4; Gal 3:27; Col 2:12\x*Tua ahih ciangin note pai unla minam khempeuh ka nungzuite na suahsak khit uh ciangin Pa, Tapa le Kha Siangtho min tawh na baptize un. 
\v 20 \x + \xo 28:20 \xt Thu 31:6; Hag 1:13; Joh 14:26; Saw 2:42; 18:10\x*Note kong piaksa thu khempeuh a zuih nadingun hilh un. En un, hun a bei dongin note kong ompih tawntung ding hi,” a ci hi. \w Amen\w*. 
